  <para style="h">Imisebenzi</para>
  <para style="toc1">Imisebenzi YabaPostoli</para>
  <para style="toc2">Imisebenzi</para>
  <para style="toc3">Ims</para>
  <para style="mt1">Imisebenzi YabaPostoli</para>
  <para style="imt">Isingeniso</para>
  <para style="imt1">Isingeniso</para>
  <para style="im">Incwadi yesibili kaLukha yaziwa njengencwadi yeMisebenzi (bona ULukha 1.0, ukhangele Isingeniso seVangeli lakhe kusiya encwadini yeMisebenzi kanye lokuphothuluka kweVangeli lakhe). Izigaba eziyisithupha zencwadi yeMisebenzi sinye ngasinye sichaza udaba olutsha luphothuluka luveza ukuhanjiswa kwevangeli likaKhristu ezizweni ezingaphandle kweJerusalema. Izigaba lezi zibalulwe ngokwehlukana emutshweni othi <char style="qt">ilizwi likaNkulunkulu laqhubeka lisanda njalo limemetheka</char>:</para>
  <para style="ili1">Esakuqala, ibandla liyakhiwa eJerusalema, kulo lukhulunywe isiGrikhi ukuze limemethekise ivangeli lalo kuwo wonke umbuso kaKhesari.</para>
  <para style="ili1">Esesibili, ivangeli lisiwa kulolonke elaseFilistiya.</para>
  <para style="ili1">Esesithathu, abeZizweni bayamukelwa embuthanweni yabalandeli bakaJesu kanye lamaJuda.</para>
  <para style="ili1">Esesine, izithunywa zithunywa entshonalanga kweRoma, esifundeni sase-Ezhiya.</para>
  <para style="ili1">Esesihlanu, izithunywa zingena eYurophu.</para>
  <para style="ili1">Esesithupha njalo singesokucina, ivangeli lifika esigodlweni seRoma lasezigabeni eziphakemeyo zomphakathi; ngaleyondlela umbuso kaNkulunkulu wamenyezelwa ezizweni zonke.</para>
  <para style="ie"/>
  <chapter number="1" style="c" sid="ACT 1"/>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Wenyukiselwa Ezulwini</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 1:1"/>Encwadini yami yakuqala, Theyofelasi, ngalandisa ngakho konke uJesu akwenzayo lakufundisayo <verse eid="ACT 1:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 1:2"/>kwaze kwafika usuku enyukiswa ngalo esiya ezulwini, esenike izeluleko ngoMoya oNgcwele kubapostoli ayebakhethile. <verse eid="ACT 1:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 1:3"/>Ngemva kokuhlupheka kwakhe, waziveza kubo, wabapha iziqiniseko ezinengi njengobufakazi bokuthi wayephila. Wabonakala kubo okwensuku ezingamatshumi amane, ekhuluma ngombuso kaNkulunkulu. <verse eid="ACT 1:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 1:4"/>Wathi esidla labo ngelinye ilanga wabalaya wathi, <char style="wj">“Lingasuki eJerusalema, lilindele isipho esathenjiswa nguBaba, elangizwa ngikhuluma ngaso.</char> <verse eid="ACT 1:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 1:5"/><char style="wj">Ngoba uJohane wabhaphathiza ngamanzi, kodwa ngemva kwensuku ezimbalwa lizabhaphathizwa ngoMoya oNgcwele.”</char><verse eid="ACT 1:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 1:6"/>Basebesithi gwaqa ndawonye bambuza bathi, “Nkosi, khathesi usuzabuyisela umbuso ko-Israyeli na?”<verse eid="ACT 1:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 1:7"/>Wathi kubo: <char style="wj">“Kakusikho kwenu ukwazi izikhathi loba insuku uBaba azimisileyo ngamandla akhe.</char> <verse eid="ACT 1:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 1:8"/><char style="wj">Kodwa lina lizakwamukela amandla nxa uMoya oNgcwele esefikile kini, njalo lizakuba ngofakazi bami eJerusalema lakulo lonke eleJudiya laseSamariya kanye lasemikhawulweni yomhlaba.”</char><verse eid="ACT 1:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 1:9"/>Esekutshilo lokhu, wenyukiswa phambi kwamehlo abo, iyezi lamfihla, abazabe besambona.<verse eid="ACT 1:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 1:10"/>Babejolozele esibhakabhakeni ngesikhathi esenyuka, masinyazana nje kwema amadoda amabili eduze kwabo egqoke okumhlophe. <verse eid="ACT 1:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 1:11"/>Athi kubo, “Madoda aseGalile, limeleni lapha lijolozele esibhakabhakeni na? UJesu lo osethethwe kini wasiwa ezulwini uzabuya ngayonale indlela elimbone esenyuka ngayo esiya ezulwini.”<verse eid="ACT 1:11"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UMathiyasi Ukhethelwa Ukuba Sesikhundleni SikaJudasi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 1:12"/>Basebebuyela eJerusalema besuka eNtabeni yama-Oliva, okungumango ongaba likhilomitha kusuka edolobheni. <verse eid="ACT 1:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 1:13"/>Ekufikeni kwabo bakhuphukela endlini ephezulu lapho ababehlala khona. Ababelapho babebalisa:</para>
  <para style="b" vid="ACT 1:13"/>
  <para style="li1" vid="ACT 1:13">uPhethro, uJohane, uJakhobe lo-Andreya;</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="ACT 1:13">uFiliphu loThomasi;</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="ACT 1:13">uBhatholomewu loMatewu;</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="ACT 1:13">uJakhobe indodana ka-Alifewu, uSimoni umZilothi, loJudasi indodana kaJakhobe.<verse eid="ACT 1:13"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 1:14"/>Bonke laba bahlangana kokuphela bekhuleka, bendawonye labesifazane loMariya unina kaJesu kanye labafowabo bakaJesu.<verse eid="ACT 1:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 1:15"/>Ngalezonsuku uPhethro wasukuma phakathi kwamakholwa (ixuku elalingafika ikhulu elilamatshumi amabili) <verse eid="ACT 1:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 1:16"/>wathi, “Bazalwane, uMbhalo kwakumele ugcwaliseke, lokho okwakhulunywa nguMoya oNgcwele endulo ngomlomo kaDavida mayelana loJudasi owaba ngumkhokheli walabo ababopha uJesu. <verse eid="ACT 1:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 1:17"/>Wayengomunye wenani lethu njalo waba lengxenye emsebenzini wethu wobuvangeli.”<verse eid="ACT 1:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 1:18"/>(Ngomvuzo awuzuzayo ngenxa yobubi bakhe, uJudasi wathenga isiqinti; khonapho wawa ngekhanda, isidumbu sakhe sadubuka, amathumbu akhe wonke agcwala phansi. <verse eid="ACT 1:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 1:19"/>Bonke eJerusalema bezwa ngalokho, yikho babiza isiqinti leso ngolimi lwabo bathi yi-Akhelidama, okutsho iSiqinti seGazi.)<verse eid="ACT 1:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 1:20"/>UPhethro wathi, “Ngoba kulotshiwe encwadini yamaHubo ukuthi:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ACT 1:20">‘Sengathi indawo yakhe ingaba ngamanxiwa;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ACT 1:20">kungabi lamuntu ozahlala kuyo,’<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1.20 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">AmaHubo 69.25</char></note></para>
  <para style="m" vid="ACT 1:20">njalo,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ACT 1:20">‘Kakube lomunye ozathatha isikhundla sakhe sobukhokheli.’<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1.20 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">AmaHubo 109.8</char></note><verse eid="ACT 1:20"/></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 1:21"/>Ngakho kufanele ukuba sikhethe omunye wamadoda abekade elathi isikhathi sonke iNkosi uJesu isesephakathi kwethu, <verse eid="ACT 1:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 1:22"/>kusukela ekubhaphathizweni kwakhe nguJohane kuze kufike esikhathini lapho uJesu athathwa khona kithi. Ukuze omunye wabo laba abe ngufakazi kanye lathi ngokuvuka kwakhe kwabafileyo.”<verse eid="ACT 1:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 1:23"/>Ngakho basebemisa amadoda amabili, uJosefa owayethiwa nguBhasabhasi (esaziwa njalo ngokuthi nguJustusi) loMathiyasi. <verse eid="ACT 1:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 1:24"/>Basebekhuleka bathi, “Nkosi, uyayazi inhliziyo yomuntu munye ngamunye. Sitshengise ukuthi nguphi phakathi kwalaba ababili omkhethileyo <verse eid="ACT 1:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 1:25"/>ukuba athathe lesisikhundla sobupostoli, uJudasi asitshiyayo esiya lapho ayefanele khona.” <verse eid="ACT 1:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="ACT 1:26"/>Basebesenza inkatho, yadla uMathiyasi, wasesengezwa kubapostoli abalitshumi lanye.<verse eid="ACT 1:26"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 1"/>
  <chapter number="2" style="c" sid="ACT 2"/>
  <para style="s1">UMoya ONgcwele Uyehla NgePhentekhosti</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 2:1"/>Kwathi kufika usuku lwePhentekhosti, bonke babendawonye. <verse eid="ACT 2:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 2:2"/>Masinyane nje kwabakhona umsindo onjengokuvunguza komoya wesiphepho wehla uvela ezulwini, wagcwala indlu yonke ababehlezi kuyo. <verse eid="ACT 2:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 2:3"/>Babona okwakungathi zinlimi ezingamalangabi omlilo ezehlukana zahlala komunye lomunye wabo. <verse eid="ACT 2:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 2:4"/>Bonke bagcwaliswa ngoMoya oNgcwele, basebeqalisa ukukhuluma ezinye izindimi njengokwaneliswa kwabo nguMoya.<verse eid="ACT 2:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 2:5"/>Ngalesosikhathi kwakuhlala amaJuda ayemesaba uNkulunkulu eJerusalema, evela kuyo yonke imibuso yomhlaba. <verse eid="ACT 2:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 2:6"/>Athi ngokuzwa umsindo lo, kwabuthana ixuku labantu bemangele ngoba omunye lomunye wabezwa bekhuluma ngolimi lwakhe. <verse eid="ACT 2:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 2:7"/>Ngokumangala okukhulu babuza bathi, “Kanti bonke laba abakhulumayo kabasimaGalile na? <verse eid="ACT 2:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 2:8"/>Pho kungani omunye lomunye wethu ebezwa bekhuluma ngolimi lwethu na? <verse eid="ACT 2:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 2:9"/>AmaPhathiya, amaMede, ama-Elamu; izakhamizi zaseMesophothamiya, lezeJudiya leKhaphadokhiya, lePhontusi le-Ezhiya, <verse eid="ACT 2:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 2:10"/>leFirigiya lePhamfiliya, leGibhithe lezingxenye zeLibhiya eduze leKhureni; izethekeli ezivela eRoma <verse eid="ACT 2:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 2:11"/>(amaJuda lamakholwa aphendukele enkolweni yesiJuda); amaKhrethe lama-Arabhu, sibezwa befakaza izimangaliso zikaNkulunkulu ngendimi zethu!” <verse eid="ACT 2:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 2:12"/>Babedidekile bengelankani, babuzana bathi, “Kutshoni lokhu?”<verse eid="ACT 2:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 2:13"/>Kodwa abanye benza inhlekisa ngabo bathi, “Banathe iwayini enengi bedlulisa.”<verse eid="ACT 2:13"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UPhethro Ukhuluma Phakathi Kwexuku Labantu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 2:14"/>UPhethro wasesukuma labalitshumi lanye, waphakamisa ilizwi lakhe wakhuluma emphakathini wathi, “Bantu bakithi elingamaJuda, lani lonke eliseJerusalema, kahleni ngilichasisele lokhu; lalelisisani lokhu engikutshoyo. <verse eid="ACT 2:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 2:15"/>Amadoda la kawadakwanga njengokucabanga kwenu. Kuseselihola lesificamunwemunye nje ekuseni! <verse eid="ACT 2:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 2:16"/>Hatshi, lokhu yikho okwakhulunywa ngumphrofethi uJoweli ukuthi:<verse eid="ACT 2:16"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 2:17"/>‘Ngezinsuku zokucina, uNkulunkulu uthi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ACT 2:17">Ngizathululela uMoya wami kubo bonke abantu.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ACT 2:17">Amadodana lamadodakazi enu azaphrofitha,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ACT 2:17">izinsizwa zenu zizabona imibono,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ACT 2:17">lamaxhegu enu azaphupha amaphupho.<verse eid="ACT 2:17"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 2:18"/>Lasezincekwini zami, ezesilisa lezesifazane,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ACT 2:18">ngizawuthulula uMoya wami ngalezonsuku,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ACT 2:18">njalo bazaphrofitha.<verse eid="ACT 2:18"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 2:19"/>Ngizatshengisa izimanga ezulwini phezulu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ACT 2:19">lezibonakaliso emhlabeni phansi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ACT 2:19">igazi lomlilo lezikhatha zentuthu.<verse eid="ACT 2:19"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 2:20"/>Ilanga lizaphendulwa libe yibumnyama,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ACT 2:20">lenyanga ibeligazi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ACT 2:20">phambi kokuba kufike usuku olukhulu lukaThixo, olukhazimulayo.<verse eid="ACT 2:20"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 2:21"/>Njalo wonke obiza</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ACT 2:21">ibizo likaThixo uzasindiswa.’<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">2.21 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">UJoweli 2.28-32</char></note><verse eid="ACT 2:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 2:22"/>Bantu bako-Israyeli, lalelani lokhu: UJesu waseNazaretha wayeyindoda eyamiswa nguNkulunkulu kini, ngezimangaliso lezibonakaliso uNkulunkulu azenzayo phakathi kwenu ngaye, njengoba lina ngokwenu lisazi. <verse eid="ACT 2:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 2:23"/>Umuntu lo wanikelwa kini ngecebo likaNkulunkulu ayelimisile langolwazi lokuzayo; njalo lina lincediswa ngabantu ababi,<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">2.23 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">kumbe </char><char style="fq" closed="false">ngabantu </char><char style="fqa" closed="false">abangelamthetho </char><char style="ft" closed="false">(okutsho abaZizwe)</char></note> lambulala ngokumbethela esiphambanweni. <verse eid="ACT 2:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 2:24"/>Kodwa uNkulunkulu wamvusa kwabafileyo, wamkhulula ebuhlungwini bokufa ngoba ukufa kwakungelamandla okumncindezela. <verse eid="ACT 2:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 2:25"/>UDavida wathi ngaye:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ACT 2:25">‘Ngayibona iNkosi iphambi kwami kokuphela.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ACT 2:25">Njengoba isesandleni sami sokunene,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ACT 2:25">angiyi kunyikinywa.<verse eid="ACT 2:25"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="ACT 2:26"/>Ngakho inhliziyo yami iyathaba</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ACT 2:26">lolimi lwami luyathokoza;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ACT 2:26">umzimba wami lawo uzahlala ulethemba,<verse eid="ACT 2:26"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="ACT 2:27"/>ngoba kawuzukungidela ukuba ngiye endaweni yabafileyo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ACT 2:27">njalo kawusoze wekele ongcwele wakho</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ACT 2:27">ukuthi abone ukubola.<verse eid="ACT 2:27"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="ACT 2:28"/>Ungazisile izindlela zempilo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ACT 2:28">uzangigcwalisa ngentokozo phambi kwakho.’<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">2.28 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">AmaHubo 16.8-11</char></note><verse eid="ACT 2:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="ACT 2:29"/>Bazalwane, ngilitshela ngilesibindi ukuthi ukhokho uDavida wafa wangcwatshwa, njalo ithuna lakhe likhona khonapha kuze kube lamuhla. <verse eid="ACT 2:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="ACT 2:30"/>Kodwa wayengumphrofethi, ekwazi ukuthi uNkulunkulu wayemthembisile ngesifungo ukuthi wayezabeka omunye wesizukulwane sakhe esihlalweni sakhe sobukhosi. <verse eid="ACT 2:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="ACT 2:31"/>Ngoba ebona okwakuphambili, wakhuluma ngokuvuka kukaKhristu kwabafileyo, ukuthi kazange atshiywe endaweni yabafileyo njalo umzimba wakhe kawukubonanga ukubola. <verse eid="ACT 2:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="ACT 2:32"/>UNkulunkulu usemvusile uJesu lo waphila, thina sonke singofakazi balokho. <verse eid="ACT 2:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="ACT 2:33"/>Njengoba esekhutshulelwe ngakwesokunene sikaNkulunkulu, usamukele kuYise uMoya oNgcwele owathenjiswayo njalo usekuthulule lokho elikubonayo lelikuzwayo khathesi. <verse eid="ACT 2:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="ACT 2:34"/>Ngoba uDavida kenyukanga ukuya ezulwini, kodwa wathi,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ACT 2:34">‘INkosi yathi eNkosini yami:</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ACT 2:34">“Hlala ngakwesokunene sami<verse eid="ACT 2:34"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="ACT 2:35"/>ngize ngenze izitha zakho</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ACT 2:35">zibe yisinyathelo senyawo zakho.”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">2.35 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">AmaHubo 110.1</char></note>’<verse eid="ACT 2:35"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="ACT 2:36"/>Ngakho-ke, u-Israyeli wonke kaqiniseke ngalokhu: uNkulunkulu usenze uJesu lo elambethelayo waba yiNkosi loKhristu.”<verse eid="ACT 2:36"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="ACT 2:37"/>Abantu bathi bekuzwa lokhu bathinteka kakhulu ezinhliziyweni, bathi kuPhethro labanye abapostoli, “Bazalwane, senze njani na?”<verse eid="ACT 2:37"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="ACT 2:38"/>UPhethro waphendula wathi, “Phendukani libhaphathizwe lonke, ebizweni likaJesu Khristu ukuze lithethelelwe izono zenu. Njalo lizakwamukela isipho soMoya oNgcwele. <verse eid="ACT 2:38"/><verse number="39" style="v" sid="ACT 2:39"/>Isithembiso ngesenu labantwabenu labo bonke abakude, lesabo bonke iNkosi uNkulunkulu wethu ezababiza.”<verse eid="ACT 2:39"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="40" style="v" sid="ACT 2:40"/>Wabaxwayisa langamanye amazwi amanengi; njalo wabancenga wathi, “Zisindiseni kulesisizukulwane esonakeleyo.” <verse eid="ACT 2:40"/><verse number="41" style="v" sid="ACT 2:41"/>Labo abalemukelayo ilizwi lakhe babhaphathizwa, kwengezwa enanini labo mhlalokho abangaba zinkulungwane ezintathu.<verse eid="ACT 2:41"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ubudlelwano Bamakholwa</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="42" style="v" sid="ACT 2:42"/>Bayikhuthalela imfundiso yabapostoli kanye lokudlelana, lokuhlephuna isinkwa lokukhuleka. <verse eid="ACT 2:42"/><verse number="43" style="v" sid="ACT 2:43"/>Wonke umuntu wagcwala ukwesaba ngezimanga lezibonakaliso ezenziwa ngabapostoli. <verse eid="ACT 2:43"/><verse number="44" style="v" sid="ACT 2:44"/>Wonke amakholwa ayendawonye, ehlanganyela kukho konke. <verse eid="ACT 2:44"/><verse number="45" style="v" sid="ACT 2:45"/>Athengisa izinto zawo lempahla zawo anika loba ngubani oswelayo. <verse eid="ACT 2:45"/><verse number="46" style="v" sid="ACT 2:46"/>Insuku zonke aqhubeka ehlangana emagumeni ethempeli njalo ehlephuna isinkwa emakhaya awo esidla ndawonye ngezinhliziyo ezimhlophe lezithobekileyo, <verse eid="ACT 2:46"/><verse number="47" style="v" sid="ACT 2:47"/>edumisa uNkulunkulu njalo ethakazelelwa ngabantu bonke. Njalo iNkosi yengeza inani lawo insuku zonke ngalabo abasebesindisiwe.<verse eid="ACT 2:47"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 2"/>
  <chapter number="3" style="c" sid="ACT 3"/>
  <para style="s1">UPhethro Usilisa Isiceli Esigogekileyo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 3:1"/>Ngelinye ilanga uPhethro loJohane babesiya ethempelini ngesikhathi sokukhuleka, ngehola lesithathu emini. <verse eid="ACT 3:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 3:2"/>Indoda eyayigogekile kusukele ekuzalweni kwayo, yayithwalwa isiwe esangweni lethempeli elalibizwa ngokuthi liSango Elihle, lapho eyayibekwa khona nsuku zonke ukuthi icele kulabo ababengena emagumeni ethempeli. <verse eid="ACT 3:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 3:3"/>Yathi ibona uPhethro loJohane bengena yabacela imali. <verse eid="ACT 3:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 3:4"/>UPhethro loJohane bayijolozela. UPhethro wasesithi, “Sikhangela!” <verse eid="ACT 3:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 3:5"/>Ngakho indoda yabakhangela, ithembe ukuthi izazuza ulutho kubo.<verse eid="ACT 3:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 3:6"/>UPhethro wasesithi, “Isiliva kumbe igolide kangilakho, kodwa engilakho ngiyakunika. Ebizweni likaJesu Khristu waseNazaretha, sukuma uhambe.” <verse eid="ACT 3:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 3:7"/>Wambamba ngesandla sokudla wamsukumisa, masinyane nje inyawo lenqagala zakhe kwaqina. <verse eid="ACT 3:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 3:8"/>Wathi lothu ngezinyawo zakhe wahle wahamba. Wasehamba labo ethempelini, ezihambela, eseqa njalo edumisa uNkulunkulu. <verse eid="ACT 3:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 3:9"/>Kwathi abantu bonke bembona ehamba edumisa uNkulunkulu, <verse eid="ACT 3:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 3:10"/>bamnanzelela ukuthi nguye owayehlala ecela esangweni lethempeli lelo, bamangala baphela amandla ngalokho okwakwenzakele kuye.<verse eid="ACT 3:10"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UPhethro Ukhuluma Lababukeleyo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 3:11"/>Isiceli sisathe sece kuPhethro loJohane, bonke abantu bamangala beza kubo begijima endaweni eyayithiwa liKhulusi likaSolomoni. <verse eid="ACT 3:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 3:12"/>UPhethro wathi ekubona lokhu wathi kubo, “Bantu bako-Israyeli, kungani kulimangalisa lokhu na? Kungani lisijolozela sengathi ngamandla ethu loba ukholo lwethu okwenze umuntu lo wahamba na? <verse eid="ACT 3:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 3:13"/>UNkulunkulu ka-Abhrahama, lo-Isaka loJakhobe, uNkulunkulu wabokhokho bethu useyikhazimulisile inceku yakhe uJesu. Lamnikela ukuba abulawe, lamphika phambi kukaPhilathu, loba yena wayesemise ukuthi amyekele ahambe. <verse eid="ACT 3:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 3:14"/>Lamphika oNgcwele njalo oLungileyo, lacela ukuthi likhululelwe umbulali. <verse eid="ACT 3:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 3:15"/>Lambulala umsunguli wokuphila, kodwa uNkulunkulu wamvusa kwabafileyo. Singofakazi bakho lokhu. <verse eid="ACT 3:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 3:16"/>Ngokukholwa ebizweni likaJesu, indoda le eliyibonayo, eliyaziyo, yenziwe yaqina. Kungenxa yebizo likaJesu lokukholwa okuza ngaye okulethe ukusila okupheleleyo kuyo njengoba lonke libona.<verse eid="ACT 3:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 3:17"/>Manje-ke bazalwane, ngiyazi ukuthi lakwenza ngokungazi, njengoba labakhokheli benu labo babengazi. <verse eid="ACT 3:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 3:18"/>Kodwa yiyo indlela uNkulunkulu agcwalisa ngayo lokho ayekutshilo ngaphambilini ngabo bonke abaphrofethi, esithi uKhristu wakhe wayezahlupheka. <verse eid="ACT 3:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 3:19"/>Ngakho phendukani, libuyele kuNkulunkulu ukuze izono zenu zesulwe, ukuze kufike izikhathi zokuhlambulula okuvela eNkosini, <verse eid="ACT 3:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 3:20"/>lokuthi ithumele uKhristu omiselwe lina, yena uJesu. <verse eid="ACT 3:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 3:21"/>Kumele ahlale ezulwini kuze kufike isikhathi lapho uNkulunkulu azaqondisa konke ngaso, njengokuthembisa kwakhe endulo ngabaphrofethi bakhe abangcwele. <verse eid="ACT 3:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 3:22"/>Ngoba uMosi wathi, ‘INkosi uNkulunkulu wenu uzalivusela umphrofethi phakathi kwabafowenu njengami; libokulalela konke alitshela khona. <verse eid="ACT 3:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 3:23"/>Loba ngubani ongayikumlalela uzakususwa ngokupheleleyo ebantwini bakibo.’<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">3.23 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">UDutheronomi 18.15, 18, 19</char></note><verse eid="ACT 3:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 3:24"/>Ngempela, bonke abaphrofethi kusukela kuSamuyeli, bonke abaphrofethi baphrofitha ngazo insuku lezi. <verse eid="ACT 3:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 3:25"/>Lina lizindlalifa zabo abaphrofethi kanye lesivumelwano uNkulunkulu asenza labokhokho benu. Wathi ku-Abhrahama, ‘Bonke abantu bomhlaba bazabusiswa ngesizukulwane sakho.’<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">3.25 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">UGenesisi 22.18; 26.4</char></note> <verse eid="ACT 3:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="ACT 3:26"/>Kuthe uNkulunkulu eseyimisile inceku yakhe, wayithumela kuqala kini ukuba ilibusise ngokuphendula omunye lomunye wenu ezindleleni zenu zobubi.”<verse eid="ACT 3:26"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 3"/>
  <chapter number="4" style="c" sid="ACT 4"/>
  <para style="s1">UPhethro LoJohane Phambi KweSanihedrini</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 4:1"/>Abaphristi lomlawuli wabalindi bethempeli kanye lamaSadusi beza kuPhethro loJohane belokhu besakhuluma labantu. <verse eid="ACT 4:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 4:2"/>Bakhathazeka kakhulu ngoba abapostoli babefundisa abantu betshumayela ukuthi kuJesu kulokuvuka kwabafileyo. <verse eid="ACT 4:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 4:3"/>Babamba uPhethro loJohane, kwathi ngenxa yokuthi kwasekuntambama, babafaka entolongweni kwaze kwaba kusasa. <verse eid="ACT 4:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 4:4"/>Kodwa abanengi abalizwayo ilizwi bakholwa, inani lamadoda lakhula okungaba zinkulungwane ezinhlanu.<verse eid="ACT 4:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 4:5"/>Ngosuku olulandelayo ababusi, abadala, labafundisi bomthetho babuthana eJerusalema. <verse eid="ACT 4:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 4:6"/>U-Anasi umphristi omkhulu, uKhayifasi, uJohane, u-Alekizanda labanye abendlu yomphristi omkhulu. <verse eid="ACT 4:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 4:7"/>Bathi uPhethro loJohane balethwe, baqala ukubathonisa besithi, “Lokhu likwenze ngamandla bani kumbe ngaliphi ibizo na?”<verse eid="ACT 4:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 4:8"/>UPhethro egcwele uMoya oNgcwele wathi kubo, “Babusi labadala babantu! <verse eid="ACT 4:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 4:9"/>Nxa sibekwa umlandu lamuhla ngesenzo somusa owenzelwe indoda ebiyisigoga, besesibuzwa ukuthi isiliswe njani, <verse eid="ACT 4:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 4:10"/>yazini lokhu, lina kanye labo bonke abantu bako-Israyeli; kungenxa yamandla kaJesu Khristu waseNazaretha elambethelayo kodwa uNkulunkulu wamvusa kwabafileyo, yiwo enza indoda le ime phambi kwenu isilile ngokupheleleyo. <verse eid="ACT 4:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 4:11"/>Yena uyilo</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ACT 4:11">‘ilitshe lina abakhi elalilahlayo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ACT 4:11">khathesi seliyilona ilitshe lekhoneni.’<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">4.11 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">AmaHubo 118.22</char></note><verse eid="ACT 4:11"/></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 4:12"/>Kakho omunye okulensindiso kuye; phela kalikho elinye ibizo ngaphansi kwezulu elaphiwa abantu ukuthi sisindiswe ngalo.”<verse eid="ACT 4:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 4:13"/>Bathi ngokubona isibindi sikaPhethro loJohane njalo benanzelela ukuthi ngabantu makhaza, ababengafundanga, batsha amathe, bakunanzelela ukuthi amadoda la ake aphila loJesu. <verse eid="ACT 4:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 4:14"/>Kodwa njengoba babeyibona indoda eyayisilisiwe imi khonapho labo, baswela ukuthi bangathini. <verse eid="ACT 4:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 4:15"/>Ngakho kwathiwa kabasuke emphakathini weSanihedrini, umphakathi wasala uhlanganisa amakhanda. <verse eid="ACT 4:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 4:16"/>Babuzana bathi, “Kambe senzeni ngamadoda la? Bonke abahlala eJerusalema bayakwazi ukuthi benze umangaliso obabazekayo, lathi asingeke sikulandule lokho. <verse eid="ACT 4:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 4:17"/>Kodwa ukuze into le siyimise ukuthi ingasabalali phakathi kwabantu, kasibaqonqoseleni ukuthi bangaphindi bakhulume lakubani ngebizo leli.”<verse eid="ACT 4:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 4:18"/>Basebebabiza njalo, babalaya ukuthi bangaqali ukukhuluma loba ukufundisa ngebizo likaJesu. <verse eid="ACT 4:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 4:19"/>Kodwa uPhethro loJohane baphendula bathi, “Yikuphi okuqondileyo emehlweni kaNkulunkulu ukulalela lina kumbe ukulalela uNkulunkulu? Kwahluleleni lokho. <verse eid="ACT 4:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 4:20"/>Thina ngokwethu asingeke siyekele ukukhuluma ngalokho esikubonileyo lesikuzwileyo.”<verse eid="ACT 4:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 4:21"/>Sebebaqonqosele njalo babakhulula. Baswela ukuthi babengabajezisa njani, ngoba abantu bonke babemdumisa uNkulunkulu ngalokho okwakwenzakele. <verse eid="ACT 4:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 4:22"/>Ngoba leyondoda eyasiliswa ngesimanga yayileminyaka engamatshumi amane ubudala.<verse eid="ACT 4:22"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Umkhuleko Wamakholwa</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 4:23"/>Ekukhululweni kwabo uPhethro loJohane babuyela ebantwini bakibo, bababikela konke okwakukhulunywe kibo ngabaphristi abakhulu labadala. <verse eid="ACT 4:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 4:24"/>Sebekuzwile lokhu, baphakamisa amazwi abo bonke bakhuleka kuNkulunkulu. Bathi, “Thixo Nkosi, wena wenza amazulu lomhlaba, lolwandle lakho konke okukuwo. <verse eid="ACT 4:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 4:25"/>Wena wakhuluma ngoMoya oNgcwele ngomlomo wenceku yakho, ubaba wethu uDavida wathi:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ACT 4:25">‘Kungani izizwe zixokozela,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ACT 4:25">labantu besakha amacebo ngeze?<verse eid="ACT 4:25"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="ACT 4:26"/>Amakhosi omhlaba ayahloma ajame</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ACT 4:26">lababusi bahlangana ndawonye</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ACT 4:26">bemelana loThixo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ACT 4:26">lalowo Ogcotshiweyo wakhe.’<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">4.26 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">AmaHubo 2.1-2</char></note><verse eid="ACT 4:26"/></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="ACT 4:27"/>Ngempela uHerodi loPhontiyasi Philathu bahlangana labeZizwe kanye labantu bako-Israyeli baceba ngenceku yakho engcwele, uJesu owamgcobayo. <verse eid="ACT 4:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="ACT 4:28"/>Benza lokho okwakumiswe ngaphambilini ngamandla akho layintando yakho ukuthi kwakuzakwenzakala. <verse eid="ACT 4:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="ACT 4:29"/>Ngakho, Nkosi, zwana ukusonga kwabo, uphe izinceku zakho amandla ukuthi zilikhulume ilizwi lakho ngesibindi esikhulu. <verse eid="ACT 4:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="ACT 4:30"/>Yelula isandla sakho ukusilisa lokwenza imimangaliso lezimanga ngebizo lenceku yakho engcwele uJesu.”<verse eid="ACT 4:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="ACT 4:31"/>Sebekhulekile, indawo ababekuyo yazamazama. Bonke bagcwaliswa ngoMoya oNgcwele, balikhuluma ngesibindi ilizwi likaNkulunkulu.<verse eid="ACT 4:31"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Amakholwa Ayahlanganyela Kuyo Yonke Impahla Yawo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="ACT 4:32"/>Wonke amakholwa ayenhliziyo nye njalo engqondo nye. Kakho owathi okwakhe ngokwakhe yedwa kodwa babelana konke ababelakho. <verse eid="ACT 4:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="ACT 4:33"/>Abapostoli baqhubeka ukufakaza ngamandla amakhulu ngokuvuka kweNkosi uJesu kwabafileyo, bonke babusiseka kakhulu. <verse eid="ACT 4:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="ACT 4:34"/>Kakho owayeswela phakathi kwabo. Kwakusithi izikhathi ngezikhathi labo ababe leziqinti loba izindlu bazithengise balethe imali abathengise ngayo <verse eid="ACT 4:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="ACT 4:35"/>bayethule ebapostolini, yabelwe loba ngubani ngokuswela kwakhe.<verse eid="ACT 4:35"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="ACT 4:36"/>UJosefa, umLevi waseSiphrasi, abapostoli ababembiza ngokuthi nguBhanabhasi (okutsho ukuthi, iNdodana yeNkuthazo), <verse eid="ACT 4:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="ACT 4:37"/>wathengisa isivande sakhe waletha imali wayethula phambi kwabapostoli.<verse eid="ACT 4:37"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 4"/>
  <chapter number="5" style="c" sid="ACT 5"/>
  <para style="s1">U-Ananiya LoSafira</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 5:1"/>Indoda eyayithiwa ngu-Ananiya ilomkayo uSafira labo bathengisa isiqinti sabo. <verse eid="ACT 5:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 5:2"/>Wavumelana lomkakhe ukuthi afihle enye imali ibe ngeyabo, kwathi enye wayethula kubapostoli.<verse eid="ACT 5:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 5:3"/>UPhethro wasesithi, “Ananiya, kungani uSathane esegabhele inhliziyo yakho usuze uqamba amanga kuMoya oNgcwele, wazigcinela ingxenye yemali eliyizuzileyo ngesiqinti senu na? <verse eid="ACT 5:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 5:4"/>Kanti besingesisenu yini singakathengiswa? Njalo lapho sesithengisiwe, imali ibingaqondananga lani na? Kuyini okubangele ukuthi ucabange ukwenza into enje na? Kawuqambelanga muntu lawo manga, kodwa uwaqambele uNkulunkulu.”<verse eid="ACT 5:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 5:5"/>U-Ananiya wonela ukukuzwa lokhu, wawela phansi wafa. Bonke abezwa ngalesisehlakalo bangenwa yikwesaba okukhulu. <verse eid="ACT 5:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 5:6"/>Kwasekungena amajaha agoqela isidumbu sakhe amthwalela phandle, ayamngcwaba.<verse eid="ACT 5:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 5:7"/>Ngemva kwamahola amathathu umkakhe laye wangena engazi okwasekwenzakele. <verse eid="ACT 5:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 5:8"/>UPhethro wambuza wathi, “Ake ungitshele, yiyo yini le intengo eliyizuzileyo wena lo-Ananiya esiqintini senu?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="ACT 5:8">Wathi, “Yebo, yiyo intengo yaso.”<verse eid="ACT 5:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 5:9"/>UPhethro wathi kuye, “Kungani livumelane ukulinga uMoya weNkosi na? Lalela! Yizisinde zamadoda asengcwabe umkakho esezisemnyango, bazakuthwala lawe futhi.”<verse eid="ACT 5:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 5:10"/>Khonokho wasakazeka phansi eduze kukaPhethro, wafa. Asengena amajaha yena esefile, amthwala aphuma laye ayamngcwaba malungana lomkakhe. <verse eid="ACT 5:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 5:11"/>Ibandla lonke lafikelwa yikwesaba okukhulu kanye labo bonke abazizwayo lezizehlakalo.<verse eid="ACT 5:11"/></para>
  <para style="s1">AbaPostoli Basilisa Abanengi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 5:12"/>Abapostoli benza imimangaliso lezimanga ezinengi ebantwini. Amakholwa wonke ayevame ukuhlangana ndawonye eKhulusini likaSolomoni. <verse eid="ACT 5:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 5:13"/>Kakho omunye owaqunga isibindi wahlangana labo, lanxa kunjalo babalodumo ebantwini. <verse eid="ACT 5:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 5:14"/>Lanxa kunjalo, amadoda labafazi abanengi bakholwa eNkosini, bengezelela ubunengi babo. <verse eid="ACT 5:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 5:15"/>Kwathi ngenxa yalokho, abantu baletha abagulayo ezitaladini, babalalisa emibhedeni lemacansini ukuze isithunzi sikaPhethro sisithe abanye babo lapho esedlula kuphela nje. <verse eid="ACT 5:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 5:16"/>Amaxuku abantu abuthana eqhamuka emizini eyayiseduze kweJerusalema, eletha abagulayo lalabo ababehlukuluzwa yimimoya emibi, bonke basiliswa.<verse eid="ACT 5:16"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukuhlukuluzwa Kwabapostoli</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 5:17"/>Kwasekusithi umphristi omkhulu kanye leqembu lakhe elalingelexuku labaSadusi bangenwa ngumhawu. <verse eid="ACT 5:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 5:18"/>Bababopha abapostoli babaphosela entolongweni yomuntu wonke. <verse eid="ACT 5:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 5:19"/>Kodwa ebusuku ingilosi yeNkosi yavula iminyango yentolongo yabakhupha. <verse eid="ACT 5:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 5:20"/>Yathi, “Hambani liyekuma emagumeni ethempeli, litshele abantu lonke ilizwi lempilo entsha.”<verse eid="ACT 5:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 5:21"/>Kwathi emadabukakusa bahle bangena emagumeni ethempeli, bafundisa abantu njengokutshelwa kwabo.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="ACT 5:21">Ekufikeni komphristi omkhulu leqembu lakhe bahle babiza iSanihedrini; inkundla yonke yabadala bako-Israyeli bathumela ilizwi entolongweni lokuthi kulethwe abapostoli, <verse eid="ACT 5:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 5:22"/>kodwa izithunywa zathi zifika entolongweni zafumana bengasekho. Ngakho zasezibuyela zayabika zathi, <verse eid="ACT 5:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 5:23"/>“Sifumane intolongo ivalwe kuhle labalindi bemi eminyango; kodwa sithe siyivula kasibonanga muntu phakathi.” <verse eid="ACT 5:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 5:24"/>Induna yabalindi bethempeli kanye labaphristi abakhulu bathi bekuzwa lokhu batsha amathe, bamangala ukuthi into le yayikhombani.<verse eid="ACT 5:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 5:25"/>Kwasekufika omunye umuntu wathi, “Zwanini! Amadoda eliwaphosele entolongweni emi emagumeni ethempeli afundisa abantu.” <verse eid="ACT 5:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="ACT 5:26"/>Besizwa lokho, induna yahle yasuka lamanxusa ayo bayabuya labapostoli. Kabasebenzisanga udlakela ngoba besesaba ukuthi abantu babengabakhanda ngamatshe.<verse eid="ACT 5:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="ACT 5:27"/>Sebebalethile abapostoli, babamisa phambi kweSanihedrini ukuthi bathonisiswe ngumphristi omkhulu. <verse eid="ACT 5:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="ACT 5:28"/>Wathi, “Saliqonqosela ukuthi lingafundisi ngebizo leli. Kodwa seligcwalise iJerusalema ngemfundiso yenu njalo lizimisele ukusethesa umlandu ngegazi lomuntu lo.”<verse eid="ACT 5:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="ACT 5:29"/>UPhethro labanye abapostoli baphendula bathi, “Kumele silalele uNkulunkulu kulokulalela abantu! <verse eid="ACT 5:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="ACT 5:30"/>UNkulunkulu wabokhokho bethu wamvusa uJesu kwabafileyo, yena elalimbulele ngokumlengisa esiphambanweni. <verse eid="ACT 5:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="ACT 5:31"/>UNkulunkulu wamphakamisela kwesokunene sakhe waba yiNkosana loMsindisi ukuze anike ukuphenduka lokuthethelelwa kwezono ku-Israyeli. <verse eid="ACT 5:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="ACT 5:32"/>Thina singofakazi balezizinto, njengaye uMoya oNgcwele, uNkulunkulu amnike kulabo abamlalelayo.”<verse eid="ACT 5:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="ACT 5:33"/>Bathi bekuzwa lokhu bathukuthela kakhulu, bafuna ukuthi babulawe. <verse eid="ACT 5:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="ACT 5:34"/>Kodwa umFarisi owayethiwa nguGamaliyeli, engumfundisi womthetho, ehlonitshwa ngabantu bonke, wasukuma wema phambi kweSanihedrini wathi amadoda lawo ake amiswe phandle kancane. <verse eid="ACT 5:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="ACT 5:35"/>Wasesithi emphakathini weSanihedrini, “Madoda ako-Israyeli, cabangani kuhle ngalokhu elifuna ukukwenza emadodeni la. <verse eid="ACT 5:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="ACT 5:36"/>Ngesikhathi esadlulayo kwafika uThewuda ezitshaya umuntu oqakathekileyo, wahuga amadoda angaba ngamakhulu amane. Wabulawa, bonke abalandeli bakhe bahlakazeka, konke kwaphelela emoyeni. <verse eid="ACT 5:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="ACT 5:37"/>Ngemva kwakhe, uJudasi umGalile laye wavela ngezinsuku zokubalwa kwabantu, wakhokhela ixuku labantu ukuba lihlamuke. Laye wabulawa, labalandeli bakhe bonke bahlakazeka. <verse eid="ACT 5:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="ACT 5:38"/>Ngakho, mayelana lalindaba yamanje ngixwayisa lokhu: Bayekeleni abantu laba! Kabahambe! Ngoba nxa inhloso yabo kumbe umkhankaso wabo uvela ebantwini, uzakuba yize. <verse eid="ACT 5:38"/><verse number="39" style="v" sid="ACT 5:39"/>Kodwa nxa uvela kuNkulunkulu, kalisoze libe lamandla okubamisa lababantu; lizazifumana seliphikisana loNkulunkulu.”<verse eid="ACT 5:39"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="40" style="v" sid="ACT 5:40"/>Inkulumo yakhe bayamukela. Bababiza abapostoli bangeniswa kwathiwa kabatshaywe. Basebeqonqoselwa ukuthi bangaqali ukukhuluma ngebizo likaJesu, basebekhululwa.<verse eid="ACT 5:40"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="41" style="v" sid="ACT 5:41"/>Abapostoli basuka eSanihedrini bethokoza ngoba basebebonakalisile ukuthi bangalimela ihlazo lokulihluphekela iBizo. <verse eid="ACT 5:41"/><verse number="42" style="v" sid="ACT 5:42"/>Insuku ngensuku, emagumeni ethempeli, njalo behamba bengena indlu ngendlu, kabazange bame ukufundisa lokutshumayela izindaba ezinhle ukuthi uJesu unguKhristu.<verse eid="ACT 5:42"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 5"/>
  <chapter number="6" style="c" sid="ACT 6"/>
  <para style="s1">Ukukhethwa Kwabayisikhombisa</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 6:1"/>Ngalezonsuku inani labafundi lisanda, amaJuda esiGrikhi ayephakathi kwabo akhonona kulabo ababengamaHebheru ngoba abafelokazi babo babengananzwa nxa kusabiwa ukudla ngezinsuku zonke. <verse eid="ACT 6:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 6:2"/>Ngakho abalitshumi lambili bahlanganisa bonke abafundi ndawonye bathi, “Kuyabe kungalunganga kithi ukuthi siyekethise ukutshumayela ilizwi likaNkulunkulu silibale ngokulungiselana ukudla. <verse eid="ACT 6:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 6:3"/>Bazalwane, khethani amadoda ayisikhombisa phakathi kwenu aziwayo ukuthi agcwele uMoya lokuhlakanipha. Umlandu lo sizawubekela wona <verse eid="ACT 6:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 6:4"/>thina siqinise ukukhuleka lokutshumayela ilizwi.”<verse eid="ACT 6:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 6:5"/>Umbono lo walithokozisa ixuku lonke. Bakhetha uStefane, indoda eyayigcwele ukukholwa loMoya oNgcwele; uFiliphu, uPhrokhorusi, uNikhanori, uThimoni, uPhamenasi loNikholasi wase-Antiyokhi, ikholwa elaphendukela enkolweni yesiJuda. <verse eid="ACT 6:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 6:6"/>Amadoda la ethulwa kubapostoli, abakhuleka bawabeka izandla.<verse eid="ACT 6:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 6:7"/>Ngakho ilizwi likaNkulunkulu lamemetheka. Inani labafundi eJerusalema landa ngokuphangisa, kwathi lenani elikhulu labaphristi layilandela inkolo.<verse eid="ACT 6:7"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UStefane Uyabotshwa</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 6:8"/>Kwathi uStefane, indoda eyayigcwele umusa kaNkulunkulu, lamandla, yenza izimanga lemimangaliso phakathi kwabantu. <verse eid="ACT 6:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 6:9"/>Kwasekuvela umona usuka emalungeni eSinagogu yabaKhululekileyo (njengokubizwa kwakhona) bengamaJuda aseKhureni le-Alekizandriya kanye lasemikhonweni yaseSilisiya le-Ezhiya. Abantu laba basuka basebephikisana loStefane, <verse eid="ACT 6:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 6:10"/>kodwa behluleka ukumelana lenhlakanipho yakhe kumbe uMoya ayekhuluma ngawo.<verse eid="ACT 6:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 6:11"/>Basebefunza abanye abantu amazwi ngasese ukuthi bathi, “Simzwile uStefane ekhuluma amazwi ahlambaza uMosi kanye loNkulunkulu.”<verse eid="ACT 6:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 6:12"/>Ngaleyondlela badungulula abantu labadala kanye labafundisi bomthetho. Bambopha uStefane bamletha phambi kweSanihedrini. <verse eid="ACT 6:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 6:13"/>Baveza ofakazi bamanga abafakaza bathi, “Indoda le kayikhawuli ukukhuluma kubi ngendawo engcwele langomthetho. <verse eid="ACT 6:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 6:14"/>Ngoba sesimuzwe esithi uJesu lo waseNazaretha uzayibhidliza indawo le njalo aguqule imikhuba uMosi asipha yona.”<verse eid="ACT 6:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 6:15"/>Bonke ababehlezi phakathi kweSanihedrini bamnanzelela uStefane babona ukuthi ubuso bakhe babufana lobuso bengilosi.<verse eid="ACT 6:15"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 6"/>
  <chapter number="7" style="c" sid="ACT 7"/>
  <para style="s1">Inkulumo KaStefane ESanihedrini</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 7:1"/>Ngakho umphristi omkhulu wasembuza wathi, “Ukumangalelwa konke lokhu kuliqiniso na?”<verse eid="ACT 7:1"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 7:2"/>Kulokhu waphendula wathi: “Bafowethu labobaba ake lingilalele! UNkulunkulu wenkazimulo waziveza kubaba wethu u-Abhrahama esahlala eMesophothamiya, engakahlali eHarani. <verse eid="ACT 7:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 7:3"/>UNkulunkulu wathi, ‘Tshiya ilizwe lakini labantu bakini uye elizweni engizakutshengisa lona.’<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">7.3 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">UGenesisi 12.1</char></note><verse eid="ACT 7:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 7:4"/>Ngakho wasuka elizweni lamaKhaladiya wayahlala eHarani. Ngemva kokufa kukayise, uNkulunkulu wamletha kuleli ilizwe lapho eselihlala khona manje. <verse eid="ACT 7:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 7:5"/>Kamuphanga lifa lapha loba nje isiqintshana somhlabathi. Kodwa uNkulunkulu wamthembisa ukuthi yena lezizukulwane zakhe ngemva kwakhe babezalizuza ilizwe lelo libe ngelabo, loba nje ngalesosikhathi u-Abhrahama wayengelamntwana. <verse eid="ACT 7:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 7:6"/>UNkulunkulu wakhuluma laye kanje: ‘Izizukulwane zakho zizakuba ngabezizweni elizweni elingayisilo lazo okweminyaka engamakhulu amane, njalo zizagqilazwa, zihlukuluzwe. <verse eid="ACT 7:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 7:7"/>Ngizasijezisa lesosizwe esibagqilazayo,’<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">7.7 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">UGenesisi 15.13-14</char></note> kusitsho uNkulunkulu, ‘emva kwalokho bazaphuma kulelolizwe bangikhonze kuyonale indawo.’ <verse eid="ACT 7:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 7:8"/>Wasenika u-Abhrahama isivumelwano sokusoka. U-Abhrahama waba nguyise ka-Isaka, wamsoka ngemva kwensuku eziyisificaminwembili ezelwe. Ngemva kwalokho u-Isaka waba nguyise kaJakhobe, uJakhobe yena waba nguyise wabokhokho abalitshumi lambili.<verse eid="ACT 7:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 7:9"/>Ngenxa yokuthi okhokho babalomhawu ngoJosefa, bamthengisela eGibhithe njengesigqili. Kodwa uNkulunkulu waba laye <verse eid="ACT 7:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 7:10"/>wamephula kuzozonke inhlupho zakhe. Wanika uJosefa inhlakanipho, wamenza wathandwa nguFaro, inkosi yaseGibhithe. Yona yasimenza umbusi eGibhithe lakuso sonke isigodlo sakhe.<verse eid="ACT 7:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 7:11"/>Indlala yasihlasela lonke elaseGibhithe leleKhenani, kwaba lobunzima obukhulu ngoba okhokho bethu bakuswela ukudla. <verse eid="ACT 7:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 7:12"/>UJakhobe esezwile ukuthi amabele ayekhona eGibhithe, wathuma okhokho bethu ekuhambeni kwabo kwakuqala. <verse eid="ACT 7:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 7:13"/>Sebesiya khona okwesibili, uJosefa wabatshela abanewabo ukuthi wayengubani, njalo uFaro waziswa ngabakibo kaJosefa. <verse eid="ACT 7:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 7:14"/>Ngemva kwalokho uJosefa wasebiza uyise uJakhobe ukuthi eze labendlu yakhe bonke, kungabantu abangamatshumi ayisikhombisa lanhlanu sebebonke. <verse eid="ACT 7:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 7:15"/>Ngakho uJakhobe wasesehlela kweleGibhithe lapho afela khona yena kanye labokhokho bethu. <verse eid="ACT 7:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 7:16"/>Izidumbu zabo zabuyiswa eShekhemu zabekwa ethuneni elathengwa ngu-Abhrahama emadodaneni kaHamori eShekhemu ngemali ethile.<verse eid="ACT 7:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 7:17"/>Kwathi isikhathi sesisondele esokuthi uNkulunkulu agcwalise isithembiso sakhe ku-Abhrahama, inani labantu bakithi eGibhithe landa ngamandla. <verse eid="ACT 7:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 7:18"/>Kwasekusiba ‘lenye inkosi eyayingazi lutho ngoJosefa yaba ngumbusi eGibhithe.’<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">7.18 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">U-Eksodasi 1.8</char></note> <verse eid="ACT 7:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 7:19"/>Yaba lesihluku ebantwini bakithi, yancindezela okhokho bethu ngokubabamba ngamandla ukuthi balahlele khatshana insane zabo ezisanda kuzalwa ukuthi zife.<verse eid="ACT 7:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 7:20"/>Ngalesosikhathi uMosi wazalwa, njalo engasumntwana makhaza. Okwezinyanga ezintathu wondliwa endlini kayise. <verse eid="ACT 7:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 7:21"/>Kwathi esebekwe phandle, indodakazi kaFaro yamthatha yamkhulisa njengomntanayo. <verse eid="ACT 7:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 7:22"/>UMosi wafundiswa kuyo yonke inhlakanipho yamaGibhithe, eligagu lokukhuluma lokwenza.<verse eid="ACT 7:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 7:23"/>Kwathi uMosi eseleminyaka engamatshumi amane obudala, wacabanga ukuya kwethekelela abantu bakibo, abako-Israyeli. <verse eid="ACT 7:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 7:24"/>Wabona omunye wabo ehlukuluzwa ngumGibhithe, ngakho wayamlamulela, wenanisa ngokubulala umGibhithe lowo. <verse eid="ACT 7:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 7:25"/>UMosi wakhumbula ukuthi abantu bakibo babezakunanzelela ukuthi uNkulunkulu wayemsebenzisa ukuthi abakhulule, kodwa kabakunanzelelanga. <verse eid="ACT 7:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="ACT 7:26"/>Ngosuku olulandelayo uMosi wawela phezu kwabako-Israyeli ababili ababesilwa. Wazama ukubalamula ngokuthi, ‘Madoda, liyizinini; kungani lihlukuluzana kangaka na?’<verse eid="ACT 7:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="ACT 7:27"/>Kodwa leyondoda eyayihlukuluza eyinye, yamfuqela eceleni uMosi yathi, ‘Ngubani okwenze umbusi lomahluli phezu kwethu? <verse eid="ACT 7:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="ACT 7:28"/>Ufuna ukungibulala njengomGibhithe ombuleleyo izolo?’<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">7.28 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">U-Eksodasi 2.14</char></note> <verse eid="ACT 7:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="ACT 7:29"/>UMosi wathi ekuzwa lokho wabalekela eMidiyani, lapho ahlala khona njengesizwe, wazala khona amadodana amabili.<verse eid="ACT 7:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="ACT 7:30"/>Sekwedlule iminyaka engamatshumi amane, ingilosi yavela kuMosi iselangabini lesixuku esibhebhayo enkangala eduze kweNtaba iSinayi. <verse eid="ACT 7:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="ACT 7:31"/>Wathi ekubona lokhu wamangala kakhulu ngalowombono. Wathi uyasondela ukuthi abonisise, wezwa ilizwi likaThixo lisithi: <verse eid="ACT 7:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="ACT 7:32"/>‘NginguNkulunkulu waboyihlo, uNkulunkulu ka-Abhrahama, lo-Isaka loJakhobe.’<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">7.32 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">U-Eksodasi 3.6</char></note> UMosi wathuthumela ngokwesaba wehluleka ukukhangela.<verse eid="ACT 7:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="ACT 7:33"/>INkosi yasisithi kuye, ‘Khupha amanyathela akho, ngoba indawo omi kuyo ingumhlabathi ongcwele. <verse eid="ACT 7:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="ACT 7:34"/>Ngempela sengikubonile ukuhlukuluzeka kwabantu bami eGibhithe. Sengikuzwile ukububula kwabo, ngakho sengibuyile phansi lapha ukuzebakhulula. Manje-ke zwana, ngizakubuyisela eGibhithe.’<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">7.34 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">U-Eksodasi 3.5, 7, 8, 10</char></note><verse eid="ACT 7:34"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="ACT 7:35"/>Nguye kanye uMosi lo ababemalile ngamazwi athi, ‘Ngubani okwenze umbusi lomahluli na?’ Wathunyelwa ukuba ngumbusi lomkhululi nguNkulunkulu mathupha, ngengilosi eyabonakala kuye isesixukwini. <verse eid="ACT 7:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="ACT 7:36"/>Wabakhokhela baphuma elizweni laseGibhithe, wenza izimanga lemimangaliso eGibhithe lasolwandle olubomvu kanye lasenkangala okweminyaka engamatshumi amane enkangala.<verse eid="ACT 7:36"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="ACT 7:37"/>Nguye lo uMosi owatshela abako-Israyeli wathi, ‘UNkulunkulu wenu uzalivusela umphrofethi phakathi kwabafowenu njengami.’<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">7.37 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">UDutheronomi 18.15</char></note> <verse eid="ACT 7:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="ACT 7:38"/>Wayephakathi kwebandla enkangala, elabokhokho bethu njalo elayo ingilosi eyakhuluma kuye eNtabeni yaseSinayi; njalo wemukela amazwi okuphila ukuthi awedlulisele kithi.<verse eid="ACT 7:38"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="ACT 7:39"/>Kodwa okhokho bethu bala ukumlalela. Bamala, kwathi ezinhliziyweni zabo babuyela eGibhithe. <verse eid="ACT 7:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="ACT 7:40"/>Batshela u-Aroni bathi, ‘Yenza onkulunkulu abazasikhokhela. UMosi lo owasikhupha eGibhithe asisakwazi ukuthi usedliwe yini!’<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">7.40 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">U-Eksodasi 32.1</char></note> <verse eid="ACT 7:40"/><verse number="41" style="v" sid="ACT 7:41"/>Yiso lesosikhathi abenza ngaso isithombe esasilesimo sethole. Baletha imihlatshelo kulo, benza umkhosi wokuthakazelela lokho okwenziwa yizandla zabo. <verse eid="ACT 7:41"/><verse number="42" style="v" sid="ACT 7:42"/>Kodwa uNkulunkulu wabafulathela, wabakhalala ukuba bakhonze ilanga, inyanga lezinkanyezi. Lokhu kuvumelana lalokho okulotshiweyo encwadini yabaphrofethi ukuthi:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ACT 7:42">‘Wena ndlu ka-Israyeli,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ACT 7:42">langilethela na imihlatshelo leminikelo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ACT 7:42">ngeminyaka engamatshumi amane enkangala?<verse eid="ACT 7:42"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="43" style="v" sid="ACT 7:43"/>Hatshi, lathwala isikhonzelo sikaMoleki</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ACT 7:43">lenkanyezi kankulunkulu wenu uRefani,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ACT 7:43">izithombe elazenzayo ukuthi lizikhonze.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ACT 7:43">Ngakho-ke, ngizalixotshela ekuthunjweni’<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">7.43 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">U-Amosi 5.25-27</char></note> ngale kweBhabhiloni.<verse eid="ACT 7:43"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="44" style="v" sid="ACT 7:44"/>Okhokho bethu babelalo ithabanikeli lobufakazi enkangala. Lalenziwe njengokuqondiswa kukaMosi nguNkulunkulu elandela isimo ayesibonile. <verse eid="ACT 7:44"/><verse number="45" style="v" sid="ACT 7:45"/>Sebelamukele ithala okhokho bethu bengaphansi kukaJoshuwa beza lalo ekuthumbeni kwabo izizwe. Lahlala elizweni kwaze kwaba yisikhathi sikaDavida, <verse eid="ACT 7:45"/><verse number="46" style="v" sid="ACT 7:46"/>owathandwa nguNkulunkulu, wacela ukuthi alungisele uNkulunkulu kaJakhobe indawo yokuhlala. <verse eid="ACT 7:46"/><verse number="47" style="v" sid="ACT 7:47"/>Kodwa kwaba nguSolomoni owamakhelayo leyondlu.<verse eid="ACT 7:47"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="48" style="v" sid="ACT 7:48"/>Lanxa kunjalo, oPhezukonke kahlali ezindlini ezakhiwe ngabantu. Njengoba esitsho umphrofethi ukuthi:<verse eid="ACT 7:48"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="49" style="v" sid="ACT 7:49"/>‘Izulu liyisihlalo sami sobukhosi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ACT 7:49">lomhlaba uyisenabelo sami.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ACT 7:49">Lizangakhela ndlu bani?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ACT 7:49">kutsho iNkosi.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ACT 7:49">Kambe izaba ngaphi indawo yami yokuphumula na?<verse eid="ACT 7:49"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="50" style="v" sid="ACT 7:50"/>Izinto zonke lezi kazenziwanga yisandla sami na?’<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">7.50 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">U-Isaya 66.1-2</char></note><verse eid="ACT 7:50"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="51" style="v" sid="ACT 7:51"/>Lina ziqholo zabantu, abanhliziyo lezindlebe ezingasokanga! Lifuze oyihlo: Lihlezi lijamelene loMoya oNgcwele! <verse eid="ACT 7:51"/><verse number="52" style="v" sid="ACT 7:52"/>Kambe kwake kwabakhona umphrofethi oyihlo abangazange bamhlukuluze na? Baze bababulala lalabo abaphrofetha ngokuza koLungileyo. Khathesi selimnikele lambulala, <verse eid="ACT 7:52"/><verse number="53" style="v" sid="ACT 7:53"/>lina eseliwemukele umthetho oweza ngezingilosi kodwa kaliwulandelanga.”<verse eid="ACT 7:53"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UStefane Ukhandwa Ngamatshe</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="54" style="v" sid="ACT 7:54"/>Amalunga eSanihedrini esekuzwile lokhu azonda, afuthelana, amgedlela amazinyo. <verse eid="ACT 7:54"/><verse number="55" style="v" sid="ACT 7:55"/>Kodwa uStefane egcwele uMoya oNgcwele wakhangela ezulwini wabona inkazimulo kaNkulunkulu loJesu emi esandleni sokunene sikaNkulunkulu. <verse eid="ACT 7:55"/><verse number="56" style="v" sid="ACT 7:56"/>Wathi, “Khangelani, ngibona izulu livuliwe leNdodana yoMuntu imi esandleni sokunene sikaNkulunkulu.”<verse eid="ACT 7:56"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="57" style="v" sid="ACT 7:57"/>Besizwa lokhu bagcika indlebe zabo, baklabalala, bamdumela <verse eid="ACT 7:57"/><verse number="58" style="v" sid="ACT 7:58"/>bamhudulela phandle kwedolobho, bamkhanda ngamatshe. Ofakazi babeka izigqoko zabo phambi kwejaha elalithiwa nguSawuli.<verse eid="ACT 7:58"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="59" style="v" sid="ACT 7:59"/>Kwathi belokhu bemkhanda uStefane wakhuleka wathi, “Nkosi Jesu, yamukela umoya wami.” <verse eid="ACT 7:59"/><verse number="60" style="v" sid="ACT 7:60"/>Wathi vutshalala ngamadolo phansi wamemeza wathi, “Nkosi, ungababekeli mlandu ngalesisono.” Kuthe esetsho lokho, walala.<verse eid="ACT 7:60"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 7"/>
  <chapter number="8" style="c" sid="ACT 8"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 8:1"/>LoSawuli wayekhona evumelana lokubulawa kwakhe.</para>
  <para style="s1" vid="ACT 8:1">Ukuhlukuluzwa Lokuhlakazeka Kwebandla</para>
  <para style="p" vid="ACT 8:1">Ngalelolanga kwaqalisa isiphithiphithi esibi sokuhlukuluza ibandla eJerusalema, kwathi bonke ngaphandle kwabapostoli bahlakazeka kulolonke iJudiya leSamariya. <verse eid="ACT 8:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 8:2"/>Abantu abakholwa kuNkulunkulu bamngcwaba uStefane bamlilela kabuhlungu. <verse eid="ACT 8:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 8:3"/>Kodwa uSawuli waqalisa ukulichitha ibandla. Wahamba engena izindlu ngezindlu ephuthuma abesilisa labesifazane esiyabaphosela entolongweni.<verse eid="ACT 8:3"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UFiliphu EseSamariya</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 8:4"/>Labo ababehlakazekile balitshumayela ilizwi loba kungaphi abaya khona. <verse eid="ACT 8:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 8:5"/>UFiliphu wehlela edolobheni elithile eSamariya watshumayela ngoKhristu khonale. <verse eid="ACT 8:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 8:6"/>Kwathi amaxuku abantu emuzwa uFiliphu njalo ebona izibonakaliso ayezenza bonke bakulalelisisa lokho ayekukhuluma. <verse eid="ACT 8:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 8:7"/>Omoya ababi baphuma ebantwini abanengi beklabalala njalo abanengi ababome imihlubulo labayizilima basiliswa. <verse eid="ACT 8:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 8:8"/>Ngakho kwaba lentokozo enkulu kulelodolobho.<verse eid="ACT 8:8"/></para>
  <para style="s1">USimoni Umenzi Wamasalamusi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 8:9"/>Okwesikhathi esithile indoda eyayithiwa nguSimoni yayisenza amasalamusi edolobheni lelo yamangalisa bonke abantu baseSamariya. Wayezikhukhumeza ezitshaya umuntu omkhulu, <verse eid="ACT 8:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 8:10"/>njalo bonke abantu, abaphakemeyo labantukazana bambuthanela bababaza bathi, “Indoda le kuqondile ibizwa ngokuthi ingaMandla amakhulu kaNkulunkulu.” <verse eid="ACT 8:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 8:11"/>Bamlandela ngoba wayebamangalisile okwesikhathi eside ngamasalamusi akhe. <verse eid="ACT 8:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 8:12"/>Kodwa kwathi sebekholwe uFiliphu etshumayela izindaba ezinhle zombuso kaNkulunkulu kanye lebizo likaJesu Khristu, babhaphathizwa, abesilisa labesifazane. <verse eid="ACT 8:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 8:13"/>USimoni laye ngokwakhe wakholwa wabhaphathizwa. Walandela uFiliphu zonke indawo, emangaliswa yizibonakaliso ezinkulu lemimangaliso ayibonayo.<verse eid="ACT 8:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 8:14"/>Kwathi abapostoli eJerusalema sebezwile ukuthi iSamariya yase ilamukele ilizwi likaNkulunkulu, bathuma uPhethro loJohane kubo. <verse eid="ACT 8:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 8:15"/>Sebefikile babakhulekela ukuthi bemukele uMoya oNgcwele, <verse eid="ACT 8:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 8:16"/>ngoba uMoya oNgcwele wawulokhu ungakehleli lakubani kubo; babebhaphathizelwe ebizweni leNkosi uJesu kuphela. <verse eid="ACT 8:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 8:17"/>Ngakho uPhethro loJohane bababeka izandla, basebewemukela uMoya oNgcwele.<verse eid="ACT 8:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 8:18"/>Kwathi uSimoni ebona ukuthi uMoya wawuphiwa ngokubekwa izandla ngabapostoli wabahuga ngemali <verse eid="ACT 8:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 8:19"/>esithi, “Ngiphani lami lawomandla ukuze kuthi wonke lowo engimbeka izandla azuze uMoya oNgcwele.”<verse eid="ACT 8:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 8:20"/>UPhethro waphendula wathi, “Sengathi imali yakho ingabhubha kanye lawe ngoba ucabanga ukuthi ungasithenga isipho sikaNkulunkulu ngemali! <verse eid="ACT 8:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 8:21"/>Kawulangxenye loba isabelo kulinkonzo ngoba inhliziyo yakho kayilunganga phambi kukaNkulunkulu. <verse eid="ACT 8:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 8:22"/>Phenduka kulobububi ukhuleke eNkosini. Mhlawumbe izakuthethelela ngokuba lomcabango onje enhliziyweni yakho. <verse eid="ACT 8:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 8:23"/>Ngoba ngiyabona ukuthi ugcwalelene ngomona njalo ugqilazwe yisono.”<verse eid="ACT 8:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 8:24"/>USimoni wasephendula wathi, “Ngikhulekelani eNkosini ukuze ngingehlelwa laloba yikuphi lwalokho okutshiloyo.”<verse eid="ACT 8:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 8:25"/>Kwathi sebefakazile njalo balitshumayela ilizwi leNkosi, uPhethro loJohane babuyela eJerusalema, bahamba betshumayela ivangeli emizini eminengi yaseSamariya.<verse eid="ACT 8:25"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UFiliphu LomTopiya</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="ACT 8:26"/>Ingilosi yeNkosi yathi kuFiliphu, “Yehlela ezansi emgwaqweni, umgwaqo wenkangala, osuka eJerusalema usiya eGaza.” <verse eid="ACT 8:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="ACT 8:27"/>Ngakho wasesuka, kwathi endleleni leyo wahlangana lomTopiya ongumthenwa, eyisikhulu esiqakathekileyo esasiphethe ingcebo kaKhandaki, indlovukazi yamaTopiya. Indoda le yayikade iye eJerusalema ukuyakhonza, <verse eid="ACT 8:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="ACT 8:28"/>isisendleleni yokubuyela ekhaya ihlezi enqoleni yayo ibala incwadi ka-Isaya umphrofethi. <verse eid="ACT 8:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="ACT 8:29"/>UMoya watshela uFiliphu wathi, “Hamba usondele enqoleni leyana walele eduze kwayo.”<verse eid="ACT 8:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="ACT 8:30"/>UFiliphu wasegijimela kuyo inqola wezwa indoda leyo ibala u-Isaya umphrofethi. UFiliphu wayibuza wathi, “Uyakuzwisisa yini lokho okubalayo?”<verse eid="ACT 8:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="ACT 8:31"/>Yathi, “Ngingakuzwisisa kanjani kungekho muntu ongichazelayo na?” Yasicela uFiliphu ukuthi agade azohlala layo.<verse eid="ACT 8:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="ACT 8:32"/>Indoda engumthenwa yayibala indima yombhalo ethi:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ACT 8:32">“Waqhutshwa njengemvu isiwa esilaheni,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ACT 8:32">njengezinyane lemvu elithula zwi phambi komgundi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ACT 8:32">kanjalo kazange awuvule umlomo wakhe.<verse eid="ACT 8:32"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="ACT 8:33"/>Ekugconweni kwakhe wancitshwa ukwahlulelwa okulungileyo.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ACT 8:33">Ngubani ongakhuluma ngezizukulwane zakhe na?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ACT 8:33">Ngoba ukuphila kwakhe kwasuswa emhlabeni.”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">8.33 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">U-Isaya 53.7-8</char></note><verse eid="ACT 8:33"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="ACT 8:34"/>Indoda engumthenwa yabuza uFiliphu yathi, “Ake ungitshele bakithi, umphrofethi ukhuluma ngobani, yena ngokwakhe kumbe ngomunye umuntu?” <verse eid="ACT 8:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="ACT 8:35"/>UFiliphu wahle waqalisa ngaleyondima yoMbhalo, wayitshela izindaba ezinhle ngoJesu.<verse eid="ACT 8:35"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="ACT 8:36"/>Bathi belokhu behamba ngomgwaqo bafika lapho okwakulamanzi khona, indoda engumthenwa yathi, “Khangela, nanka amanzi. Kulani ukuthi ngihle ngibhaphathizwe na?” [ <verse eid="ACT 8:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="ACT 8:37"/>UFiliphu wathi, “Nxa ukholwa ngenhliziyo yakho yonke ungabhaphathizwa.” Isikhulu saphendula sathi, “Ngiyakholwa ukuthi uJesu Khristu uyiNdodana kaNkulunkulu.”]<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">8.37 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Livesi ayikho kwamanye amaBhayibhili esiLungu.</char></note> <verse eid="ACT 8:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="ACT 8:38"/>Isikhulu sathi inqola kayimiswe. Ngakho bobabili, uFiliphu lendoda engumthenwa baya emanzini uFiliphu wayibhaphathiza. <verse eid="ACT 8:38"/><verse number="39" style="v" sid="ACT 8:39"/>Bathi bephuma emanzini uMoya weNkosi wahle wamthatha uFiliphu, indoda engumthenwa ayabe isambona njalo, kodwa yaqhubeka ngendlela yayo ithokoza. <verse eid="ACT 8:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="ACT 8:40"/>Kodwa uFiliphu wabonakala e-Azotha, walidabula ilizwe etshumayela ivangeli kuyo yonke imizi waze wayafika eKhesariya.<verse eid="ACT 8:40"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 8"/>
  <chapter number="9" style="c" sid="ACT 9"/>
  <para style="s1">Ukuphenduka KukaSawuli</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 9:1"/>Kusenjalo, uSawuli wayelokhu esonga ngomvamvithi ukubulala abafundi beNkosi. Waya kuMphristi omkhulu <verse eid="ACT 9:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 9:2"/>wayacela izincwadi zokuya emasinagogweni aseDamaseko, ukuze kuthi nxa engafumana khonale labo abangabeNdlela, abesilisa loba abesifazane, abalethe eJerusalema beyizibotshwa. <verse eid="ACT 9:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 9:3"/>Wathi esebanga eDamaseko ngohambo lwakhe, masinyane kwaphazima ukukhanya kuvela ezulwini kwamzingelezela. <verse eid="ACT 9:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 9:4"/>Wawela phansi, wezwa ilizwi lisithi kuye, <char style="wj">“Sawuli, Sawuli, ungihlukuluzelani na?”</char><verse eid="ACT 9:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 9:5"/>USawuli wabuza wathi, “Ungubani, Nkosi?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="ACT 9:5">Ilizwi lathi, <char style="wj">“NginguJesu omhlukuluzayo.</char> <verse eid="ACT 9:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 9:6"/><char style="wj">Manje phakama uye edolobheni lapho ozatshelwa khona omele ukwenze.”</char><verse eid="ACT 9:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 9:7"/>Amadoda ayehamba loSawuli ema lapho esetshe amathe; balizwa ilizwi, kodwa kababonanga muntu. <verse eid="ACT 9:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 9:8"/>USawuli wavuka phansi, kodwa wathi evula amehlo akhe wayengasaboni lutho. Ngakho bamhola ngesandla bangena laye eDamaseko. <verse eid="ACT 9:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 9:9"/>Waba yisiphofu okwensuku ezintathu, engadli njalo enganathi lutho.<verse eid="ACT 9:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 9:10"/>EDamaseko kwakulomfundi owayethiwa ngu-Ananiya. INkosi yambiza ngombono yathi, <char style="wj">“Ananiya!”</char></para>
  <para style="p" vid="ACT 9:10">Waphendula wathi, “Yebo, Nkosi.”<verse eid="ACT 9:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 9:11"/>INkosi yamtshela yathi, <char style="wj">“Hamba uye endlini kaJudasi eMgwaqweni oQondileyo, ubuze khona ngendoda yaseThasasi ethiwa nguSawuli, ngoba iyakhuleka.</char> <verse eid="ACT 9:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 9:12"/><char style="wj">Usebelombono wabona indoda ethiwa ngu-Ananiya ifika imbeka izandla ibuyisa ukubona kwakhe.”</char><verse eid="ACT 9:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 9:13"/>U-Ananiya waphendula wathi, “Nkosi sengiyizwile indumela yalumuntu mayelana lokubi konke akwenzayo ebantwini bakho eJerusalema. <verse eid="ACT 9:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 9:14"/>Uze lapha ngamandla awaphiwe ngabaphristi abakhulu ukuzabopha bonke ababiza ibizo lakho.”<verse eid="ACT 9:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 9:15"/>Kodwa iNkosi yathi ku-Ananiya, <char style="wj">“Hamba! Indoda le iyisitsha sami engisikhethileyo ukuthwala ibizo lami phambi kwabeZizwe lamakhosi abo laphambi kwabantu bako-Israyeli.</char> <verse eid="ACT 9:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 9:16"/><char style="wj">Ngizamtshengisa ukuthi uzahlupheka kanganani ngenxa yebizo lami.”</char><verse eid="ACT 9:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 9:17"/>U-Ananiya wasehamba esiya kuleyondlu wafika wangena. Wabeka izandla zakhe phezu kukaSawuli wathi, “Mzalwane, Sawuli, iNkosi uJesu obonakale kuwe endleleni usiza lapha ungithumile ukuze ukwazi ukubona njalo futhi ugcwaliswe ngoMoya oNgcwele.” <verse eid="ACT 9:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 9:18"/>Masinyane, kwakhithika okwakungathi zinkwethu emehlweni kaSawuli, wasebona njalo. Wasukuma wabhaphathizwa, <verse eid="ACT 9:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 9:19"/>kwathi esedlile, wathola amandla.</para>
  <para style="s1" vid="ACT 9:19">USawuli EseDamaseko LaseJerusalema</para>
  <para style="p" vid="ACT 9:19">USawuli wahlala insuku ezithile labafundi eDamaseko. <verse eid="ACT 9:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 9:20"/>Waseqalisa ukutshumayela emasinagogweni ukuthi uJesu uyiNdodana kaNkulunkulu. <verse eid="ACT 9:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 9:21"/>Bonke labo abamuzwayo bamangala babuza bathi, “Kasuye yini umuntu lo owenza isihluku eJerusalema kulabo abalibizayo lelibizo na? Njalo kabuyanga yini lapha ukuzabathatha beyizibotshwa abese kubaphristi abakhulu na?” <verse eid="ACT 9:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 9:22"/>Kodwa uSawuli wasebenza ngamandla amakhulu wadidekisa amaJuda ayehlala eDamaseko ngokubonisa kamhlophe ukuthi uJesu unguKhristu.<verse eid="ACT 9:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 9:23"/>Sekudlule insuku ezinengi amaJuda abumba icebo lokumbulala, <verse eid="ACT 9:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 9:24"/>kodwa uSawuli walizwa icebo labo. Emini lebusuku bamlindela emasinagogweni edolobho ukuze bambulale. <verse eid="ACT 9:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 9:25"/>Kodwa abalandeli bakhe bamthatha ebusuku bamehlisa ngesilulu esikhaleni esasisemdulini.<verse eid="ACT 9:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="ACT 9:26"/>Wathi esefikile eJerusalema wazama ukuhlangana labafundi, kodwa bonke babemesaba, bengakholwa ukuthi ngempela wayesengumfundi. <verse eid="ACT 9:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="ACT 9:27"/>Kodwa uBhanabhasi wamthatha wamusa kubapostoli. Wabatshela ngokuthi uSawuli wayibona njani iNkosi esendleleni esiya eDamaseko lokuthi watshumayela njani ngesibindi ngebizo likaJesu. <verse eid="ACT 9:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="ACT 9:28"/>USawuli wasehlala labo, wazihambela ekhululekile eJerusalema, ekhuluma ngesibindi ngebizo leNkosi. <verse eid="ACT 9:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="ACT 9:29"/>Wakhuluma njalo waphikisana lamaJuda esiGrikhi, kodwa azama ukumbulala. <verse eid="ACT 9:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="ACT 9:30"/>Kwathi abazalwane bekuzwa lokhu, bambalekisela eKhesariya bafika bamedlulisela eThasasi.<verse eid="ACT 9:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="ACT 9:31"/>Ngalesosikhathi ibandla kulolonke elaseJudiya leGalile leSamariya laba lesikhathi esihle sokuthula. Laqina, njalo ngokukhuthazwa nguMoya oNgcwele landa ngobunengi, lahlala liyesaba iNkosi.<verse eid="ACT 9:31"/></para>
  <para style="s1">U-Eniyasi LoDokhasi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="ACT 9:32"/>Kwathi uPhethro ebhoda phakathi kwelizwe wayakwethekelela abangcwele eLida. <verse eid="ACT 9:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="ACT 9:33"/>Wafumana khonale indoda eyayithiwa ngu-Eniyasi, eyayiyisigulane esome umhlubulo sihlezi silele okweminyaka eyisificaminwembili. <verse eid="ACT 9:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="ACT 9:34"/>UPhethro wathi kuye, “Eniyasi, uJesu Khristu uyakusilisa. Vuka uthathe icansi lakho.” Masinyane u-Eniyasi wasukuma. <verse eid="ACT 9:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="ACT 9:35"/>Bonke labo ababehlala eLida laseSharoni bambona baphendukela eNkosini.<verse eid="ACT 9:35"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="ACT 9:36"/>EJopha kwakulomfundi owayethiwa nguThabitha (ngesiGrikhi ibizo lakhe nguDokhasi), owayehlala esenza okuhle esiza abaswelayo. <verse eid="ACT 9:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="ACT 9:37"/>Ngalesosikhathi wagula wafa, isidumbu sakhe sageziswa, sabekwa endlini ephezulu. <verse eid="ACT 9:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="ACT 9:38"/>ILida yayiseduze kweJopha; yikho abafundi sebezwile ukuthi uPhethro wayeseLida, bathuma amadoda amabili kuye bamncenga bathi, “Sicela ukuthi uze ngokuphangisa!”<verse eid="ACT 9:38"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="ACT 9:39"/>UPhethro wahamba labo, wathi ekufikeni kwakhe wasiwa endlini ephezulu. Bonke abafelokazi bema bemhanqile, bekhala, bemtshengisa izembatho lezinye izigqoko ezazithungwe nguDokhasi esaphila.<verse eid="ACT 9:39"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="40" style="v" sid="ACT 9:40"/>UPhethro wabakhupha bonke endlini; waseguqa ngamadolo wakhuleka. Wasephendukela esidunjini sowesifazane wathi, “Thabitha, vuka!” Owesifazane wasevula amehlo akhe, wathi ebona uPhethro wahlala. <verse eid="ACT 9:40"/><verse number="41" style="v" sid="ACT 9:41"/>Wambamba ngesandla wamsukumisa. Wasebiza amakholwa labafelokazi wamethula kubo esephila. <verse eid="ACT 9:41"/><verse number="42" style="v" sid="ACT 9:42"/>Lokhu kwasuka kwaziwa kulolonke iJopha, abantu abanengi bakholwa eNkosini. <verse eid="ACT 9:42"/><verse number="43" style="v" sid="ACT 9:43"/>UPhethro wahlala okwesikhathi eJopha loSimoni umtshuki wezikhumba.<verse eid="ACT 9:43"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 9"/>
  <chapter number="10" style="c" sid="ACT 10"/>
  <para style="s1">UKhoneliyasi Unxusa UPhethro</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 10:1"/>EKhesariya kwakulendoda eyayithiwa nguKhoneliyasi, yayingumlawuli webutho lekhulu elalithiwa liViyo lase-Ithaliya. <verse eid="ACT 10:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 10:2"/>Yena lendlu yakhe yonke babekhonza njalo bemesaba uNkulunkulu. Wayenika ngesihle labo abaswelayo njalo ekhuleka kuNkulunkulu kokuphela. <verse eid="ACT 10:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 10:3"/>Ngelinye ilanga, sokungaba lihola lesithathu emini waba lombono. Wabona kamhlophe ingilosi kaNkulunkulu, eyeza kuye yathi, “Khoneliyasi!”<verse eid="ACT 10:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 10:4"/>UKhoneliyasi wayiqhuzulela amehlo ngokwesaba. Wabuza wathi, “Kuyini, Nkosi?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="ACT 10:4">Ingilosi yaphendula yathi, “Imikhuleko yakho lezipho zakho kwabaswelayo sekufinyelele kuNkulunkulu kwaba yisikhumbuzo. <verse eid="ACT 10:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 10:5"/>Ngakho-ke, thumela amadoda eJopha ayebuya lendoda ethiwa nguSimoni owaziwa ngokuthi nguPhethro. <verse eid="ACT 10:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 10:6"/>Ihlala loSimoni ongumtshuki wezikhumba, olendlu okhunjini lolwandle.”<verse eid="ACT 10:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 10:7"/>Ingilosi eyakhuluma laye isihambile, uKhoneliyasi wabiza izinceku zakhe ezimbili kanye loyedwa owayengumncedisi webutho owayeyindoda ekhonzayo. <verse eid="ACT 10:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 10:8"/>Wabatshela konke okwakwenzakele, wasebathuma eJopha.<verse eid="ACT 10:8"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Umbono KaPhethro</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 10:9"/>Sekungaba phakathi laphakathi kwemini sebebanga edolobheni, uPhethro wakhwela ophahleni ukuyakhuleka. <verse eid="ACT 10:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 10:10"/>Wezwa eselambile esefuna ulutho lokudla, kwathi ukudla kusalungiswa wehlelwa yisiyeziphupho. <verse eid="ACT 10:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 10:11"/>Wabona izulu livulekile, kusehliselwa emhlabeni ulutho olwalunjengelembu elikhulu libanjwe ngamagumbi alo womane. <verse eid="ACT 10:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 10:12"/>Lalithwele yonke imihlobo yezinyamazana ezilenyawo ezine, kanye lezinanakazana ezihuquzelayo emhlabeni lezinyoni zemoyeni. <verse eid="ACT 10:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 10:13"/>Ilizwi laselimtshela lathi, <char style="wj">“Vuka Phethro. Hlaba udle.”</char><verse eid="ACT 10:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 10:14"/>UPhethro waphendula wathi, “Hatshi, Nkosi! Kangikaze ngidle lutho olungahlanzekanga lolungcolileyo.”<verse eid="ACT 10:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 10:15"/>Laphinda ilizwi lakhuluma okwesibili kuye lathi, <char style="wj">“Ungabokuthi ulutho oseluhlanjululwe nguNkulunkulu kaluhlanzekanga.”</char><verse eid="ACT 10:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 10:16"/>Lokhu kwenzakala kathathu, kwasekusithi masinyane ilembu labuyiselwa ezulwini.<verse eid="ACT 10:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 10:17"/>Kwathi uPhethro esamangele ngokuthi umbono lowo wawusitshoni, amadoda ayethunywe nguKhoneliyasi ayibona indlu kaSimoni, ema entubeni. <verse eid="ACT 10:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 10:18"/>Akhuleka abuza ingabe uSimoni owayethiwa nguPhethro wayehlala khonapho yini.<verse eid="ACT 10:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 10:19"/>Kwathi uPhethro elokhu esacabanga ngombono, uMoya wathi kuye, “Simoni, kulamadoda amathathu akudingayo. <verse eid="ACT 10:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 10:20"/>Ngakho-ke, phakama wehlele phansi. Ungathandabuzi ukuhamba lawo, ngoba ngiwathumile.”<verse eid="ACT 10:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 10:21"/>UPhethro wehla wathi emadodeni lawo, “Nginguye lowo elimdingayo. Lilandeni?”<verse eid="ACT 10:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 10:22"/>Amadoda aphendula athi, “Sivela kuKhoneliyasi umlawuli wekhulu lamabutho. Ungumuntu olungileyo owesaba uNkulunkulu, ohlonitshwa yibo bonke abangamaJuda. Ingilosi engcwele imtshele ukuthi kakulethe endlini yakhe ukuze ezwe lokho ongabe uyakutsho.” <verse eid="ACT 10:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 10:23"/>UPhethro wasewangenisa endlini amadoda lawo njengezethekeli zakhe.</para>
  <para style="s1" vid="ACT 10:23">UPhethro Endlini KaKhoneliyasi</para>
  <para style="p" vid="ACT 10:23">Ngosuku olulandelayo uPhethro wasuka labo, kwathi labanye abazalwane beJopha bahamba laye. <verse eid="ACT 10:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 10:24"/>Ngelanga elilandelayo wafika eKhesariya. UKhoneliyasi wayesebalindele esebize izihlobo zakhe labangane abaseduze. <verse eid="ACT 10:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 10:25"/>Kuthe uPhethro engena, uKhoneliyasi wamhlangabeza, wazilahla phansi ezinyaweni zakhe ngenhlonipho. <verse eid="ACT 10:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="ACT 10:26"/>Kodwa uPhethro wamsukumisa. Wathi, “Sukuma, mina ngingumuntu nje.”<verse eid="ACT 10:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="ACT 10:27"/>UPhethro wangena endlini elokhu ekhuluma laye, wafumana ixuku labantu elikhulu. <verse eid="ACT 10:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="ACT 10:28"/>Wathi kubo, “Liyakwazi ukuthi kungaphandle komthetho wethu ukuthi umJuda ahlanganyele loweZizwe loba ukuthi amethekelele. Kodwa uNkulunkulu usengitshengisile ukuthi kangingakutsho ukuthi omunye umuntu kahlanzekanga loba ungcolile. <verse eid="ACT 10:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="ACT 10:29"/>Yikho kuthe lapho ngibizwa lapha, ngahle ngeza ngingazange ngibalise lokhu lalokhuyana. Sengibuza-ke manje, ungibizelani?”<verse eid="ACT 10:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="ACT 10:30"/>UKhoneliyasi waphendula wathi, “Ensukwini ezintathu ezedluleyo bengisendlini yami ngikhuleka ngasonalesi isikhathi, ngehola lesithathu emini. Masinyane indoda ebigqoke izigqoko ezikhazimulayo yema phambi kwami, <verse eid="ACT 10:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="ACT 10:31"/>yathi, ‘Khoneliyasi, uNkulunkulu usewuzwile umkhuleko wakho wakhumbula lezipho zakho kwabaswelayo. <verse eid="ACT 10:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="ACT 10:32"/>Thumela ilizwi eJopha ubize uSimoni owaziwa ngokuthi nguPhethro. Wethekelele emzini kaSimoni umtshuki wezikhumba, ohlala malungana lolwandle.’ <verse eid="ACT 10:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="ACT 10:33"/>Yikho ngihle ngathuma abantu kuwe ngokuphangisa, kwaba kuhle ukuthi lawe uze. Manje sonke sesikhona lapha phambi kukaNkulunkulu ukuthi sizwe konke iNkosi ekuyale ukuthi usitshele khona.”<verse eid="ACT 10:33"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="ACT 10:34"/>UPhethro waseqalisa ukukhuluma wathi: “Sengibona khathesi ukuthi ngeqiniso uNkulunkulu kalabandlululo, <verse eid="ACT 10:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="ACT 10:35"/>kodwa wamukela abantu benhlanga zonke abamesabayo, abenza okulungileyo. <verse eid="ACT 10:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="ACT 10:36"/>Yilo leli ilizwi uNkulunkulu alithumela ebantwini bako-Israyeli, elikhuluma ngezindaba ezinhle zokuthula ngoJesu Khristu oyiNkosi yabo bonke. <verse eid="ACT 10:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="ACT 10:37"/>Liyakwazi osekwenzakele kulolonke elaseJudiya, kusukela eGalile ngemva kobhaphathizo olwatshunyayelwa nguJohane, <verse eid="ACT 10:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="ACT 10:38"/>ukuthi uNkulunkulu wamgcoba kanjani uJesu waseNazaretha ngoMoya oNgcwele langamandla, lokuthi wahamba izindawana zonke esenza ubuhle njalo esilisa bonke ababesemandleni omubi, ngoba uNkulunkulu wayelaye.<verse eid="ACT 10:38"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="ACT 10:39"/>Singofakazi bakho konke akwenzayo elizweni lamaJuda laseJerusalema. Bambulala ngokumlengisa esiphambanweni, <verse eid="ACT 10:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="ACT 10:40"/>kodwa uNkulunkulu wamvusa kwabafileyo ngosuku lwesithathu, wakwenza ukuthi abonakale. <verse eid="ACT 10:40"/><verse number="41" style="v" sid="ACT 10:41"/>Kabonwanga ngabantu bonke, kodwa ngofakazi uNkulunkulu ayevele esebakhethile, yithi thina esadla sanatha laye ngemva kokuvuka kwakhe kwabafileyo. <verse eid="ACT 10:41"/><verse number="42" style="v" sid="ACT 10:42"/>Wasilaya ukuba sitshumayele ebantwini bonke njalo sifakaze ukuthi unguye uNkulunkulu ambekayo ukuba ngumahluleli wabaphilayo labafileyo. <verse eid="ACT 10:42"/><verse number="43" style="v" sid="ACT 10:43"/>Bonke abaphrofethi bafakaza ngaye ukuthi bonke abakholwa kuye baphiwa ukuthethelelwa kwezono ngebizo lakhe.”<verse eid="ACT 10:43"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="44" style="v" sid="ACT 10:44"/>UPhethro elokhu esakhuluma amazwi la uMoya oNgcwele wehlela kubo bonke abalizwayo ilizwi. <verse eid="ACT 10:44"/><verse number="45" style="v" sid="ACT 10:45"/>AmaJuda, amakholwa asokiweyo ayeze loPhethro amangaliswa yikuthi uMoya oNgcwele wawuthululelwe lakwabeZizwe. <verse eid="ACT 10:45"/><verse number="46" style="v" sid="ACT 10:46"/>Ngoba babezwa bekhuluma ngendimi bedumisa uNkulunkulu.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="ACT 10:46">UPhethro wasesithi, <verse eid="ACT 10:46"/><verse number="47" style="v" sid="ACT 10:47"/>“Kambe ukhona yini umuntu ongalela abantu laba ukuba babhaphathizwe ngamanzi na? Sebemukele uMoya oNgcwele njengathi.” <verse eid="ACT 10:47"/><verse number="48" style="v" sid="ACT 10:48"/>Wasesithi kababhaphathizwe ebizweni likaJesu Khristu. Basebecela uPhethro ukuthi ahlale labo okwensukwana ezithile.<verse eid="ACT 10:48"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 10"/>
  <chapter number="11" style="c" sid="ACT 11"/>
  <para style="s1">UPhethro Uchaza Ukwenza Kwakhe</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 11:1"/>Abapostoli labazalwane kulolonke elaseJudiya bezwa ukuthi abeZizwe labo basebelamukele ilizwi likaNkulunkulu. <verse eid="ACT 11:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 11:2"/>Yikho kwathi uPhethro esebuyele eJerusalema, amaJuda, amakholwa asokileyo, amsola <verse eid="ACT 11:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 11:3"/>athi, “Wangena endlini yabantu abangasokanga wadla labo.”<verse eid="ACT 11:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 11:4"/>UPhethro wabalondela konke kusukela ekuqaleni, wakuchasisa njengokwenzakala kwakho, wathi, <verse eid="ACT 11:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 11:5"/>“Ngangisedolobheni laseJopha ngikhuleka, ngehlelwa yisiyeziphupho ngaba lombono. Ngabona ulutho olwalunjengelembu elikhulu lisehliselwa phansi ngamagumbi alo womane livela ezulwini, lehlela phansi lapho engangikhona. <verse eid="ACT 11:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 11:6"/>Ngakhangela phakathi kwalo ngabona izinyamazana zomhlaba zezinyawo ezine, izilo zeganga, izinanakazana ezihuquzelayo lezinyoni zemoyeni. <verse eid="ACT 11:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 11:7"/>Ngasengisizwa ilizwi lingitshela lisithi, <char style="wj">‘Vuka Phethro. Hlaba udle.’</char><verse eid="ACT 11:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 11:8"/>Ngaphendula ngathi, ‘Hatshi bo, Nkosi! Kowami umlomo kakukaze kungene ulutho olungahlanzekanga loba olungcolileyo.’<verse eid="ACT 11:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 11:9"/>Ilizwi lakhuluma okwesibili livela ezulwini lathi, <char style="wj">‘Ungabokuthi ulutho oseluhlanjululwe nguNkulunkulu kaluhlanzekanga.’</char> <verse eid="ACT 11:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 11:10"/>Lokhu kwenzakala kathathu, konke kwase kubuyiselwa njalo ezulwini.<verse eid="ACT 11:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 11:11"/>Ngalesosikhathi amadoda amathathu ayethunywe kimi evela eKhesariya afika endlini engangihlala kuyo. <verse eid="ACT 11:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 11:12"/>UMoya wangitshela ukuthi ngingathandabuzi ukuhamba lawo. Laba abazalwane abayisithupha labo bahamba lami sayangena endlini yendoda leyo. <verse eid="ACT 11:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 11:13"/>Yasitshela ukuthi yabona ingilosi endlini yayo isithi, ‘Thumela eJopha ubize uSimoni owaziwa ngokuthi nguPhethro. <verse eid="ACT 11:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 11:14"/>Uzakulethela ilizwi eliyilo elizakusindisa wena kanye lendlu yakho.’<verse eid="ACT 11:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 11:15"/>Kwathi ngiqalisa nje ukukhuluma, uMoya oNgcwele wehlela phezu kwabo njengoba wehlela kithi ekuqaleni. <verse eid="ACT 11:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 11:16"/>Ngakho ngasengikhumbula okwatshiwo yiNkosi isithi, <char style="wj">‘UJohane wabhaphathiza ngamanzi, kodwa lina lizabhaphathizwa ngoMoya oNgcwele.’</char> <verse eid="ACT 11:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 11:17"/>Ngakho-ke, nxa uNkulunkulu wabanika sona lesosipho asinika sona thina esakholwa eNkosini uJesu Khristu, ngangingubani mina engangingakhumbula ukuthi ngingamelana loNkulunkulu na?”<verse eid="ACT 11:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 11:18"/>Bathi sebekuzwile lokhu, kababe besaba lansolo, badumisa uNkulunkulu besithi, “Ngakho-ke, uNkulunkulu usebanikile labo abeZizwe ukuphendukela ekuphileni.”<verse eid="ACT 11:18"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ibandla E-Antiyokhi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 11:19"/>Kwathi labo ababehlakazekile ngenxa yokuhlukunyezwa okwaqala ngokufa kukaStefane bahamba baze bayafika eFenikhiya, leSiphrasi le-Antiyokhi betshumayela ilizwi kumaJuda kuphela. <verse eid="ACT 11:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 11:20"/>Kodwa abanye babo, amadoda ayevela eSiphrasi laseKhureni, aya e-Antiyokhi atshumayela lakumaGrikhi, ebatshela ngezindaba ezinhle ngeNkosi uJesu. <verse eid="ACT 11:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 11:21"/>INkosi yaba labo, ngakho abantu abanengi bakholwa baphendukela eNkosini.<verse eid="ACT 11:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 11:22"/>Ibandla eliseJerusalema lakuzwa lokhu laselithumela uBhanabhasi e-Antiyokhi. <verse eid="ACT 11:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 11:23"/>Ekufikeni kwakhe wazibona izithelo zomusa kaNkulunkulu, wathokoza njalo wabakhuthaza bonke ukuthi baqhubeke ngobuqotho eNkosini ngezinhliziyo zabo zonke. <verse eid="ACT 11:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 11:24"/>Wayeyindoda elungileyo, egcwele uMoya oNgcwele lokukholwa. Abantu abanengi kakhulu balethwa eNkosini.<verse eid="ACT 11:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 11:25"/>UBhanabhasi wasesiya eThasasi ukuyadinga uSawuli. <verse eid="ACT 11:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="ACT 11:26"/>Esemfumene wahamba laye e-Antiyokhi. Ngakho okomnyaka wonke uBhanabhasi loSawuli babehlangana lebandla befundisa abantu abanengi kakhulu. Abafundi baqalisa ukubizwa ngokuthi ngamaKhristu e-Antiyokhi.<verse eid="ACT 11:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="ACT 11:27"/>Ngalesosikhathi abanye abaphrofethi bafika e-Antiyokhi bevela eJerusalema. <verse eid="ACT 11:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="ACT 11:28"/>Omunye wabo owayethiwa ngu-Agabhasi wasukuma eholwa nguMoya wabonisa ukuthi kwakuzakuba lendlala embi eyayizakubakhona kulolonke ilizwe lombuso wamaRoma. (Lokhu kwenzakala ngesikhathi sokubusa kukaKlawudiyasi.) <verse eid="ACT 11:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="ACT 11:29"/>Abafundi bazimisela ukunika usizo kubazalwane ababehlala eJudiya, ngulowo enika ngokwenelisa kwakhe. <verse eid="ACT 11:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="ACT 11:30"/>Bakwenza lokhu, bathumeza izipho zabo ebadaleni ngoBhanabhasi loSawuli.<verse eid="ACT 11:30"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 11"/>
  <chapter number="12" style="c" sid="ACT 12"/>
  <para style="s1">Umangaliso Wokuphuma KukaPhethro Entolongweni</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 12:1"/>Kungaba yisikhathi lapho iNkosi uHerodi eyabopha khona abanye ababe ngabebandla eqonde ukubahlukumeza. <verse eid="ACT 12:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 12:2"/>Wabulalisa uJakhobe umfowabo kaJohane ngenkemba. <verse eid="ACT 12:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 12:3"/>Wathi esebone ukuthi lokho kwakuwathabisa amaJuda, wabopha loPhethro njalo. Lokho kwenzakala ngezinsuku zoMkhosi weSinkwa esingelaMvubelo. <verse eid="ACT 12:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 12:4"/>Esembophile wamphosela entolongweni, wamnikela ukuba alindwe ngamaviyo amane amabutho, ngalinye lilamabutho amane. UHerodi wayefuna ukuthi ngemva kwePhasika amkhuphele obala athonisiswe phambi kwabantu.<verse eid="ACT 12:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 12:5"/>Ngakho uPhethro wagcinwa entolongweni, kodwa ibandla lamkhulekela njalonjalo kuNkulunkulu.<verse eid="ACT 12:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 12:6"/>Ngobusuku obandulela ukuthonisiswa kukaPhethro nguHerodi, uPhethro wayelele ephahlwe ngamabutho amabili, ebotshwe ngamaketane amabili, kumi abalindi emnyango wentolongo. <verse eid="ACT 12:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 12:7"/>Masinyane ingilosi yeNkosi yavela, kwabakhona ukukhanya kulelokamela lentolongo. Yathinta uPhethro ohlangothini, yamvusa yathi, “Phangisa, vuka!” Amaketane akhithika ezingalweni zikaPhethro.<verse eid="ACT 12:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 12:8"/>Ingilosi yasisithi kuye, “Gqoka, ufake lamanyathela akho.” UPhethro wenzenjalo. Ingilosi yamtshela yathi, “Yembatha ijazi lakho ungilandele.” <verse eid="ACT 12:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 12:9"/>UPhethro wayilandela ngaphandle kwentolongo, kodwa wayedidekile engakwazi ukuthi lokho ingilosi eyayikwenza kwakusenzakala ngempela; wayekhumbula ukuthi ubona umbono. <verse eid="ACT 12:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 12:10"/>Bedlula kubalindi, owokuqala lowesibili bafika esangweni lensimbi elaliphumela edolobheni. Lazivulekela baphuma. Kwathi sebehambe baphutsha umgwaqo wedolobho, ingilosi yamtshiya.<verse eid="ACT 12:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 12:11"/>Kwayikhona uPhethro enanzelela, wathi, “Khathesi sengisazi kungelakuthandabuza ukuthi iNkosi ithume ingilosi yayo yangihlenga ezibotshweni zikaHerodi lakukho konke obekufiswa ngamaJuda.”<verse eid="ACT 12:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 12:12"/>Sekumkhanyele kuhle lokhu, waqonda endlini kaMariya unina kaJohane, owayethiwa nguMakho njalo, khona lapho abantu abanengi babebuthene bekhuleka. <verse eid="ACT 12:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 12:13"/>UPhethro waqoqoda entubeni yangaphandle, kwathi incekukazi eyayithiwa nguRoda yayabuza ukuthi ngubani owayesemnyango. <verse eid="ACT 12:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 12:14"/>Isilizwile ilizwi likaPhethro yathaba kakhulu, yagijimela phakathi ingasawuvulanga, yabika yathi, “UPhethro usemnyango!”<verse eid="ACT 12:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 12:15"/>Bathi, “Uyahlanya wena.” Kwathi ngoba wala elokhu ephikelela ukuthi liqiniso, bathi, “Kutsho ukuthi yingilosi yakhe.”<verse eid="ACT 12:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 12:16"/>Kodwa uPhethro wala elokhu eqoqoda, bathi bevula umnyango bambona, bamangala kakhulu. <verse eid="ACT 12:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 12:17"/>UPhethro wabatshengisa ngesandla ukuthi bathule, wasebalandisela ukuthi iNkosi imkhuphe kanjani entolongweni. Wathi, “Libotshela uJakhobe labazalwane ngalokhu.” Wasesuka waya kwenye indawo.<verse eid="ACT 12:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 12:18"/>Ekuseni kwaba lokunyakazela okukhulu phakathi kwabebutho. Babuza bathi, “Kambe ngabe uPhethro wenzenjani?” <verse eid="ACT 12:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 12:19"/>Kwathi uHerodi esemthungathe waze wabeka phansi, wathonisisa abalindi wasesithi kababulawe.</para>
  <para style="s1" vid="ACT 12:19">Ukufa KukaHerodi</para>
  <para style="p" vid="ACT 12:19">UHerodi wasuka eJudiya waya eKhesariya wayahlala khona okwesikhathi esithile. <verse eid="ACT 12:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 12:20"/>Wayekade exabana labantu beThire labeSidoni; basebehlangana ndawonye bacela ukukhuluma laye. Sebezuze ukusekelwa nguBhlastu inceku ethembekileyo enkosini, bacela ukuthula ngoba ukudla kwabo babekuthola elizweni lenkosi.<verse eid="ACT 12:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 12:21"/>Ngosuku olumisiweyo, uHerodi wagqoka izigqoko zobukhosi wahlala esihlalweni sakhe sobukhosi, wasekhuluma ebantwini. <verse eid="ACT 12:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 12:22"/>Bamemeza bathi, “Leli yilizwi likaNkulunkulu, hatshi elomuntu.” <verse eid="ACT 12:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 12:23"/>Masinyane nje, ngenxa yokuthi uHerodi wayengamkhonzi uNkulunkulu, ingilosi yeNkosi yamtshaya yamlahla phansi, wadliwa zimpethu wafa.<verse eid="ACT 12:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 12:24"/>Kodwa ilizwi likaNkulunkulu laqhubeka likhula njalo lisanda.<verse eid="ACT 12:24"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UBhanabhasi loSawuli Bayabuyela</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 12:25"/>Kwathi uBhanabhasi loSawuli sebewuqedile umlandu wabo, babuyela besuka eJerusalema, bahamba loJohane, owayethiwa nguMakho.<verse eid="ACT 12:25"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 12"/>
  <chapter number="13" style="c" sid="ACT 13"/>
  <para style="nb">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 13:1"/>Ebandleni elalise-Antiyokhi kwakulabaphrofethi labafundisi: uBhanabhasi, loSimiyoni owayethiwa nguNigeri, loLusiya waseKhureni, loManayeni (owayekhuliswe loHerodi umbusi) kanye loSawuli. <verse eid="ACT 13:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 13:2"/>Kwathi beyikhonza iNkosi njalo bezilile uMoya oNgcwele wathi, “Ngahlukaniselani uBhanabhasi loSawuli baye emsebenzini engibabizele wona.” <verse eid="ACT 13:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 13:3"/>Ngakho bathi sebezilile njalo sebekhulekile, bababeka izandla babakhupha.<verse eid="ACT 13:3"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Kuyiwa ESiphrasi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 13:4"/>Bonke bobabili baholwa nguMoya oNgcwele, behlela eSelusiya lapho abawela khona ngomkhumbi baya eSiphrasi. <verse eid="ACT 13:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 13:5"/>Bathi sebefikile eSalami, balitshumayela ilizwi likaNkulunkulu emasinagogweni amaJuda. UJohane wayelabo engumsizi wabo.<verse eid="ACT 13:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 13:6"/>Basibhoda sonke isihlenge baze bafika ePhafosi. Khonapho bafumana umJuda oyisanuse, njalo engumphrofethi wamanga owayethiwa nguBha-Jesu, <verse eid="ACT 13:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 13:7"/>wayeyinceku kasibalukhulu, uSegiyasi Phawuli. Usibalukhulu lowo, indoda ekhaliphileyo, yathumela ukuthi kubizwe uBhanabhasi loSawuli ngoba wayefuna ukuzwa ilizwi likaNkulunkulu. <verse eid="ACT 13:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 13:8"/>Kodwa u-Elima isanuse (phela yikho ibizo lakhe elikutshoyo) waphikisana labo wazama ukuphambula usibalukhulu ekukholweni. <verse eid="ACT 13:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 13:9"/>Kwasekusithi uSawuli, owayethiwa njalo nguPhawuli, egcwele uMoya oNgcwele, wamjolozela u-Elima wathi, <verse eid="ACT 13:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 13:10"/>“Wena ungumntakaSathane lesitha sakho konke okulungileyo! Ugcwele zonke inhlobo zenkohliso lokudlelezela. Kawuyikufa wakhawula yini ukuhlinikeza izindlela eziqondileyo? <verse eid="ACT 13:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 13:11"/>Khathesi-ke, isandla seNkosi sizakutshaya. Uzakuba yimpumputhe, awuzukubona ukukhanya kwelanga okwesikhathi esithile.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="ACT 13:11">Masinyane wehlelwa yinkungu lomnyama, waphumputha, waswela umuntu wokumhola ngesandla. <verse eid="ACT 13:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 13:12"/>Kwathi usibalukhulu esekubonile lokho okwakwenzakele wakholwa, ngoba wamangaliswa yimfundiso ngeNkosi.<verse eid="ACT 13:12"/></para>
  <para style="s1">E-Antiyokhi YasePhisidiya</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 13:13"/>Besuka ePhafosi uPhawuli labaphelekezeli bakhe bawela ngomkhumbi baya ePhega esePhamfiliya lapho uJohane abatshiya khona esebuyela eJerusalema. <verse eid="ACT 13:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 13:14"/>Besuka ePhega baya e-Antiyokhi yasePhisidiya. NgeSabatha bangena esinagogweni bahlala phansi. <verse eid="ACT 13:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 13:15"/>Sekubaliwe eMthethweni labaPhrofethi, abaphathi besinagogu bedlulisela ilizwi kubo lisithi, “Bazalwane, nxa lilelizwi lokukhuthaza abantu, khulumani.”<verse eid="ACT 13:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 13:16"/>UPhawuli wasukuma welekelela ngesandla wathi, “Madoda ako-Israyeli kanye lani abeZizwe elimesabayo uNkulunkulu, ngilalelani! <verse eid="ACT 13:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 13:17"/>UNkulunkulu wabantu bako-Israyeli wakhetha okhokho bethu wenza abantu baphumelela ngesikhathi behlezi eGibhithe. Ngamandla amakhulu wabakhupha kulelolizwe <verse eid="ACT 13:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 13:18"/>wababekezelela ekuhambeni kwabo okweminyaka engamatshumi amane besenkangala. <verse eid="ACT 13:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 13:19"/>Wachitha izizwe eziyisikhombisa eKhenani wanika ilizwe lazo abantu bakhe laba yilifa labo. <verse eid="ACT 13:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 13:20"/>Konke lokho kwathatha iminyaka engamakhulu amane lamatshumi amahlanu (450).</para>
  <para style="p" vid="ACT 13:20">Ngemva kwalokhu uNkulunkulu wababekela abahluleli kwaze kwaba yisikhathi sikaSamuyeli umphrofethi. <verse eid="ACT 13:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 13:21"/>Abantu bacela inkosi, wabanika uSawuli indodana kaKhishi, owesizwana sikaBhenjamini, wabusa iminyaka engamatshumi amane. <verse eid="ACT 13:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 13:22"/>Ngemva kokuba esemsusile uSawuli, wabeka uDavida waba yinkosi. Wafakaza ngaye wathi, ‘Sengifumane uDavida indodana kaJese, indoda ethandwa yinhliziyo yami; uzakwenza konke engifuna ukuba akwenze.’<verse eid="ACT 13:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 13:23"/>Esizukulwaneni salindoda uNkulunkulu uselethe ko-Israyeli uMsindisi uJesu njengokuthembisa kwakhe. <verse eid="ACT 13:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 13:24"/>Mandulo kokufika kukaJesu, uJohane watshumayela ukuphenduka lokubhaphathizwa kubo bonke abantu bako-Israyeli. <verse eid="ACT 13:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 13:25"/>UJohane esewuphetha umsebenzi wakhe wathi, ‘Licabanga ukuthi ngingubani na? Kangisuye lowo. Hatshi, kodwa uyeza ngemva kwami, omanyathela akhe akungilingananga ukuthi ngiwathukulule.’<verse eid="ACT 13:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="ACT 13:26"/>Bazalwane, bantwana baka-Abhrahama lani beZizwe elimesabayo uNkulunkulu, lelilizwi lensindiso selithunyelwe kithi. <verse eid="ACT 13:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="ACT 13:27"/>Abantu baseJerusalema kanye lababusi babo kabamamukelanga uJesu, ikanti kwathi ngokumlahla bagcwalisa amazwi abaphrofethi afundwayo ngamaSabatha wonke. <verse eid="ACT 13:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="ACT 13:28"/>Lokuba bengazange bafumane ubufakazi obuqondileyo ukuthi agwetshelwe ukubulawa, bacela uPhilathu ukuthi abulawe. <verse eid="ACT 13:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="ACT 13:29"/>Bathi sebekwenzile konke lokho okwakulotshwe ngaye, bamethula esiphambanweni bamlalisa ethuneni. <verse eid="ACT 13:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="ACT 13:30"/>Kodwa uNkulunkulu wamvusa kwabafileyo, <verse eid="ACT 13:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="ACT 13:31"/>Wabonwa okwensuku ezinengi yilabo abahamba laye besuka eGalile besiya eJerusalema. Manje yibo asebe ngofakazi ebantwini bakithi.<verse eid="ACT 13:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="ACT 13:32"/>Silitshela izindaba ezinhle ukuthi: Lokho uNkulunkulu akuthembisa okhokho bethu <verse eid="ACT 13:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="ACT 13:33"/>usesigcwalisele khona, thina abantwababo, ngokumvusa uJesu kwabafileyo. Njengalokhu kulotshiwe eHubeni lesibili ukuthi:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ACT 13:33">‘UyiNdodana yami;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ACT 13:33">lamhla sengibe nguYihlo.’<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">13.33 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">AmaHubo 2.7</char></note><verse eid="ACT 13:33"/></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="ACT 13:34"/>Lokho ukuthi uNkulunkulu wamvusa kwabafileyo, engasoze abole lanini, kucacisiwe emazwini la:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ACT 13:34">‘Ngizakunika izibusiso ezingcwele eziqinisekileyo ezathenjiswa uDavida.’<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">13.34 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">U-Isaya 55.3</char></note><verse eid="ACT 13:34"/></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="ACT 13:35"/>Kanjalo kulotshiwe kwenye indawo ukuthi:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ACT 13:35">‘Kawusoze wekele oNgcwele wakho abone ukubola.’<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">13.35 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">AmaHubo 16.10</char></note><verse eid="ACT 13:35"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="ACT 13:36"/>Ngoba kwathi uDavida eseyifezile injongo kaNkulunkulu ngalesosikhathi aphila kuso, walala; wangcwatshwa labokhokho bakhe, umzimba wakhe wabola. <verse eid="ACT 13:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="ACT 13:37"/>Kodwa lowo uNkulunkulu amvusayo kwabafileyo kazange akubone ukubola.<verse eid="ACT 13:37"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="ACT 13:38"/>Ngakho-ke, bazalwane bami, ngithanda ukuba lazi ukuthi ngoJesu ukuthethelelwa kwezono kuyatshunyayelwa kini. <verse eid="ACT 13:38"/><verse number="39" style="v" sid="ACT 13:39"/>Ngaye bonke abakholwayo sebehlanjululwe ezonweni zonke abebengeke bahlanjululwe kuzo ngomthetho kaMosi. <verse eid="ACT 13:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="ACT 13:40"/>Qaphelani ukuthi lokho okwakhulunywa ngabaphrofethi kungenzakali kini, ukuthi:<verse eid="ACT 13:40"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="41" style="v" sid="ACT 13:41"/>‘Khangelani, lina bachothozi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ACT 13:41">mangalani libhubhe,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ACT 13:41">ngoba ensukwini zenu ngizakwenza into</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ACT 13:41">elingasoze liyikholwe</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ACT 13:41">lanxa kube lalingakutshelwa ngubani.’<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">13.41 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">UHabhakhukhi 1.5</char></note>”<verse eid="ACT 13:41"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="42" style="v" sid="ACT 13:42"/>Kwathi uPhawuli loBhanabhasi sebesuka esinagogweni abantu babacela ukuthi babuye bazokhuluma njalo ngalezizinto ngeSabatha elilandelayo. <verse eid="ACT 13:42"/><verse number="43" style="v" sid="ACT 13:43"/>Abantu sebechithekile amaJuda amanengi lamakholwa ayephendukele enkolweni yesiJuda balandela uPhawuli loBhanabhasi, bona bakhuluma labo bebakhuthaza ukuthi baqhubeke bebambelele emuseni kaNkulunkulu.<verse eid="ACT 13:43"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="44" style="v" sid="ACT 13:44"/>NgeSabatha elilandelayo phose lonke idolobho labuthana ukuzakuzwa ilizwi leNkosi. <verse eid="ACT 13:44"/><verse number="45" style="v" sid="ACT 13:45"/>Kwathi amaJuda ebona amaxuku abantu, aba lomona, akhuluma ehlambaza lokho okwakutshiwo nguPhawuli.<verse eid="ACT 13:45"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="46" style="v" sid="ACT 13:46"/>UPhawuli loBhanabhasi basebewaphendula ngesibindi bathi, “Bekumele silikhulume kini ilizwi likaNkulunkulu kuqala. Kodwa njengoba lililahla ngoba lizibona lina lingakufanelanga ukuphila okungapheliyo, khathesi sesiphendukela kwabeZizwe. <verse eid="ACT 13:46"/><verse number="47" style="v" sid="ACT 13:47"/>Phela nanku iNkosi esisiyale khona yathi:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ACT 13:47">‘Sengilenze isibane sabeZizwe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ACT 13:47">ukuthi lilethe insindiso emikhawulweni yomhlaba.’<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">13.47 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">U-Isaya 49.6</char></note>”<verse eid="ACT 13:47"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="48" style="v" sid="ACT 13:48"/>Kwathi abeZizwe bekuzwa lokhu bathaba, balidumisa ilizwi leNkosi; kwathi bonke ababemiselwe ukuphila okungapheliyo bakholwa.<verse eid="ACT 13:48"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="49" style="v" sid="ACT 13:49"/>Ilizwi leNkosi landa umango wonke. <verse eid="ACT 13:49"/><verse number="50" style="v" sid="ACT 13:50"/>Kodwa amaJuda athela umoya omubi kwabesifazane abahlonitshwayo ababekholwa lamadoda ayengabakhokheli bedolobho. Akhwezela ukuhlukuluzwa kukaPhawuli loBhanabhasi, abaxotsha emangweni wakibo. <verse eid="ACT 13:50"/><verse number="51" style="v" sid="ACT 13:51"/>Ngakho bathintitha uthuli ezinyaweni zabo njengesixwayiso, baqonda e-Ikhoniyamu. <verse eid="ACT 13:51"/><verse number="52" style="v" sid="ACT 13:52"/>Abafundi bagcwala ngentokozo langoMoya oNgcwele.<verse eid="ACT 13:52"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 13"/>
  <chapter number="14" style="c" sid="ACT 14"/>
  <para style="s1">E-Ikhoniyamu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 14:1"/>E-Ikhoniyamu uPhawuli loBhanabhasi baya esinagogweni yamaJuda njengenjayelo yabo. Khonapho bakhuluma kwazwela kwaze kwathi amaJuda amanengi lamaGrikhi akholwa. <verse eid="ACT 14:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 14:2"/>Kodwa amaJuda ayengafuni ukukholwa adunga abeZizwe, abathela umoya omubi ngabazalwane. <verse eid="ACT 14:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 14:3"/>UPhawuli loBhanabhasi bahlala isikhathi eside khona lapho bekhulumela iNkosi ngesibindi. INkosi yaqinisa ilizwi lomusa wayo ngokubapha amandla okwenza imimangaliso lezimanga. <verse eid="ACT 14:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 14:4"/>Abantu bedolobho lelo badabukana phakathi; abanye bema lamaJuda, kwathi abanye basekela abapostoli. <verse eid="ACT 14:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 14:5"/>AbeZizwe lamaJuda ndawonye labakhokheli babo bakha icebo lokubahlukumeza lokubakhanda ngamatshe. <verse eid="ACT 14:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 14:6"/>Kodwa balizwa icebo lelo basebebalekela emadolobheni aseLikhawoniya, eListra leDebhe lasemangweni yakhona, <verse eid="ACT 14:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 14:7"/>lapho abaqhubeka khona ukutshumayela izindaba ezinhle.<verse eid="ACT 14:7"/></para>
  <para style="s1">EListra LaseDebhe</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 14:8"/>EListra kwakulendoda eyayiyisigoga ikwazi ukuhlala kuphela, ilokhu yazalwayo ingakaze ihambe. <verse eid="ACT 14:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 14:9"/>Yamlalela uPhawuli lapho ekhuluma. UPhawuli wayijolozela wabona ukuthi yayikholwa ukuba ingasiliswa <verse eid="ACT 14:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 14:10"/>wasememeza wathi, “Sukuma ngezinyawo zakho!” Ngalokho indoda yathi lothu yahle yahamba.<verse eid="ACT 14:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 14:11"/>Kwathi ixuku labantu selikubonile okwakwenziwe nguPhawuli, lamemeza ngolimi lwesiLikhawoniya lathi, “Onkulunkulu sebehlele kithi belesimo sabantu!” <verse eid="ACT 14:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 14:12"/>UBhanabhasi bambiza bathi nguZewusi, uPhawuli bathi nguHemesi ngoba nguye owayekhokhela ekukhulumeni. <verse eid="ACT 14:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 14:13"/>Umphristi kaZewusi owayelethempeli eduze ngaphandle kwedolobho, waletha inkunzi lemigaxo emasangweni edolobho ngoba yena kanye lexuku labantu babefuna ukwenza imihlatshelo kubo.<verse eid="ACT 14:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 14:14"/>Kodwa kwathi abapostoli, uBhanabhasi loPhawuli bekuzwa lokhu, badabula izigqoko zabo bazithela phakathi kwabantu bememeza besithi: <verse eid="ACT 14:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 14:15"/>“Madoda, likwenzelani lokhu? Lathi singabantu njengani. Sililethela izindaba ezinhle, silitshela ukuthi litshiye izinto lezi eziyize liye kuNkulunkulu ophilayo owenza amazulu lomhlaba, lolwandle lakho konke okukuwo. <verse eid="ACT 14:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 14:16"/>Endulo waziyekela izizwe zonke zahamba ngezindlela zazo. <verse eid="ACT 14:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 14:17"/>Ikanti kazange ekele ukuzifakazela: Utshengisile umusa ngokulipha izulu laphezulu lamabele ngesikhathi sawo; ulipha ukudla okunengi njalo agcwalise inhliziyo zenu ngentokozo.” <verse eid="ACT 14:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 14:18"/>Loba sebetsho lamazwi baba lobunzima ukuthi bekelise abantu bonke ukuba babenzele umhlatshelo.<verse eid="ACT 14:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 14:19"/>Kwasekufika amaJuda evela e-Antiyokhi lase-Ikhoniyamu afika adunga abantu. UPhawuli bamkhanda ngamatshe bamhudulela ngaphandle kwedolobho, becabanga ukuthi wayesefile. <verse eid="ACT 14:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 14:20"/>Kodwa ngemva kokuba abafundi sebembuthanele, waphaphama wabuyela edolobheni. Ngosuku olulandelayo yena loBhanabhasi basuka baya eDebhe.<verse eid="ACT 14:20"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Babuyela E-Antiyokhi Ese-Asiriya</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 14:21"/>Bazitshumayela izindaba ezinhle kulelodolobho bazuza inani elikhulu labafundi. Basebebuyela eListra, le-Ikhoniyamu le-Antiyokhi <verse eid="ACT 14:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 14:22"/>beqinisa abafundi njalo bebakhuthaza ukuthi babambelele ekukholweni. Bathi, “Kufanele sedlule ezinhlungwini ezinengi ukuze singene embusweni kaNkulunkulu.” <verse eid="ACT 14:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 14:23"/>UPhawuli loBhanabhasi babakhethela abadala kulelo lalelo bandla, babanikela eNkosini ngomkhuleko langokuzila ngoba bebeke ithemba labo kuyo iNkosi. <verse eid="ACT 14:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 14:24"/>Sebehambe bedlula ePhisidiya, bafika ePhamfiliya, <verse eid="ACT 14:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 14:25"/>kwathi sebetshumayele ilizwi ePhega basebesiya e-Athaliya.<verse eid="ACT 14:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="ACT 14:26"/>Besuka e-Athaliya bawela ngomkhumbi babuyela e-Antiyokhi, lapho ababenikelwe khona emuseni kaNkulunkulu ukwenza umsebenzi lowo abasebewufezile. <verse eid="ACT 14:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="ACT 14:27"/>Ekufikeni kwabo khona, balihlanganisa ndawonye ibandla balibikela konke lokho uNkulunkulu ayekwenzile ngabo, lokuthi wayesevulele abeZizwe umnyango wokukholwa. <verse eid="ACT 14:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="ACT 14:28"/>Bahlala khona isikhathi eside labafundi.<verse eid="ACT 14:28"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 14"/>
  <chapter number="15" style="c" sid="ACT 15"/>
  <para style="s1">Umhlangano Omkhulu EJerusalema</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 15:1"/>Amadoda athile eza e-Antiyokhi evela eJudiya, afika afundisa abazalwane esithi: “Ngaphandle kokuthi lisokwe ngendlela yomkhuba eyafundiswa nguMosi lingeke lisindiswe.” <verse eid="ACT 15:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 15:2"/>Lokhu kwenza uPhawuli loBhanabhasi baphikisana labo kakhulu. Ngakho uPhawuli loBhanabhasi bakhethwa kanye lamanye amakholwa ukuthi baye eJerusalema ukuyabona abapostoli labadala ngaloludaba. <verse eid="ACT 15:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 15:3"/>Ibandla labavalelisa. Bathi bedabula eFenikhiya leSamariya balandisa ngokuthi abeZizwe basebephendukile. Indaba le yathokozisa bonke abazalwane. <verse eid="ACT 15:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 15:4"/>Bafika eJerusalema bemukelwa kuhle libandla langabapostoli labadala, bababikela konke uNkulunkulu ayekwenzile ngabo.<verse eid="ACT 15:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 15:5"/>Kwasekusithi amanye amakholwa ayengawoluhlu lwabaFarisi asukuma athi, “AbeZizwe kumele basokwe njalo batshelwe ukuthi balandele umthetho kaMosi.”<verse eid="ACT 15:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 15:6"/>Abapostoli labadala bahlangana bakhuluma ngalindaba. <verse eid="ACT 15:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 15:7"/>Ngemva kokuphikisana okukhulu uPhethro wasukuma wakhuluma kubo wathi: “Bazalwane, liyakwazi ukuthi esikhathini esedluleyo uNkulunkulu wangikhetha phakathi kwenu ukuthi abeZizwe bezwe kwezami izindebe ilizwi levangeli bakholwe. <verse eid="ACT 15:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 15:8"/>UNkulunkulu owazi inhliziyo watshengisa ukuthi uyabemukela ngokubapha uMoya oNgcwele, njengalokhu akwenzayo kithi. <verse eid="ACT 15:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 15:9"/>Kenzanga umahluko phakathi kwethu labo, ngoba wahlanza inhliziyo zabo ngokukholwa. <verse eid="ACT 15:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 15:10"/>Pho-ke lizamelani ukulinga uNkulunkulu ngokwethesa abafundi beZizweni ijogwe thina labokhokho bethu esehluleka ukulithwala? <verse eid="ACT 15:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 15:11"/>Hatshi! Sikholwa ukuthi sisindiswa ngomusa weNkosi uJesu, njengabo labo.”<verse eid="ACT 15:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 15:12"/>Wonke umhlangano wathula zwi balalela uBhanabhasi loPhawuli belandisa ngemimangaliso lezimanga uNkulunkulu ayezenzile kwabeZizwe ngabo. <verse eid="ACT 15:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 15:13"/>Bathi sebeqedile uJakhobe wakhuluma wathi: “Bazalwane, ake lingilalele. <verse eid="ACT 15:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 15:14"/>USimoni usesilandisele ngokuthi ekuqaleni uNkulunkulu watshengisa njani ukunakekela kwakhe abeZizwe ngokukhetha phakathi kwabo abantu ukuba babe ngabakhe. <verse eid="ACT 15:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 15:15"/>Amazwi abaphrofethi ayavumelana lalokhu, njengalokhu kulotshiwe ukuthi:<verse eid="ACT 15:15"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 15:16"/>‘Ngemva kwalokhu ngizabuya</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ACT 15:16">ngakhe kutsha indlu kaDavida ewileyo.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ACT 15:16">Amanxiwa ayo ngizawavuselela,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ACT 15:16">njalo ngizayimisa kutsha,<verse eid="ACT 15:16"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 15:17"/>ukwenzela ukuthi lonke uluntu luyidinge iNkosi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ACT 15:17">kanye labeZizwe abaziwa ngebizo lami,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ACT 15:17">kutsho iNkosi eyenza lezizinto’<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">15.17 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">U-Amosi 9.11-12</char></note>:<verse eid="ACT 15:17"/></para>
  <para style="q2">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 15:18"/>ezivele zisaziwa kusukela endulo.<verse eid="ACT 15:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 15:19"/>Ngokubona kwami, kakumelanga sikwenze kube lukhuni kwabeZizwe abaphendukela kuNkulunkulu. <verse eid="ACT 15:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 15:20"/>Esikhundleni salokho, kasibalobeleni sibatshele ukuthi baxwaye ukudla okungcoliswe yizithombe, lokuhlobonga, lenyama yenyamazana ekhanyiweyo lobubende. <verse eid="ACT 15:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 15:21"/>Phela uMosi sekwatshunyayelwa ngaye kuwo wonke amadolobho kusukela ekuqaleni njalo kufundwa ngaye emasinagogweni amaSabatha wonke.”<verse eid="ACT 15:21"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Incwadi Yomhlangano Omkhulu Kumakholwa AbeZizwe</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 15:22"/>Abapostoli labadala kanye lebandla lonke bamisa ukukhetha abanye babo ukuthi babathume e-Antiyokhi loPhawuli loBhanabhasi. Bakhetha uJudasi owayethiwa nguBhasabhasi, loSayilasi, la engamadoda amabili ayengabakhokheli kubazalwane. <verse eid="ACT 15:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 15:23"/>Babaphathisa incwadi le:</para>
  <para style="pmo" vid="ACT 15:23">Abapostoli labadala, abazalwane benu,</para>
  <para style="pmo" vid="ACT 15:23">KwabeZizwe abakholwayo e-Antiyokhi, lase-Asiriya laseSilisiya:</para>
  <para style="pmo" vid="ACT 15:23">Siyalibingelela.<verse eid="ACT 15:23"/></para>
  <para style="pm">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 15:24"/>Sesizwile ukuthi bakhona abasuka kithi bengelamvumo yethu bafika balidunga, bedida ingqondo zenu ngalokho ababekutsho. <verse eid="ACT 15:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 15:25"/>Ngakho sivumelene sonke ukukhetha amadoda athile ukuthi siwathumele kini labangane bethu abathandekayo, uBhanabhasi loPhawuli, <verse eid="ACT 15:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="ACT 15:26"/>amadoda adele impilo zawo ngenxa yebizo leNkosi yethu uJesu Khristu. <verse eid="ACT 15:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="ACT 15:27"/>Ngakho sithumela uJudasi loSayilasi ukugcwalisa ngomlomo lokhu esikulobayo. <verse eid="ACT 15:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="ACT 15:28"/>Kubonakale kufanele kuMoya oNgcwele lakithi ukuthi singalethesi omthwalo omkhulu ngaphandle kwezimiso lezi: <verse eid="ACT 15:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="ACT 15:29"/>Xwayani ukudla okunikelwe ezithombeni, ububende, inyama yenyamazana ekhanyiweyo kanye lokuhlobonga. Lizabe lenze kuhle nxa lizixwaya lezizinto.</para>
  <para style="pmc" vid="ACT 15:29">Salani kuhle.<verse eid="ACT 15:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="ACT 15:30"/>Bawavalelisa amadoda ahamba aya e-Antiyokhi, lapho afika ahlanganisa ibandla ndawonye ethula incwadi. <verse eid="ACT 15:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="ACT 15:31"/>Abantu bayibala bathokoza ngenxa yamazwi ayo akhuthazayo. <verse eid="ACT 15:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="ACT 15:32"/>UJudasi loSayilasi, bona ngokwabo ababengabaphrofethi, bakhuluma okunengi ukukhuthaza lokuqinisa abazalwane. <verse eid="ACT 15:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="ACT 15:33"/>Sebehlale isikhathi esithile khonapho, abazalwane babavalelisa ngesibusiso sokuthula sebebuyela kulabo ababathumayo. [<verse eid="ACT 15:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="ACT 15:34"/>Kodwa uSayilasi wakhetha ukusala khona.]<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">15.34 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Livesi ayikho kwamanye amaBhayibhili esiLungu.</char></note> <verse eid="ACT 15:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="ACT 15:35"/>Kodwa uPhawuli loBhanabhasi basala e-Antiyokhi, lapho bona kanye labanye abanengi bafundisa njalo batshumayela ilizwi leNkosi.<verse eid="ACT 15:35"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukungavumelani KukaPhawuli LoBhanabhasi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="ACT 15:36"/>Emva kwesikhatshanyana uPhawuli wathi kuBhanabhasi, “Kasibuyele emuva siyebona abazalwane emadolobheni wonke esitshumayele khona ilizwi leNkosi ukuthi baqhuba njani.” <verse eid="ACT 15:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="ACT 15:37"/>UBhanabhasi wayefuna ukuthi bahambe loJohane, owayethiwa nguMakho, <verse eid="ACT 15:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="ACT 15:38"/>kodwa uPhawuli wakubona kungafanele ukuhamba laye ngoba wayeke wabafulathela besePhamfiliya kaze aqhubeka labo emsebenzini. <verse eid="ACT 15:38"/><verse number="39" style="v" sid="ACT 15:39"/>Baphikisana kakubi baze bacina betshiyana. UBhanabhasi wamthatha uMakho bawelela eSiphrasi, <verse eid="ACT 15:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="ACT 15:40"/>kodwa uPhawuli wakhetha ukuhamba loSayilasi, basuka bebekwe ngabazalwane emuseni weNkosi. <verse eid="ACT 15:40"/><verse number="41" style="v" sid="ACT 15:41"/>Wahamba phakathi kwe-Asiriya leSilisiya eqinisa amabandla.<verse eid="ACT 15:41"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 15"/>
  <chapter number="16" style="c" sid="ACT 16"/>
  <para style="s1">UThimothi Usebenza LoPhawuli LoSayilasi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 16:1"/>Wafika eDebhe wedlulela eListra lapho okwakuhlala khona umfundi owayethiwa nguThimothi, olonina owaye ngumJudakazi, elikholwa, kodwa uyise engumGrikhi. <verse eid="ACT 16:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 16:2"/>Abazalwane baseListra lase-Ikhoniyamu babemncoma. <verse eid="ACT 16:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 16:3"/>UPhawuli wayefuna ukuhamba laye, ngakho wasemsoka ngenxa yamaJuda akuleyondawo ngoba bonke babekwazi ukuthi uyise wayengumGrikhi. <verse eid="ACT 16:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 16:4"/>Ekuhambeni kwabo kulelo lalelodolobho, babezethula izinqumo ezenziwa ngabapostoli labadala eJerusalema ukuze abantu bazilandele. <verse eid="ACT 16:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 16:5"/>Ngakho amabandla aqiniswa ekukholweni abantu banda mihla yonke.<verse eid="ACT 16:5"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Umbono KaPhawuli Ngendoda YeMasedoniya</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 16:6"/>UPhawuli labaphelekezeli bakhe bayibhoda yonke imango yaseFirigiya laseGalathiya, uMoya oNgcwele esemalele ukuthi atshumayele ilizwi edolobheni lase-Ezhiya. <verse eid="ACT 16:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 16:7"/>Bathi sebefike emngceleni waseMisiya, bazama ukungena eBhithiniya, kodwa uMoya kaJesu kawubavumelanga. <verse eid="ACT 16:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 16:8"/>Ngakho bedlula eceleni kweMisiya behlela eTrowasi. <verse eid="ACT 16:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 16:9"/>Ebusuku uPhawuli wehlelwa ngumbono wendoda yaseMasedoniya imi imncenga isithi, “Woza eMasedoniya uzosisiza.” <verse eid="ACT 16:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 16:10"/>UPhawuli esebone umbono lowo, sahle salungisa masinyane ukuthi siye eMasedoniya, sibona ukuthi uNkulunkulu wayesibizile ukuba sitshumayele ivangeli kubo.<verse eid="ACT 16:10"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukuphenduka KukaLidiya EFiliphi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 16:11"/>Sasuka eTrowasi sawela ulwandle santsheza saqonda eSamathrake, ngosuku olulandelayo sedlulela eNiyapholi. <verse eid="ACT 16:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 16:12"/>Sesisuka lapho saya eFiliphi, elaliyilona idolobho elikhulu lesiqinti seMasedoniya eyayibuswa ngamaRoma. Sahlala lapho okwensuku ezinengi.<verse eid="ACT 16:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 16:13"/>NgeSabatha saphumela ngaphandle kwamasango omuzi saya emfuleni sifuna indawo yokukhuleka. Sahlala phansi saqalisa ukukhuluma labesifazane ababebuthene khonapho. <verse eid="ACT 16:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 16:14"/>Omunye walabo ababelalele ngowesifazane owayethiwa nguLidiya, umthengisi welembu eliyibubende evela edolobheni laseThiyathira, ekhonza uNkulunkulu. INkosi yayivula inhliziyo yakhe ukuba emukele ilizwi likaPhawuli. <verse eid="ACT 16:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 16:15"/>Kwathi yena kanye labendlu yakhe sebebhaphathiziwe, wasinxusela emzini wakhe. Wathi, “Nxa lingemukela njengekholwa eNkosini, wozani lizohlala endlini yami.” Wasincenga savuma.<verse eid="ACT 16:15"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UPhawuli LoSayilasi Entolongweni</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 16:16"/>Ngelinye ilanga sathi sisiya endaweni yokukhuleka sahlangana lentombazana eyayiyisigqili, ilomoya wobungoma. Yayizuzela abanini bayo imali enengi ngalokho kuhlahlula. <verse eid="ACT 16:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 16:17"/>Intombazana le yalandela uPhawuli lathi sonke imemeza isithi, “Amadoda la ayizinceku zikaNkulunkulu oPhezukonke, alitshela indlela yokusindiswa.” <verse eid="ACT 16:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 16:18"/>Yakwenza lokhu okwensuku ezinengi. Ekucineni uPhawuli kwamcaphula lokho waphenduka wathi kuwo umoya, “Ngiyakulaya ngebizo likaJesu Khristu ukuthi uphume kuyo!” Umoya wahle waphuma kuyo khonapho.<verse eid="ACT 16:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 16:19"/>Abanikazi bentombazana bathi ngokunanzelela ukuthi ithemba labo lokuzuza imali laselinyamalele, bababamba, uPhawuli loSayilasi babadonsela enkundleni yokuthengisa ukuba bayeqondana leziphathamandla. <verse eid="ACT 16:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 16:20"/>Babamisa phambi kwabomantshi bathi, “Amadoda la angamaJuda asedunge idolobho lakithi <verse eid="ACT 16:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 16:21"/>ngokukhuthaza imikhuba engaphandle komthetho ukuthi thina amaRoma siyamukele kumbe siyilandele.”<verse eid="ACT 16:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 16:22"/>Ixuku layingenela indaba yokuhlasela uPhawuli loSayilasi, ngakho omantshi bathi kabakhululwe izigqoko batshaywe. <verse eid="ACT 16:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 16:23"/>Sebebatshaye kabuhlungu babaphosela entolongweni kwathiwa umlindijele abakhangele aqinisise. <verse eid="ACT 16:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 16:24"/>Esezwe lowomlayo wabafuqela endlini yentolongo ephakathi wababopha inyawo, wazibophela ensikeni.<verse eid="ACT 16:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 16:25"/>Sekungaba phakathi kwamabili ebusuku uPhawuli loSayilasi bakhuleka bahlabela amahubo kuNkulunkulu, ezinye izibotshwa zibalalele. <verse eid="ACT 16:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="ACT 16:26"/>Masinyane kwaba lokuzamazama komhlaba kwaze kwanyikinyeka lezisekelo zentolongo. Izivalo zentolongo zathi gwabu zavuleka, amaketane ezibotshwa athukuluka. <verse eid="ACT 16:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="ACT 16:27"/>Umlindijele waphaphama, wathi ngokubona iminyango yentolongo ivulekile, wakhokha inkemba yakhe esefuna ukuzibulala ngoba ekhumbula ukuthi izibotshwa zasezibalekile. <verse eid="ACT 16:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="ACT 16:28"/>Kodwa uPhawuli wamemeza wathi, “Ungazilimazi bo! Sikhona sonke!”<verse eid="ACT 16:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="ACT 16:29"/>Umlindijele wathi kakulethwe izibane, wangena wazilahla phambi kukaPhawuli loSayilasi eqhaqhazela. <verse eid="ACT 16:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="ACT 16:30"/>Wasebakhuphela phandle wababuza wathi, “Madoda, ngenzeni ukuze ngisindiswe na?”<verse eid="ACT 16:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="ACT 16:31"/>Baphendula bathi, “Kholwa eNkosini uJesu, uzasindiswa; wena kanye lendlu yakho.” <verse eid="ACT 16:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="ACT 16:32"/>Basebemtshumayeza ngelizwi leNkosi kanye labanye abendlu yakhe. <verse eid="ACT 16:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="ACT 16:33"/>Ngalelohola lebusuku umlindijele wabathatha wabagezisa imvimvinya zabo; kwasekusithi khonokho nje yena labendlu yakhe bahle babhaphathizwa. <verse eid="ACT 16:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="ACT 16:34"/>Umlindijele wahamba labo endlini yakhe, wabapha ukudla. Indlu yakhe yonke yaba lokuthokoza ngoba basebekholwa kuNkulunkulu.<verse eid="ACT 16:34"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="ACT 16:35"/>Kwathi sokusile, omantshi bathuma amanxusa abo kumlindijele lomlayo othi: “Bakhulule abantu labo.” <verse eid="ACT 16:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="ACT 16:36"/>Umlindijele watshela uPhawuli wathi, “Omantshi sebethe wena loSayilasi likhululwe. Selingahamba. Lihambe ngokuthula.”<verse eid="ACT 16:36"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="ACT 16:37"/>Kodwa uPhawuli wathi emanxuseni: “Basibhaxabule phambi kwabantu singazange sithonisiswe thina singamaRoma agcweleyo, basiphosela entolongweni. Kanti manje sebefuna ukusikhupha ngasese na? Hatshi! Kababuye bona ngokwabo bazesikhupha.”<verse eid="ACT 16:37"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="ACT 16:38"/>Amanxusa akubika lokhu kubomantshi abathi ngokuzwa ukuthi uPhawuli loSayilasi babengamaRoma agcweleyo, bethuka. <verse eid="ACT 16:38"/><verse number="39" style="v" sid="ACT 16:39"/>Beza ukuzabancenga, babakhupha entolongweni, babacela ukuthi basuke kulelodolobho. <verse eid="ACT 16:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="ACT 16:40"/>UPhawuli loSayilasi sebephumile entolongweni baya endlini kaLidiya lapho abahlangana khona labazalwane babaqinisa. Basebesuka bahamba.<verse eid="ACT 16:40"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 16"/>
  <chapter number="17" style="c" sid="ACT 17"/>
  <para style="s1">EThesalonika</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 17:1"/>Bathi sebedlule e-Amfipholi le-Apholoniya, bafika eThesalonika lapho okwakulesinagogu yamaJuda khona. <verse eid="ACT 17:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 17:2"/>Njengenjayelo yakhe uPhawuli waya esinagogweni, kwathi ngamaSabatha amathathu wabonisana labo ngeMibhalo, <verse eid="ACT 17:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 17:3"/>echaza njalo eveza obala ukuthi uKhristu wayemele ahlupheke njalo avuke kwabafileyo. Wathi, “UJesu lo engitshumayela ngaye kini unguye uKhristu.” <verse eid="ACT 17:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 17:4"/>Amanye amaJuda akukholwa lokho asehlanganyelana loPhawuli loSayilasi, njengalokho okwenziwa linani elikhulu lamaGrikhi abesaba uNkulunkulu, kugoqela lehlekanyana labesifazane abahloniphekayo.<verse eid="ACT 17:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 17:5"/>Kodwa amaJuda aba lomona; ngakho asehuga izixhwali endaweni yokuthengisa, abalixuku elithile asevusa umsindo edolobheni. Aphuthumela endlini kaJasoni edinga uPhawuli loSayilasi efuna ukubaletha phambi kukazulu. <verse eid="ACT 17:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 17:6"/>Kodwa kwathi sebebaswele basebedonsela uJasoni labanye abazalwane abathile kubaphathi bedolobho bememeza besithi: “Amadoda la abekade edala uhlupho emhlabeni wonke manje aseze lapha, <verse eid="ACT 17:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 17:7"/>uJasoni yena wawemukela endlini yakhe. Bonke bahlinikeza imithetho kaKhesari besithi kulenye inkosi ethiwa nguJesu.” <verse eid="ACT 17:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 17:8"/>Bathi bekuzwa lokhu abantu labaphathi bedolobho bazonda kakhulu. <verse eid="ACT 17:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 17:9"/>Kwasekuthiwa uJasoni labanye bakhe kabakhuphe isibambiso ngemali ethile, kwayikhona bekhululwa ukuthi bahambe.<verse eid="ACT 17:9"/></para>
  <para style="s1">EBheriya</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 17:10"/>Konela ukuthi kuhlwe abazalwane babasusa uPhawuli loSayilasi babasa eBheriya. Ekufikeni kwabo khona baya esinagogweni yamaJuda. <verse eid="ACT 17:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 17:11"/>AmaJuda eBheriya wona ayelesimilo esingcono kulaleso esamaThesalonika, ngoba alemukela ilizwi ngomfutho omkhulu njalo ayihlola iMibhalo insuku zonke ukuze abone ukuthi lokho uPhawuli ayekutsho kwakuliqiniso na. <verse eid="ACT 17:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 17:12"/>AmaJuda amanengi akholwa, kanye labesifazane abanengi bamaGrikhi abahloniphekayo lamadoda amanengi amaGrikhi.<verse eid="ACT 17:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 17:13"/>Kwathi amaJuda aseThesalonika esezwile ukuthi uPhawuli wayesetshumayela ilizwi likaNkulunkulu eBheriya, aya khona futhi, athela abantu umoya omubi abadunga. <verse eid="ACT 17:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 17:14"/>Abazalwane bahle bathumela uPhawuli ngasokhunjini lolwandle, kodwa uSayilasi loThimothi basala eBheriya. <verse eid="ACT 17:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 17:15"/>Amadoda ayephelekezela uPhawuli amtshiya e-Athene asebuyela lomlayezo wokuthi uSayilasi loThimothi bamlandele ngokuphangisa.<verse eid="ACT 17:15"/></para>
  <para style="s1">E-Athene</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 17:16"/>UPhawuli esabamelele e-Athene, wakhathazeka kakhulu ngokubona ukuthi idolobho lelo laligcwele izithombe. <verse eid="ACT 17:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 17:17"/>Ngakho wabonisana lamaJuda kanye lamaGrikhi ayemesaba uNkulunkulu esinagogweni lasendaweni yokuthengisa zonke insuku lalabo ababekhonapho. <verse eid="ACT 17:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 17:18"/>Ixuku lezazi zama-Ephikhuri lamaStoyikhi laphikisana laye. Abanye babo babuza bathi, “Uwumani lolu luzama ukuthini kanti?” Abanye bathi, “Kungathi utshumayela ngonkulunkulu bezizweni.” Bakutsho lokhu ngoba uPhawuli wayetshumayela izindaba ezinhle ngoJesu langokuvuka kwabafileyo. <verse eid="ACT 17:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 17:19"/>Basebehamba laye enkundleni ye-Ariyophagasi, bafika bathi kuye, “Ake usitshele ukuthi imfundiso le entsha oyethulayo iyini. <verse eid="ACT 17:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 17:20"/>Uletha ezindlebeni zethu imibono engajayelekanga, ngakho sifuna ukwazi ukuthi itshoni.” <verse eid="ACT 17:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 17:21"/>(Wonke ama-Atheni labezizwe ababehlala khona babechitha isikhathi sabo bengenzi lutho ngaphandle kokukhuluma lokulalela imibono emitsha.)<verse eid="ACT 17:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 17:22"/>UPhawuli wasukuma enkundleni ye-Ariyophagasi wathi, “Madoda ase-Atheni! Ngiyabona ukuthi kukho konke lingabantu abakhonzayo. <verse eid="ACT 17:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 17:23"/>Ngoba ngithe ngihambahamba, ngabona izithombe zenu, ngaze ngafumana i-alithari elilombhalo othi:</para>
  <para style="pc" vid="ACT 17:23">Kunkulunkulu Ongaziwayo.</para>
  <para style="m" vid="ACT 17:23">Manje-ke lokho elikukhonza njengolutho olungaziwayo yikho engizakutshumayela kini.<verse eid="ACT 17:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 17:24"/>UNkulunkulu owenza umhlaba lakho konke okukuwo uyiNkosi yezulu lomhlaba, njalo kahlali emathempelini akhiwe ngezandla. <verse eid="ACT 17:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 17:25"/>Njalo kancediswa yizandla zabantu ingathi kukhona akuswelayo, ngoba yena ngokwakhe upha bonke abantu impilo, umphefumulo lokunye konke. <verse eid="ACT 17:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="ACT 17:26"/>Ngomuntu oyedwa wenza zonke izizwe zabantu, ukuthi zakhe emhlabeni wonke; njalo wamisa izikhathi abazilungiselweyo lazo kanye izindawo abamele bahlale kuzo. <verse eid="ACT 17:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="ACT 17:27"/>UNkulunkulu wakwenza lokhu ukuze abantu bamdinge lokuthi mhlawumbe bamfinyelele bamfumane, loba nje uvele engakhatshana komunye lomunye wethu. <verse eid="ACT 17:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="ACT 17:28"/>‘Ngoba siphila kuye, sihambe ngaye njalo sipheleliswe nguye.’ Njengokutsho kwezinye izimbongi zakini ukuthi, ‘Singabantwabakhe.’<verse eid="ACT 17:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="ACT 17:29"/>Ngakho-ke njengoba singabantwana bakaNkulunkulu, kasingacabangini ukuthi ubuNkulunkulu bunjengegolide, loba isiliva kumbe ilitshe; umfanekiso obunjwe ngobungcitshi bomuntu. <verse eid="ACT 17:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="ACT 17:30"/>Endulo uNkulunkulu kakunakanga ukungazi lokhu, kodwa khathesi uselaya bonke abantu ezindaweni zonke ukuba baphenduke. <verse eid="ACT 17:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="ACT 17:31"/>Ngoba uselumisile usuku lapho azakwahlulela khona umhlaba ngokulunga ngaye umuntu amkhethileyo. Usebuvezile ubufakazi balokhu kubo bonke abantu ngokumvusa kwabafileyo.”<verse eid="ACT 17:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="ACT 17:32"/>Bathi besizwa ngokuvuka kwabafileyo, abanye babo bamklolodela, kodwa abanye bathi, “Sifuna ukuphinda sikuzwe ukhuluma ngale indaba njalo.” <verse eid="ACT 17:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="ACT 17:33"/>Ngalokho-ke, uPhawuli wasesuka enkundleni. <verse eid="ACT 17:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="ACT 17:34"/>Abantu abathile baba ngabalandeli bakaPhawuli, bakholwa. Phakathi kwabo kwakuloDiyonisiyu owayelilunga le-Ariyophagasi, njalo lowesifazane okwakuthiwa nguDamari kanye labanye abalinani elithile.<verse eid="ACT 17:34"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 17"/>
  <chapter number="18" style="c" sid="ACT 18"/>
  <para style="s1">EKhorinte</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 18:1"/>Ngemva kwalokho uPhawuli wasuka e-Athene waya eKhorinte. <verse eid="ACT 18:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 18:2"/>Khonapho wahlangana lomJuda owayethiwa ngu-Akhwila, owasePhontusi ngomdabuko, owayesanda kufika lapho evele e-Ithali lomkakhe uPhrisila ngoba uKlawudiyasi wayekhuphe isinqumo sokuthi amaJuda wonke aphume eRoma. UPhawuli wahamba wayababona, <verse eid="ACT 18:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 18:3"/>kwathi ngoba engumenzi wamathente njengabo wasehlala labo, wasebenza labo. <verse eid="ACT 18:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 18:4"/>NgamaSabatha wonke wayesiya esinagogweni ebonisana lamaJuda lamaGrikhi ezama ukuwaphendula.<verse eid="ACT 18:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 18:5"/>Kwathi uSayilasi loThimothi sebefikile bevela eMasedoniya, uPhawuli wasenikela isikhathi sakhe sonke ekutshumayeleni kuphela efakaza kumaJuda ukuthi uJesu wayenguKhristu. <verse eid="ACT 18:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 18:6"/>Kodwa kwathi lapho amaJuda emphikisa njalo emchothoza, wathintitha izembatho zakhe phambi kwawo wathi, “Igazi lenu kalibe phezu kwamakhanda enu! Mina sengiwenzile owami umlandu. Kusukela manje sengisiya kwabeZizwe.”<verse eid="ACT 18:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 18:7"/>UPhawuli wasesuka esinagogweni waya endlini eseceleni, eyayingekaThithu Justusi, owayekhonza uNkulunkulu. <verse eid="ACT 18:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 18:8"/>UKhrispasi, umphathi wesinagogu, kanye lendlu yakhe yonke bakholwa eNkosini; kwathi labanengi bamaKhorinte abamuzwayo bakholwa, babhaphathizwa.<verse eid="ACT 18:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 18:9"/>Ngobunye ubusuku iNkosi yakhuluma kuPhawuli ngombono yathi: <char style="wj">“Ungesabi; qhubeka utshumayela, ungathuli.</char> <verse eid="ACT 18:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 18:10"/><char style="wj">Ngoba mina ngilawe, kakho ozakuhlasela akulimaze, ngoba ngilabantu abanengi kulelidolobho.”</char> <verse eid="ACT 18:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 18:11"/>Ngakho uPhawuli wahlala khona okomnyaka olengxenye, ebafundisa ilizwi likaNkulunkulu.<verse eid="ACT 18:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 18:12"/>UGaliyo esangusibalukhulu wase-Akhayiya, amaJuda eKhorinte amanyana ahlasela uPhawuli, amletha emthethwandaba, <verse eid="ACT 18:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 18:13"/>amangalela esithi, “Indoda le idonsela abantu ekukhonzeni uNkulunkulu ngezindlela eziphambene lomthetho.”<verse eid="ACT 18:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 18:14"/>Kwathi uPhawuli esathi uyakhuluma, uGaliyo wathi kumaJuda, “Kube lina maJuda libika ngokona okuthile loba icala lokuganga okubi, bekufanele ukuthi ngililalele. <verse eid="ACT 18:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 18:15"/>Kodwa njengoba kuphathelane ngezinto zamazwi lamabizo, langomthetho wenu; kulungiseni lina. Mina kangiyikuba ngumahluleli wezinto ezinjalo.” <verse eid="ACT 18:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 18:16"/>Wasesithi kabaxotshwe enkantolo. <verse eid="ACT 18:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 18:17"/>Bonke basebephendukela uSosithene, umphathi wesinagogu, bamtshaya phambi kwenkantolo. Kodwa uGaliyo kazange athi thiki lakancane.<verse eid="ACT 18:17"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UPhrisila Lo-Akhwila Lo-Apholo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 18:18"/>UPhawuli waphinda wahlala njalo okwesikhathi esithile eKhorinte. Wasetshiya abazalwane waya e-Asiriya, ephelekezelwa nguPhrisila lo-Akhwila. Engakaweli ulwandle waqala wagela inwele zakhe eKhenkireya ngenxa yesifungo ayesenzile. <verse eid="ACT 18:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 18:19"/>Bafika e-Efesu lapho uPhawuli atshiya khona uPhrisila lo-Akhwila. Yena waya esinagogweni wayabonisana lamaJuda. <verse eid="ACT 18:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 18:20"/>Bamcela ukuthi ahlale okwesikhathi eside kodwa wala. <verse eid="ACT 18:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 18:21"/>Wathi esesuka wathembisa wathi, “Ngizaphenduka nxa kuyintando kaNkulunkulu.” Wasewela ulwandle esuka e-Efesu. <verse eid="ACT 18:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 18:22"/>Wakhuphukela eKhesariya wahamba wayabingelela ibandla eJerusalema, wasesehlela e-Antiyokhi.<verse eid="ACT 18:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 18:23"/>UPhawuli eseke wahlala e-Antiyokhi wasuka lapho wabhoda indawo ngendawo kuwo wonke umango waseGalathiya lowaseFirigiya eqinisa bonke abafundi.<verse eid="ACT 18:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 18:24"/>Kusenjalo, umJuda owayethiwa ngu-Apholo, owe-Alekizandriya ngomdabuko, weza e-Efesu. Wayeyindoda efundileyo, elolwazi olukhulu ngeMibhalo. <verse eid="ACT 18:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 18:25"/>Yayifundisiwe ngendlela yeNkosi, ikhuluma ngomfutho njalo ifundisa okuqondileyo ngoJesu, isazi ngobhaphathizo lukaJohane kuphela. <verse eid="ACT 18:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="ACT 18:26"/>Yakhuluma ngesibindi esinagogweni. Kwathi uPhrisila lo-Akhwila beyizwa, bayinxusa emzini wabo, bayichazela ngokugcweleyo indlela kaNkulunkulu.<verse eid="ACT 18:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="ACT 18:27"/>U-Apholo wayefuna ukuya e-Akhayiya, abazalwane basebemkhuthaza, babhalela abafundi khonale ukuthi bamamukele. Wathi efika khona waba luncedo olukhulu kulabo ababekholwe beholwa ngumusa. <verse eid="ACT 18:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="ACT 18:28"/>Ngoba watshukana lamaJuda ewaphikisa enkundleni, ebonisa obala eMibhalweni ukuthi uJesu wayenguKhristu.<verse eid="ACT 18:28"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 18"/>
  <chapter number="19" style="c" sid="ACT 19"/>
  <para style="s1">UPhawuli E-Efesu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 19:1"/>Kwathi u-Apholo eseKhorinte uPhawuli wathatha indlela ehamba phakathi kwelizwe waze wayafika e-Efesu. Khonapho wafumana abafundi abathile, <verse eid="ACT 19:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 19:2"/>wababuza wathi, “Lamamukela na uMoya oNgcwele ngesikhathi liqalisa ukukholwa?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="ACT 19:2">Baphendula bathi, “Hatshi, kasizwanga lokuzwa ukuthi kuloMoya oNgcwele.”<verse eid="ACT 19:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 19:3"/>Ngakho uPhawuli wasebuza wathi, “Pho lathola luphi ubhaphathizo?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="ACT 19:3">Baphendula bathi, “Ubhaphathizo lukaJohane.”<verse eid="ACT 19:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 19:4"/>UPhawuli wathi, “Ubhaphathizo lukaJohane lwalulubhaphathizo lokuphenduka. Watshela abantu ukuthi bakholwe kulowo owayezakuza ngemva kwakhe, esitsho ukuthi kuJesu.” <verse eid="ACT 19:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 19:5"/>Sebekuzwile lokhu babhaphathizelwa ebizweni leNkosi uJesu. <verse eid="ACT 19:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 19:6"/>UPhawuli esebeke izandla zakhe phezu kwabo uMoya oNgcwele wehlela kubo, bakhuluma ngendimi njalo baphrofitha. <verse eid="ACT 19:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 19:7"/>Babengamadoda ayengaba litshumi lambili bebonke.<verse eid="ACT 19:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 19:8"/>UPhawuli wangena esinagogweni wakhuluma ngesibindi khona okwezinyanga ezintathu, echaza okusuthisayo ngombuso kaNkulunkulu. <verse eid="ACT 19:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 19:9"/>Kodwa abanye babo baba yiziqholo; bala ukukholwa, bakhuluma kubi obala ngeNdlela. Ngakho uPhawuli wabatshiya. Wathatha abafundi wasuka wayahlangana labo baxoxisana nsuku zonke esikolweni sikaThiranu. <verse eid="ACT 19:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 19:10"/>Lokhu kwaqhubeka okweminyaka emibili, kwaze kwathi wonke amaJuda lamaGrikhi ayehlala kulesosifunda sase-Ezhiya alizwa ilizwi leNkosi.<verse eid="ACT 19:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 19:11"/>UNkulunkulu wenza imimangaliso engajayelekanga ngoPhawuli, <verse eid="ACT 19:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 19:12"/>izifinyo lamathawulo okwakuthintiswe kuye kwakusiwa kwabagulayo bahle basile emikhuhlaneni yabo lemimoya emibi iphume kubo.<verse eid="ACT 19:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 19:13"/>Amanye amaJuda ayebhoda exotsha imimoya emibi azama ukubiza ibizo leNkosi uJesu kulabo ababelamadimoni. Ayesithi, “Ngebizo likaJesu uPhawuli atshumayela ngaye, ngikulaya ukuthi uphume.” <verse eid="ACT 19:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 19:14"/>Ababesenza lokhu ngamadodana ayisikhombisa kaSkeva umphristi omkhulu wamaJuda. <verse eid="ACT 19:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 19:15"/>Kwelinye ilanga umoya omubi waphendula wathi, “UJesu ngiyamazi, loPhawuli ngiyamazi, kodwa lina lingobani na?” <verse eid="ACT 19:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 19:16"/>Kwasekusithi indoda eyayilomoya omubi yabeqela, yabehlula bonke. Yabatshaya okuzwayo baze baphuma endlini bebaleka benqunu njalo besopha igazi.<verse eid="ACT 19:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 19:17"/>Kwathi lokhu sekuzwakele kumaJuda lamaGrikhi ayehlala e-Efesu, onke ethuka ngokwesaba, ibizo leNkosi uJesu laselihlonitshwa kakhulu. <verse eid="ACT 19:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 19:18"/>Abanengi balabo abasebekholwa beza baphumela egcekeni, bevuma iziphambeko zabo. <verse eid="ACT 19:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 19:19"/>Abanengi ababehlahlula baletha ndawonye imiqulu yabo bayitshisa obala. Bathi sebehlolile izindleko zaleyomiqulu kwabonakala kungaba ngamadrakhima azinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amahlanu. <verse eid="ACT 19:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 19:20"/>Ngaleyondlela ilizwi leNkosi landa kabanzi njalo lakhula laba lamandla.<verse eid="ACT 19:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 19:21"/>Ngemva kwakho konke lokhu sekwenzakele, uPhawuli wazimisela ukuya eJerusalema, ezadlula eMasedoniya lase-Akhayiya. Wathi, “Nxa sengike ngaya khona, kuzamele ngethekelele laseRoma.” <verse eid="ACT 19:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 19:22"/>Wathuma ababili abasizi bakhe eMasedoniya, uThimothi lo-Erastu, yena esasele okwesikhatshana esifundeni sase-Ezhiya.<verse eid="ACT 19:22"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Isiyaluyalu E-Efesu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 19:23"/>Ngalesosikhathi kwaba lokudungeka okukhulu ngeNdlela. <verse eid="ACT 19:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 19:24"/>Umkhandi wesiliva owayethiwa nguDemetriyasi owayesenza izikhonzelo zokukhonzela u-Athemisi ngesiliva, wayengenisa imali ezwayo kubakhandi. <verse eid="ACT 19:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 19:25"/>Wababizela ndawonye kanye lezinye izisebenzi zemisebenzi efananayo wathi kubo, “Madoda, liyakwazi ukuthi sizuza imali enengi ngomsebenzi lo. <verse eid="ACT 19:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="ACT 19:26"/>Liyabona njalo liyezwa ukuthi uPhawuli lo usenze abantu abanengi bakholwa njalo uzadukisa abantu abanengi lapha e-Efesu lakuso sonke isifunda sase-Ezhiya. Uthi yena onkulunkulu ababunjwe ngumuntu kabasibo onkulunkulu lakancinyane. <verse eid="ACT 19:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="ACT 19:27"/>Kulengozi-ke yokuthi kakuyikuba ngumsebenzi wethu kuphela ozalahlekelwa libizo lawo elihle, kodwa lethempeli likankulunkulukazi omkhulu u-Athemisi lizadunyazwa, laye unkulunkulukazi ngokwakhe, yena okhonzwa kusosonke isifunda sase-Ezhiya lasemhlabeni wonke, uzakwemukwa ubukhosi bakhe.”<verse eid="ACT 19:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="ACT 19:28"/>Bathi bekuzwa lokhu bafuthelana ngokuzonda, bahle bamemeza besithi, “Mkhulu u-Athemisi wama-Efesu!” <verse eid="ACT 19:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="ACT 19:29"/>Masinyane nje idolobho lonke laphithizela. Abantu badumela uGayiyasi lo-Aristakhasi ababe ngabaphelekezeli bakaPhawuli, bengabeMasedoniya, babahudulela enkundleni yemidlalo bonke bayakuthi cwi khona. <verse eid="ACT 19:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="ACT 19:30"/>UPhawuli wayefuna ukuzithela emphakathini, kodwa abafundi bamalela. <verse eid="ACT 19:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="ACT 19:31"/>Labanye abaphathi besifunda, ababengabangane bakaPhawuli, labo bamthumela ilizwi bathi angaqali ukuyavela enkundleni yemidlalo.<verse eid="ACT 19:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="ACT 19:32"/>Kwakungasaqondakali enkundleni: Abanye babeklabalala besitsho lokhu, abanye labo besitsho okunye. Abantu abanengi babevele bengazi lokuthi babelandeni lapho. <verse eid="ACT 19:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="ACT 19:33"/>AmaJuda afuqela u-Alekizanda phambili esithi kawakhulumele. Waphakamisa isandla ukuwathulisa ukuze achasise kuhle indaba ebantwini. <verse eid="ACT 19:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="ACT 19:34"/>Kodwa athi ngokunanzelela ukuthi wayengumJuda, onke ahlaba umkhosi kanyekanye okwaphose kwathatha amahola amabili, besithi, “Mkhulu u-Athemisi wama-Efesu!”<verse eid="ACT 19:34"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="ACT 19:35"/>Unobhala wedolobho walithulisa ixuku wathi, “Madoda ase-Efesu, akusikho yini ukuthi umhlaba wonke uyakwazi ukuthi idolobho lase-Efesu yilo elingumlondolozi wethempeli lika-Athemisi omkhulu, kanye lomfanekiso wakhe owehla uvela ezulwini? <verse eid="ACT 19:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="ACT 19:36"/>Pho-ke njengoba lokhu kuyinto engaphikiswayo, thulani lingenzi izinto zamawala. <verse eid="ACT 19:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="ACT 19:37"/>Selilethe amadoda la lapha, kodwa wona engagqekezanga emathempelini kumbe athuka unkulunkulukazi wethu. <verse eid="ACT 19:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="ACT 19:38"/>Ngakho nxa uDemetriyasi lalabo akhanda labo belensolo loba ngobani, imithethwandaba ivuliwe, njalo labahluleli bakhona. Bangamangala. <verse eid="ACT 19:38"/><verse number="39" style="v" sid="ACT 19:39"/>Nxa kukhona njalo okunye elifuna ukukutsho, kakuyethoniswa ngomthetho enkundleni. <verse eid="ACT 19:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="ACT 19:40"/>Njengoba kunje nje sisengozini yokubekwa icala lokuvusa isiyaluyalu ngenxa yezehlakalo zalamuhla. Kungenzeka lokho sizakwehluleka ukuchaza imbangela yalesisiphithiphithi, ngoba ngempela kungekho sizatho.” <verse eid="ACT 19:40"/><verse number="41" style="v" sid="ACT 19:41"/>Eqeda kukhuluma lokhu, wawuchitha umhlangano.<verse eid="ACT 19:41"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 19"/>
  <chapter number="20" style="c" sid="ACT 20"/>
  <para style="s1">Udlula EMasedoniya LaseGrisi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 20:1"/>Kwathi umsindo usuphelile uPhawuli wabiza abafundi, wathi esebaqinisile wabavalelisa waqonda eMasedoniya. <verse eid="ACT 20:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 20:2"/>Wahamba wadabula kulowomango, ekhuluma amazwi amanengi okukhuthaza abantu, wacina esefike eGrisi <verse eid="ACT 20:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 20:3"/>lapho ahlala khona okwezinyanga ezintathu. AmaJuda abumba icebo ngaye eselungele ukuwela aye e-Asiriya yikho wacabanga ukuthi abuyele ngendlela yaseMasedoniya. <verse eid="ACT 20:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 20:4"/>Wayephelekezelwa nguSophatha indodana kaPhirusi waseBheriya, lo-Aristakhasi, loSekhundu waseThesalonika, loGayiyasi waseDebhe, loThimothi laye, kwasekusiba nguThikhikhasi loThrofimasi abesifunda sase-Ezhiya. <verse eid="ACT 20:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 20:5"/>Amadoda la asandulela ayasimelela eTrowasi. <verse eid="ACT 20:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 20:6"/>Kodwa sawela ulwandle sisuka eFiliphi ngemva koMkhosi weSinkwa esingelaMvubelo, kwathi ngemva kwensuku ezinhlanu sahlangana labanye eTrowasi lapho esahlala khona insuku eziyisikhombisa.<verse eid="ACT 20:6"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UYuthikhasi Uvuswa Ekufeni ETrowasi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 20:7"/>Ngosuku lokuqala lweviki sahlangana ukuhlephuna isinkwa. UPhawuli watshumayela ebantwini, kwathi ngoba efuna ukusuka kusisa, wakhuluma kwaze kwaba phakathi kobusuku. <verse eid="ACT 20:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 20:8"/>Endlini ephezulu lapho esasihlanganele khona kwakulezibane ezinengi. <verse eid="ACT 20:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 20:9"/>Kwakulejaha elalithiwa nguYuthikhasi lihlezi ewindini, labanjwa yibuthongo uPhawuli elokhu ekhuluma engaqedi. Lathi selijumekile, lawela phansi lisuka esitezi sesithathu labuthwa selifile. <verse eid="ACT 20:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 20:10"/>UPhawuli wehla, wazilahla phezu kwejaha lelo waligona wathi, “Lingethuki, liyaphila!” <verse eid="ACT 20:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 20:11"/>Wasebuyela phezulu esitezi wahlephuna isinkwa wadla. Esekhulume kwaze kwasa, wasuka. <verse eid="ACT 20:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 20:12"/>Abantu balisa ekhaya ijaha liphila, bona baduduzeka kakhulu.<verse eid="ACT 20:12"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UPhawuli Uvalelisa Abadala Base-Efesu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 20:13"/>Sathungamela ukuya emkhunjini sagwedla sisiya e-Asosi lapho esasizathatha khona uPhawuli awele lathi. Lokhu wayekulungiselele ngoba wayezahamba ngenyawo esiya khonale. <verse eid="ACT 20:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 20:14"/>Wathi ngokuhlangana lathi e-Asosi samngenisa saqonda eMithilene. <verse eid="ACT 20:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 20:15"/>Ngosuku olulandelayo sawela sisuka lapho sayafika eKhiyosi. Kwathi ngosuku olulandelayo sachaphela eSamosi, ngosuku olulandelayo sayafika eMilethusi. <verse eid="ACT 20:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 20:16"/>UPhawuli wayezimisele ukuwela edlule eceleni kwe-Efesu engafuni ukuchitha isikhathi esifundeni sase-Ezhiya, ngoba wayejahe ukuyafika eJerusalema, nxa kusenzeka kube ngosuku lwePhentekhosti.<verse eid="ACT 20:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 20:17"/>EseMilethusi uPhawuli wathumela ilizwi e-Efesu ebiza abadala bebandla. <verse eid="ACT 20:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 20:18"/>Sebefikile wathi kubo, “Liyakwazi ukuthi ngaphila njani ngesikhathi sonke ngilani, kusukela ngosuku engafika ngalo esifundeni sase-Ezhiya. <verse eid="ACT 20:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 20:19"/>Ngayikhonza iNkosi ngokuzithoba okukhulu langezinyembezi, loba ngangilingwa kabuhlungu ngamacebo amaJuda. <verse eid="ACT 20:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 20:20"/>Liyakwazi ukuthi kangizange ngithikaze ukutshumayela loba yikuphi obekungaba luncedo kini kodwa ngalifundisa obala njalo ngingena izindlu ngezindlu. <verse eid="ACT 20:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 20:21"/>Ngitshumayele kumaJuda lakumaGrikhi ukuthi kumele baphendukele kuNkulunkulu ngokuphenduka, bakholwe eNkosini yethu uJesu.<verse eid="ACT 20:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 20:22"/>Okwamanje ngiqhutshwa nguMoya ukuthi ngiye eJerusalema loba ngingazi ukuthi kuzakwenzakalani kimi khonale. <verse eid="ACT 20:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 20:23"/>Ngazi kuphela ukuthi kuwo wonke amadolobho uMoya oNgcwele ungixwayisa ukuthi ukubotshwa lobunzima kungimelele. <verse eid="ACT 20:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 20:24"/>Kodwa eyami impilo ngiyibona ingasilutho kimi, injongo yami emqoka yikuqeda loluhambo lokufeza lumsebenzi engiwuphiwe yiNkosi uJesu, umsebenzi wokufakaza ivangeli lomusa kaNkulunkulu.<verse eid="ACT 20:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 20:25"/>Khathesi ngiyazi ukuthi kakho kini engihambe ngitshumayela khona umbuso ozaphinda angibone futhi. <verse eid="ACT 20:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="ACT 20:26"/>Ngakho ngiyafakaza kini lamuhla ukuthi kangilacala ngegazi labantu bonke. <verse eid="ACT 20:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="ACT 20:27"/>Ngoba kangingabazanga ukutshumayela kini yonke intando kaNkulunkulu. <verse eid="ACT 20:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="ACT 20:28"/>Zigcineni lina kanye lawo wonke umhlambi uMoya oNgcwele olenze laba ngabathungameli. Wobani ngabelusi bebandla likaNkulunkulu, owalithenga ngegazi lakhe. <verse eid="ACT 20:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="ACT 20:29"/>Ngiyazi ukuthi nxa sengisukile lapha, impisi eziphangayo zizakuza phakathi kwenu ziwungenele umhlambi. <verse eid="ACT 20:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="ACT 20:30"/>Laphakathi kwenu kuzavela abantu abazalihlanekela iqiniso ukuze abanye abafundi babalandele. <verse eid="ACT 20:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="ACT 20:31"/>Ngakho lihlale liqaphele! Khumbulani ukuthi okweminyaka emithathu kangizange ngiphumule ukuxwayisa omunye lomunye wenu ubusuku lemini ngezinyembezi.<verse eid="ACT 20:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="ACT 20:32"/>Khathesi ngilinikela kuNkulunkulu laselizwini lomusa wakhe elilamandla okulakha lokulipha ilifa phakathi kwabo bonke abangcwelisiweyo. <verse eid="ACT 20:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="ACT 20:33"/>Kangihawukelanga siliva samuntu, loba igolide kumbe izembatho. <verse eid="ACT 20:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="ACT 20:34"/>Lina ngokwenu liyakwazi ukuthi izandla zami lezi zagcwalisa zonke izinswelo zami lezabakhula bami. <verse eid="ACT 20:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="ACT 20:35"/>Kukho konke engakwenzayo ngalibonisa ukuthi ngalindlela yokusebenza nzima kumele sisize ababuthakathaka, sikhumbula amazwi eNkosi uJesu athi, <char style="wj">‘Kubusiseke kakhulu ukupha ukwedlula ukwamukela.’</char> ”<verse eid="ACT 20:35"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="ACT 20:36"/>Esekutshilo lokhu waguqa phansi kanye labo bonke, wakhuleka. <verse eid="ACT 20:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="ACT 20:37"/>Bonke bakhala lapho bemgona lokumanga. <verse eid="ACT 20:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="ACT 20:38"/>Okwabadanisa kakhulu kwaba yilizwi lakhe lokuthi babengasayikuphinde babubone njalo ubuso bakhe. Basebemphelekezela emkhunjini.<verse eid="ACT 20:38"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 20"/>
  <chapter number="21" style="c" sid="ACT 21"/>
  <para style="s1">Ukuya EJerusalema</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 21:1"/>Sathi sesizehlukanise kubo ngobuhlungu, sawela ulwandle saqonda nta eKhosi. Ngosuku olulandelayo saya eRodi, sasuka khona saya ePhathara. <verse eid="ACT 21:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 21:2"/>Safumana umkhumbi owawuchaphela eFenikhiya, sangena kuwo, sahamba. <verse eid="ACT 21:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 21:3"/>Sayithi tshazi iSiphrasi, sedlula ngeningizimu kwayo, saya e-Asiriya. Sakhuphukela eThire lapho umkhumbi wethu wawuzakwethula khona umthwalo wawo. <verse eid="ACT 21:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 21:4"/>Safumana abafundi khona, sahlala labo insuku eziyisikhombisa. Baholwa nguMoya ukuthi bamncenge uPhawuli ukuthi angayi eJerusalema. <verse eid="ACT 21:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 21:5"/>Kodwa isikhathi sethu sesifikile, sasuka saqhubeka ngohambo lwethu. Bonke abafundi lamakhosikazi abo kanye labantwana basiphelekezela basikhupha edolobheni, safika okhunjini saguqa sakhuleka. <verse eid="ACT 21:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 21:6"/>Sesivalelisene, sangena emkhunjini, bona babuyela emakhaya.<verse eid="ACT 21:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 21:7"/>Saqhubeka ngohambo lwethu sisuka eThire sayakhuphukela ePhetholemayi, lapho sabingelela abazalwane, sahlala labo usuku lonke. <verse eid="ACT 21:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 21:8"/>Sasuka ngelanga elilandelayo safika eKhesariya sayahlala endlini kaFiliphu umvangeli, engomunye wabayisiKhombisa. <verse eid="ACT 21:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 21:9"/>Wayelamadodakazi amane angendanga njalo ephrofitha.<verse eid="ACT 21:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 21:10"/>Sesihlale insuku ezimbalwa kwafika umphrofethi owayethiwa ngu-Agabhasi evela eJudiya. <verse eid="ACT 21:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 21:11"/>Weza kithi, wathatha ibhanti likaPhawuli, wazibopha izandla lezinyawo zakhe ngalo, wathi, “UMoya oNgcwele uthi, ‘Ngayonale indlela amaJuda aseJerusalema azabopha umninibhanti leli abesemnikela kwabeZizwe.’ ”<verse eid="ACT 21:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 21:12"/>Sathi sikuzwa lokhu sonke labantu bakhonapho sancengana loPhawuli ukuthi angayi eJerusalema. <verse eid="ACT 21:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 21:13"/>UPhawuli waphendula wathi, “Likhalelani lingidabula inhliziyo yami na? Kangilungelanga ukubotshwa kuphela, kodwa lokufa eJerusalema ngifela ibizo leNkosi uJesu.” <verse eid="ACT 21:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 21:14"/>Kwathi ngoba engancengeki sadela sathi, “Mayenzeke intando yeNkosi.”<verse eid="ACT 21:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 21:15"/>Ngemva kwalokhu, salungisa sasesisiya eJerusalema. <verse eid="ACT 21:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 21:16"/>Abafundi abathile abaseKhesariya basiphelekezela basisa emzini kaMnasoni lapho esasizahlala khona. Wayeyindoda edabuka eSiphrasi, engomunye wabafundi bakuqala.<verse eid="ACT 21:16"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukufika KukaPhawuli EJerusalema</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 21:17"/>Ekufikeni kwethu eJerusalema abazalwane basamukela ngokuthokoza. <verse eid="ACT 21:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 21:18"/>Ngosuku olulandelayo uPhawuli lathi sonke sahamba ukuyabona uJakhobe, bonke abadala babekhona. <verse eid="ACT 21:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 21:19"/>UPhawuli wababingelela, wabika ngokugcweleyo konke uNkulunkulu ayekwenzile kwabeZizwe ngokusebenza kwakhe.<verse eid="ACT 21:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 21:20"/>Bathi sebekuzwile lokhu bamdumisa uNkulunkulu. Ngakho basebesithi kuPhawuli, “Uyabona mzalwane ukuthi izinkulungwane ezinengi zamaJuda sezikholiwe njalo wonke atshisekela umlayo. <verse eid="ACT 21:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 21:21"/>Sebetshelwe ukuthi wena ufundisa wonke amaJuda ahlala phakathi kwabeZizwe ukuthi afulathele uMosi, ubatshela ukuthi angasoki abantwababo lokuthi angalandeli amasiko ethu. <verse eid="ACT 21:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 21:22"/>Pho senzeni? Ngeqiniso bazakuzwa ukuthi usufikile, <verse eid="ACT 21:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 21:23"/>ngakho yenza lokhu esikutshela khona. Kulamadoda amane phakathi kwethu asenze isifungo. <verse eid="ACT 21:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 21:24"/>Hamba lawo amadoda la, ubambisane lawo emkhutsheni wokuzihlambulula, uwabhadalele izindleko zawo zakhona ukuze aphuce amakhanda awo. Ngakho umuntu wonke uzakwazi ukuthi akulaqiniso kulimibiko ngawe, kodwa babone ukuthi wena ngokwakho uphila ngokulandela umlayo. <verse eid="ACT 21:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 21:25"/>AbeZizwe bona abakholwayo sesibalobele ngesinqumo sethu ukuthi kabaxwaye ukudla okunikelwe ezithombeni, bangadli ububende, lenyama yenyamazana ekhanyiweyo lokuhlobonga.”<verse eid="ACT 21:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="ACT 21:26"/>Ngosuku olulandelayo uPhawuli wawathatha lawomadoda wayazihlambulula kanye lawo. Wasesiya ethempelini ukuyakwazisa ngosuku lokuphela kwensuku zokuhlambulula lokuthi umnikelo walowo lalowo wabo wawuzakwenziwa nini.<verse eid="ACT 21:26"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UPhawuli Uyabotshwa</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="ACT 21:27"/>Kwathi lezinsuku eziyisikhombisa sezizaphela, amaJuda athile esifunda sase-Ezhiya abona uPhawuli ethempelini. Alidunga lonke ixuku ambamba <verse eid="ACT 21:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="ACT 21:28"/>ehlaba umkhosi esithi, “Madoda ako-Israyeli; sibambiseni! Yiyo le indoda efundisa abantu bonke ezindaweni zonke okuphambene labantu bakithi lomlayo wakithi kanye lendawo le. Ngaphandle kwalokho, usengenise amaGrikhi emagumeni ethempeli wangcolisa indawo le eNgcwele.” <verse eid="ACT 21:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="ACT 21:29"/>(Mandulo babebone uThrofimasi wase-Efesu edolobheni eloPhawuli basebekhumbula ukuthi uPhawuli wayeze laye emagumeni ethempeli.)<verse eid="ACT 21:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="ACT 21:30"/>Idolobho lonke laphithizela, abantu beza begijima beqhamuka inxa zonke. Bamdumela uPhawuli bamhudula bemsusa ethempelini, amasango alo ahle avalwa. <verse eid="ACT 21:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="ACT 21:31"/>Bathi besazama ukumbulala, umbiko wafika kumlawuli wamabutho amaRoma ukuthi idolobho lonke laseJerusalema laseliphithizela. <verse eid="ACT 21:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="ACT 21:32"/>Khonokho nje wathatha abanye abaphathi kanye lamabutho wagijimela esiphithiphithini leso. Kwathi labo ababevusa uthuli bebona umlawuli lamabutho akhe bema ukutshaya uPhawuli.<verse eid="ACT 21:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="ACT 21:33"/>Umlawuli weza wafika wambopha wathi kabotshwe ngamaketane amabili. Wasembuza ukuthi wayengubani lokuthi wayoneni. <verse eid="ACT 21:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="ACT 21:34"/>Abathile exukwini bamemeza lokhu, abanye bamemeza okunye, kwasekusithi ngoba umlawuli engalizwa iqiniso ngenxa yokuxokozela waselaya ukuthi uPhawuli kasiwe enkambeni yamabutho. <verse eid="ACT 21:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="ACT 21:35"/>Esefikile ezinyathelweni zokuqansela endlini, abantu baphithizela ngamandla waze wathwalwa ngamabutho. <verse eid="ACT 21:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="ACT 21:36"/>Ixuku elalilandela laphikelela limemeza lisithi, “Msusele amanqe!”<verse eid="ACT 21:36"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UPhawuli Ukhuluma Lexuku Labantu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="ACT 21:37"/>Amabutho esathi amngenisa ngaphakathi, uPhawuli wacela kumlawuli wathi, “Ngingaba lelizwi lawe na?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="ACT 21:37">Yena waphendula wathi, “Uyasikhuluma yini isiGrikhi? <verse eid="ACT 21:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="ACT 21:38"/>Kawusuye yini umGibhithe owaqala umvukela, wakhokhela izinkulungwane ezine zamathekulambuso enkangala?”<verse eid="ACT 21:38"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="ACT 21:39"/>UPhawuli waphendula wathi, “NgingumJuda waseThasasi eSilisiya, isakhamuzi sedolobho elihloniphekayo. Ngicela ukuthi kengikhulume labantu laba.”<verse eid="ACT 21:39"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="40" style="v" sid="ACT 21:40"/>Esethole imvumo kumlawuli, uPhawuli wema ezinyathelweni zokuqansela endlini wathulisa ixuku ngesandla. Kwathi bonke sebethule wakhuluma kubo ngesiHebheru wathi,<verse eid="ACT 21:40"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 21"/>
  <chapter number="22" style="c" sid="ACT 22"/>
  <para style="nb">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 22:1"/>“Bazalwane labobaba, manje lalelani lizwe ukuzivikela kwami.”<verse eid="ACT 22:1"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 22:2"/>Bathi bemuzwa ekhuluma kubo ngesiHebheru bathula zwi.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="ACT 22:2">UPhawuli wasesithi, <verse eid="ACT 22:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 22:3"/>“Mina ngingumJuda owazalelwa eThasasi eseSilisiya, kodwa ngakhulela kulonaleli idolobho. Ngafunda ngaphansi kukaGamaliyeli, ngafundiswa okugcweleyo ngomlayo wabokhokho, lami ngakhuthalela uNkulunkulu njengani lamuhla. <verse eid="ACT 22:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 22:4"/>Ngabahlukuluza abalandeli bale iNdlela baze bafa, ngibopha abesilisa labesifazane ngibaphosela entolongweni, <verse eid="ACT 22:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 22:5"/>into engafakazwa ngumphristi omkhulu kanye lenkundla. Ngaze ngathola izincwadi kubo zisiya kubazalwane babo eDamaseko, ngaya khona ngifuna ukubaletha labobantu beyizibotshwa eJerusalema ukuthi bazojeziswa.<verse eid="ACT 22:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 22:6"/>Kwathi sekungaba yimini enkulu sengisondela eDamaseko, masinyane kwaphazima ukukhanya kuvela ezulwini kwangizingelezela. <verse eid="ACT 22:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 22:7"/>Ngawela phansi, ngezwa ilizwi lisithi kimi, <char style="wj">‘Sawuli! Sawuli! Ungihlukuluzelani na?’</char><verse eid="ACT 22:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 22:8"/>Ngabuza ngathi, ‘Ungubani, Nkosi?’</para>
  <para style="p" vid="ACT 22:8">Waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">‘NginguJesu waseNazaretha omhlukuluzayo.’</char> <verse eid="ACT 22:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 22:9"/>Ababengiphelekezela bakubona ukukhanya, kodwa kabalizwanga ilizwi lalowo owayekhuluma lami.<verse eid="ACT 22:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 22:10"/>Ngabuza ngathi, ‘Kumele ngenzeni Nkosi?’</para>
  <para style="p" vid="ACT 22:10">INkosi yathi, <char style="wj">‘Phakama uye eDamaseko. Khonale uzatshelwa konke osumiselwe ukuthi ukwenze.’</char> <verse eid="ACT 22:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 22:11"/>Abaphelekezeli bami bangihola ngesandla bangisa eDamaseko ngoba inkazimulo yokukhanya yayingenze ngaba yisiphofu.<verse eid="ACT 22:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 22:12"/>Indoda eyayithiwa ngu-Ananiya yeza yazangibona. Yayingumlandeli omkhulu womlayo njalo ihlonitshwa kakhulu yiwo wonke amaJuda ayehlala khona. <verse eid="ACT 22:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 22:13"/>Wema eceleni kwami wathi, ‘Mzalwane Sawuli, bona njalo!’ Ngalesosikhathi ngahle ngazuza amandla okumbona.<verse eid="ACT 22:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 22:14"/>Wasesithi, ‘UNkulunkulu wabokhokho bethu usekukhethile ukuthi uyazi intando yakhe lokuthi umbone oLungileyo lokuba uzwe amazwi aphuma emlonyeni wakhe. <verse eid="ACT 22:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 22:15"/>Uzakuba ngufakazi wakhe ebantwini bonke ngalokho okubonileyo lokuzwileyo. <verse eid="ACT 22:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 22:16"/>Pho usalindeni? Sukuma ubhaphathizwe, ugeze izono zakho, ubiza ibizo lakhe.’<verse eid="ACT 22:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 22:17"/>Ngithe sengibuyile eJerusalema ngikhuleka ethempelini, ngafikelwa yisiyeziphupho, <verse eid="ACT 22:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 22:18"/>ngabona iNkosi ikhuluma isithi kimi, <char style="wj">‘Phangisa! Suka masinyane eJerusalema ngoba kabayikubamukela ubufakazi bakho ngami.’</char><verse eid="ACT 22:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 22:19"/>Ngaphendula ngathi, ‘Nkosi, lababantu bayakwazi ukuthi nganginquma lamasinagogu ngibabopha njalo ngibatshaya labo abakholwa kuwe. <verse eid="ACT 22:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 22:20"/>Lalapho kuchithwa igazi lomfakazi wakho uStefane ngangimi khonapho ngivumelana labo njalo ngilinde izigqoko zalabo ababembulala.’<verse eid="ACT 22:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 22:21"/>INkosi yasisithi kimi, <char style="wj">‘Hamba; ngizakuthumela kude kwabeZizwe.’ ”</char><verse eid="ACT 22:21"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UPhawuli UngumRoma</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 22:22"/>Abantu bamlalela uPhawuli sonke isikhathi, kodwa esetsho lokhu bavungama bamemeza bathi, “Kasuswe emhlabeni lo umuntu! Kamelanga aphile!”<verse eid="ACT 22:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 22:23"/>Bathi sebeklabalala, behlubula amajazi abo, njalo bephosa uthuli emoyeni, <verse eid="ACT 22:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 22:24"/>umlawuli wamabutho walaya ukuthi uPhawuli kangeniswe enkambeni yamabutho. Wayala ukuthi atshaywe njalo abuzisiswe ukuthi kungani abantu bemvukela kanje. <verse eid="ACT 22:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 22:25"/>Bathi sebemlalisa phansi ukuthi bambhaxabule bembophile, uPhawuli wathi kumphathi wekhulu owayemi khonapho, “Kusemthethweni yini ukuthi utshaye umuntu ongumRoma ongetheswanga cala na?”<verse eid="ACT 22:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="ACT 22:26"/>Umphathi wekhulu esekuzwile lokho wayabikela umlawuli wamabutho wathi, “Usuzathini manje? Indoda le ingumRoma.”<verse eid="ACT 22:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="ACT 22:27"/>Umlawuli wamabutho waya kuPhawuli wambuza wathi, “Ake ungitshele, kanti ungumRoma na?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="ACT 22:27">Wathi, “Yebo, nginguye.”<verse eid="ACT 22:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="ACT 22:28"/>Umlawuli wamabutho wasesithi, “Mina ngahlawula imali ukuthi ngithole ilungelo lokuba ngumRoma.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="ACT 22:28">UPhawuli waphendula wathi, “Kodwa mina nginguye ngokuzalwa.”<verse eid="ACT 22:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="ACT 22:29"/>Labo abasebelungele ukumbuzisisa bahle batshedela emuva masinyane. Umlawuli webutho ngokwakhe wethuka esenanzelela ukuthi wayebophe uPhawuli, umRoma, ngamaketane.<verse eid="ACT 22:29"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Phambi KweSanihedrini</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="ACT 22:30"/>Ngosuku olulandelayo, njengoba umlawuli wamabutho wayefuna ukwazi isibili ukuthi kungani uPhawuli wayebekwa icala ngamaJuda, wamkhulula walaya abaphristi abakhulu leSanihedrini yonke ukuthi bahlangane. Wasemletha uPhawuli wamisa phambi kwabo.<verse eid="ACT 22:30"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 22"/>
  <chapter number="23" style="c" sid="ACT 23"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 23:1"/>UPhawuli wawujolozela umphakathi weSanihedrini wathi, “Bazalwane, sengiwugcwalisile umlandu wami kuNkulunkulu ngenhliziyo eqotho kuze kube lamuhla.” <verse eid="ACT 23:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 23:2"/>Umphristi omkhulu, u-Ananiya, kwamcunula lokhu, watshela labo ababemi eduze kukaPhawuli ukuthi bamukule umlomo. <verse eid="ACT 23:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 23:3"/>UPhawuli wathi kuye, “UNkulunkulu uzakumukula, wena mduli oconjwe ngekalaga emhlophe! Lapha uhlalele ukungahlulela ngomthetho, ikanti wena ngokwakho uyaweqa umthetho ngokulaya ukuthi ngitshaywe!”<verse eid="ACT 23:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 23:4"/>Labo ababemi eduze kukaPhawuli bathi, “Ulesibindi sokuthuka umphristi omkhulu kaNkulunkulu wena?”<verse eid="ACT 23:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 23:5"/>UPhawuli waphendula wathi, “Bazalwane, bengingazi ukuthi ungumphristi omkhulu; ngoba kulotshiwe ukuthi: ‘Ungakhulumi okubi ngombusi wabantu bakini.’<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">23.5 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">U-Eksodasi 22.28</char></note>”<verse eid="ACT 23:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 23:6"/>UPhawuli wayesazi ukuthi abanye babo babe ngamaSadusi, abanye bengabaFarisi, wasememeza phakathi kweSanihedrini wathi, “Bazalwane, mina ngingumFarisi, indodana yomFarisi. Ngithoniselwa ukuthi ngilethemba lokuvuka kwabafileyo.” <verse eid="ACT 23:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 23:7"/>Wathi ngokutsho lokhu, kwavuka umsindo phakathi kwabaFarisi lamaSadusi, umphakathi wasudabukana phakathi. <verse eid="ACT 23:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 23:8"/>(AmaSadusi athi kakulakuvuka ekufeni, lokuthi kakulazingilosi loba imimoya, kodwa abaFarisi bayakuvuma konke lokho ukuthi kukhona.)<verse eid="ACT 23:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 23:9"/>Kwaba lokuxokozela okukhulu, kwathi abanye abafundisi bomthetho ababe ngabaFarisi basukuma bayidaza inkani. Bathi, “Kasiboni lutho olubi ngendoda le. Mhlawumbe umoya kumbe ingilosi ikhulume kuye ke?” <verse eid="ACT 23:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 23:10"/>Yavutha inkani umlawuli webutho waze wesaba ukuthi uPhawuli sebengamdabudabula. Waselaya amabutho ukuthi ahle amsuse kubo ngamandla amlethe enkambeni yamabutho.<verse eid="ACT 23:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 23:11"/>Ngobusuku obulandelayo iNkosi yema eduze kukaPhawuli yathi, <char style="wj">“Iba lesibindi! Njengoba usufakaze ngami eJerusalema, kusamele njalo uyofakaza eRoma.”</char><verse eid="ACT 23:11"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Icebo Lokubulala UPhawuli</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 23:12"/>Ngosuku olulandelayo amaJuda abumba icebo njalo enza isifungo sokuthi kawayikudla kumbe anathe engakambulali uPhawuli. <verse eid="ACT 23:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 23:13"/>Kwakungamadoda edlula amatshumi amane ayehambisana lalelocebo. <verse eid="ACT 23:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 23:14"/>Baya kubaphristi abakhulu labadala bathi, “Sesifunge ijoyi lokuthi kasiyikudla lutho size simbulale uPhawuli. <verse eid="ACT 23:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 23:15"/>Ngakho-ke lina leSanihedrini khalazani kumlawuli webutho ukuthi amlethe kini ngenhloso yokuthi lifuna ubufakazi obugcweleyo ngecala lakhe. Thina sesilungisile ukuthi simbulale engakafiki lapha.”<verse eid="ACT 23:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 23:16"/>Kodwa kwathi ukuba indodana kadadewabo kaPhawuli isilizwile lelicebo, yaya enkambeni yamabutho yayamtshela uPhawuli.<verse eid="ACT 23:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 23:17"/>UPhawuli wasebiza omunye umphathi wekhulu wathi, “Hamba lejaha leli kumlawuli wamabutho; kukhona elifuna ukukutsho kuye.” <verse eid="ACT 23:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 23:18"/>Ngakho wasemusa kumlawuli.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="ACT 23:18">Umphathi wekhulu wathi, “Isibotshwa esinguPhawuli singibizile sangicela ukuthi ngilethe ijaha leli kuwe ngoba kukhona elifuna ukukutshela khona.”<verse eid="ACT 23:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 23:19"/>Umlawuli wamthatha lowojaha, wambamba ngesandla waya laye eceleni, wambuza wathi, “Kuyini ofuna ukungitshela khona?”<verse eid="ACT 23:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 23:20"/>Wathi: “AmaJuda asevumelene ukuthi akucele wena ukuthi ulethe uPhawuli phambi kweSanihedrini kusasa ngenhloso yokuthi afuna ingcazelo epheleleyo mayelana laye. <verse eid="ACT 23:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 23:21"/>Ungabavumeli ngoba abeqa amatshumi amane bawo bazamcathamela. Asenze isifungo sokuthi angadli njalo anganathi engakabulali uPhawuli. Kunje nje sebelungile, sebelindele imvumo yakho ngesicelo sabo.”<verse eid="ACT 23:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 23:22"/>Umlawuli wathi kahambe umfana, wamqonqosela wathi, “Ungatsheli muntu ukuthi usungazisile ngalokhu.”<verse eid="ACT 23:22"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UPhawuli Udluliselwa EKhesariya</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 23:23"/>Wasebiza abaphathi bebutho ababili wabalaya wathi, “Lungisani ixuku lamabutho angamakhulu amabili, abagadi bamabhiza abangamatshumi ayisikhombisa labangamakhulu amabili abahlome ngemikhonto ukuthi baye eKhesariya lamuhla ebusuku ngehola lesithathu. <verse eid="ACT 23:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 23:24"/>Lilungisele loPhawuli amabhiza ukuze asiwe kuMbusi uFelikhe evikelekile.”<verse eid="ACT 23:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 23:25"/>Wabhala incwadi kanje:<verse eid="ACT 23:25"/></para>
  <para style="pmo">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="ACT 23:26"/>Klawudiyasi Lisiya,</para>
  <para style="pmo" vid="ACT 23:26">Kumhlekazi, uMbusi uFelikhe:</para>
  <para style="pmo" vid="ACT 23:26">Ngiyabingelela.<verse eid="ACT 23:26"/></para>
  <para style="pm">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="ACT 23:27"/>Indoda le yabanjwa ngamaJuda, okwathi esezama ukuyibulala ngafika lamabutho ami sayilamulela ngoba ngasengizwile ukuthi ingumRoma. <verse eid="ACT 23:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="ACT 23:28"/>Ngadinga ukwazi ukuthi ayesithi yoneni, yikho ngayiletha phambi kweSanihedrini yawo. <verse eid="ACT 23:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="ACT 23:29"/>Ngezwa ukuthi icala layo laliphathelene lomlayo wawo, kodwa kwasweleka icala elingafanela ukufa loba ukugwetshelwa entolongweni. <verse eid="ACT 23:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="ACT 23:30"/>Ngithe sengilunywe indlebe ngecebo lokuyibulala ngahle ngayedlulisela kuwe. Ngiphinde ngatshela omayimangalela ukuthi bazokwethula kuwe abamangalela ngakho.<verse eid="ACT 23:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="ACT 23:31"/>Ngakho amabutho azilandela lezo ziqondiso amthatha uPhawuli ebusuku ayamfikisa e-Antiphatri. <verse eid="ACT 23:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="ACT 23:32"/>Ngosuku olulandelayo amabutho amtshiya leqembu labagade amabhiza ukuthi liqhubeke laye, bona babuyela enkambeni. <verse eid="ACT 23:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="ACT 23:33"/>Kwathi abamabhiza sebefikile eKhesariya bayethula incwadi kumbusi loPhawuli laye bamnikela kuye. <verse eid="ACT 23:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="ACT 23:34"/>Umbusi wayibala incwadi wambuza ukuthi wayedabuka kusiphi isifunda. Esezwile ukuthi wayengoweSilisiya, <verse eid="ACT 23:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="ACT 23:35"/>Wathi, “Icala lakho ngizalihlola nxa labo abakumangalelayo sebefikile lapha.” Waselaya ukuthi uPhawuli agcinwe elindiwe esigodlweni sikaHerodi.<verse eid="ACT 23:35"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 23"/>
  <chapter number="24" style="c" sid="ACT 24"/>
  <para style="s1">Icala Lithethwa NguFelikhe</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 24:1"/>Ngemva kwensuku ezinhlanu umphristi omkhulu u-Ananiya wehlela eKhesariya labadala abathile kanye lomeli owayethiwa nguThethula, bafika beneka ukumangalela kwabo uPhawuli kumbusi. <verse eid="ACT 24:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 24:2"/>UPhawuli esebiziwe, uThethula walethula icala kuFelikhe wathi: “Mhlekazi! Ngaphansi kombuso wakho sesikholise isikhathi sokuthula eside, ikanti lombono wakho usulethe intuthuko kulesisizwe. <verse eid="ACT 24:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 24:3"/>Yonke indawo, ngazozonke izindlela, mhlekazi omuhle Felikhe, siyakwamukela konke lokhu ngokubonga okukhulu. <verse eid="ACT 24:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 24:4"/>Kodwa ukuthi ngingakuchitheli isikhathi, ngiyakucela ukuthi uke usizwe kancinyane esikutshoyo.<verse eid="ACT 24:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 24:5"/>Indoda le siyifumane ukuthi iluhlupho, ivusa isiphithiphithi phakathi kwamaJuda kuwo wonke umhlaba. Ingumholi wequla lamaNazarini <verse eid="ACT 24:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 24:6"/>futhi yazama njalo ukungcolisa ithempeli; yikho sayibamba. Sasifuna ukumahlulela ngokomlayo wethu. [ <verse eid="ACT 24:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 24:7"/>Kodwa umlawuli uLisiya weza wazamthatha ngodlakela ezandleni zethu, wathi obamangalelayo kabeze phambi kwakhe].<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">24.7 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Livesi ayikho kwamanye amaBhayibhili esiLungu.</char></note> <verse eid="ACT 24:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 24:8"/>Ngokumhlola wena ngokwakho uzalibona iqiniso ngazozonke lezizinto esimangalela ngazo.”<verse eid="ACT 24:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 24:9"/>AmaJuda lawo ayingenela indaba eqinisa ukuthi lezizinto zaziliqiniso.<verse eid="ACT 24:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 24:10"/>Kwathi umbusi esemphile ithuba lokuthi akhulume uPhawuli waphendula wathi: “Ngiyazi ukuthi usube ngumahluli walesisizwe okweminyaka eminengi; ngakho ngizivikela ngesibindi langentokozo. <verse eid="ACT 24:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 24:11"/>Ungalithola iqiniso lokuthi kakudluli insuku ezilitshumi lambili ngiyile eJerusalema ukuyakhonza. <verse eid="ACT 24:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 24:12"/>Abangimangalelayo kabazange bangifumane ngiphikisana lomuntu ethempelini, loba ngitshotshozela amaxuku emasinagogweni kumbe ngaphi edolobheni. <verse eid="ACT 24:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 24:13"/>Bangezake balethe ubufakazi kuwe balezizinto abangimangalela ngazo. <verse eid="ACT 24:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 24:14"/>Kodwa ngiyavuma ukuthi ngikhonza uNkulunkulu wabokhokho bethu, njengomlandeli weNdlela abayibiza ngokuthi ngumvukela. Ngiyakukholwa konke okuvumelana loMlayo lokubhaliweyo kubaphrofethi, <verse eid="ACT 24:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 24:15"/>njalo ngilethemba elifana lelamadoda la kuNkulunkulu, ukuthi kuzakuba lokuvuka kwabafileyo, abalungileyo lababi. <verse eid="ACT 24:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 24:16"/>Ngakho ngiyazama kokuphela ukuba isazela sami sihlale sihlanzekile phambi kukaNkulunkulu laphambi kwabantu.<verse eid="ACT 24:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 24:17"/>Ngemva kweminyaka eminengi ngingekho, ngeza eJerusalema ukuletha izipho zabaswelayo ebantwini bakithi lokwethula iminikelo. <verse eid="ACT 24:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 24:18"/>Ngangihlanzekile ngokomkhuba baze bangifumane ethempelini ngisenza lokhu. Kwakungelaxuku labantu elalilami, kumbe ukuthi ngangiphazamisa ngokuthile. <verse eid="ACT 24:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 24:19"/>Kodwa kukhona amaJuda athile avela esifundeni sase-Ezhiya, okufanele ukuthi ngabe akhona lapha phambi kwakho, angethese icala nxa kukhona akusolayo ngami. <verse eid="ACT 24:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 24:20"/>Kumbe wonala akhona kawachaze ukuthi licala bani alifumanayo kimi mhlazana ngimi eSanihedrini, <verse eid="ACT 24:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 24:21"/>ngaphandle kwalokhu kodwa engakumemezayo ngimi phambi kwawo ukuthi: ‘Kungenxa yokuvuka kwabafileyo okwenza ngithonisiswe phambi kwenu lamuhla.’ ”<verse eid="ACT 24:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 24:22"/>Ngakho uFelikhe, owayesazi kakhulu ngeNdlela walimisa icala. Wathi, “Kuzakuthi nxa uLisiya umlawuli angafika ngizaliquma icala lenu.” <verse eid="ACT 24:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 24:23"/>Walaya umphathi wekhulu ukuthi agcine uPhawuli elindiwe kodwa amvumele ukukhululeka okuthile kanye labangane bakhe ukuthi bamuphe lokho akuswelayo.<verse eid="ACT 24:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 24:24"/>Ngemva kwensuku ezinengi uFelikhe wafika lomkakhe uDrusila owaye ngumJudakazi. Wathi kakubizwe uPhawuli, wamlalela echaza ngokukholwa kuJesu Khristu. <verse eid="ACT 24:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 24:25"/>UPhawuli wathi esebalisa ngokulunga, langokuzithiba langokwahlulelwa okuzayo uFelikhe wesaba wathi, “Sekwanele okwamanje! Usungahamba. Kungaze kulunge njalo ngizakubiza.” <verse eid="ACT 24:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="ACT 24:26"/>Yena wayecabanga ukuthi uPhawuli uzamupha imali yokumfumbathisa, yikho wayembiza futhifuthi ekhuluma laye.<verse eid="ACT 24:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="ACT 24:27"/>Isidlule iminyaka emibili, uFelikhe walandelwa esikhundleni nguPhokhiyu Festasi, kodwa ngoba uFelikhe wayefuna ukuthabisa amaJuda, watshiya uPhawuli elokhu esentolongweni.<verse eid="ACT 24:27"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 24"/>
  <chapter number="25" style="c" sid="ACT 25"/>
  <para style="s1">Ukuthonisiswa Phambi KukaFestasi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 25:1"/>Ngemva kwensuku ezintathu efikile esifundeni uFestasi, wasuka eKhesariya waya eJerusalema <verse eid="ACT 25:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 25:2"/>lapho abaphristi abakhulu labakhokheli bamaJuda bema phambi kwakhe beneka amacala kaPhawuli. <verse eid="ACT 25:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 25:3"/>Bamcela ngokuphangisa uFestasi, ukuba abenzele umusa, abalethele uPhawuli eJerusalema, ngoba babeceba ukumcathamela bambulale endleleni. <verse eid="ACT 25:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 25:4"/>UFestasi waphendula wathi, “UPhawuli uvalelwe eKhesariya, njalo mina ngokwami Ngiya khona masinyane. <verse eid="ACT 25:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 25:5"/>Akuthi abanye abakhokheli bakini bahambe lami bafike bamethese amacala khonale, nxa kukhona akonileyo.”<verse eid="ACT 25:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 25:6"/>Esehlale insuku eziyisificaminwembili loba ezilitshumi labo, wehlela eKhesariya, kwathi ngosuku olulandelayo wangenisa inkundla wathi kalethwe uPhawuli phambi kwakhe. <verse eid="ACT 25:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 25:7"/>Esefikile uPhawuli amaJuda ayebuyile evela eJerusalema ambuthanela, ethula amacala amanengi esabekayo ngaye, kodwa engelabufakazi ngawo.<verse eid="ACT 25:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 25:8"/>UPhawuli wasezivikela wathi, “Angenzanga lutho oluphikisa umlayo wamaJuda kumbe ukudumaza ithempeli, kumbe oluphikisa uKhesari.”<verse eid="ACT 25:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 25:9"/>UFestasi wayefuna ukwenzela amaJuda umusa, wathi kuPhawuli, “Uyavuma na ukuya eJerusalema ukuthi ngiyekuthonisela khona amacala la?”<verse eid="ACT 25:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 25:10"/>Waphendula uPhawuli wathi, “Khathesi sengisiyakuma phambi kwenkundla kaKhesari, lapho engifanele ukuthonisiswa khona. Kangonanga lutho kumaJuda, njengoba lawe usazi kakuhle. <verse eid="ACT 25:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 25:11"/>Kodwa, nxa ngilecala lokwenza loba yini efanele ukufa kangali ukubulawa. Kodwa nxa lawomacala engiwetheswa ngamaJuda la engasiqiniso, kakho olelungelo lokunginikela kuwo. Ngilidlulisela kuKhesari!”<verse eid="ACT 25:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 25:12"/>UFestasi esehlanganise amakhanda lomphakathi wakhe, wathi, “Usulidlulisele kuKhesari. Uzakuya-ke kuKhesari!”<verse eid="ACT 25:12"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UFestasi Ubonisana LeNkosi U-Agripha</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 25:13"/>Sekuyizinsuku ezimbalwa ngemva kwalokho iNkosi u-Agripha loBhenikhe bafika eKhesariya ukuyaqinisa ubudlelwano laye uFestasi. <verse eid="ACT 25:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 25:14"/>Njengoba babezachitha insuku ezinengi khona, uFestasi wakhuluma leNkosi ngendaba kaPhawuli. Wathi, “Kulendoda lapha eyatshiywa nguFelikhe iyisibotshwa. <verse eid="ACT 25:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 25:15"/>Ngathi ngiseJerusalema, abaphristi abakhulu labadala bamaJuda bayimangalela ngamacala athile, bacela ukuthi ibulawe.<verse eid="ACT 25:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 25:16"/>Ngabatshela ukuthi kakusimkhuba wamaRoma ukunikela umuntu engakahlanganiswa labamangaleli bakhe, waphiwa ithuba lokuzivikela kulawo macala abambeka wona. <verse eid="ACT 25:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 25:17"/>Bathi sebefikile lapha behamba lami, ngahle ngalingenisa icala, kodwa inkundla ngayihlanganisa ngosuku olulandelayo, ngathi indoda leyo kayingeniswe. <verse eid="ACT 25:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 25:18"/>Sebephakamile ukuba bakhulume, kabasambekanga lawomacala engangiwakhumbula. <verse eid="ACT 25:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 25:19"/>Kodwa, kulezinto ezithile ababephikisana ngazo laye mayelana lenkolo yabo langenye indoda eyafayo ethiwa nguJesu, uPhawuli athi yena iyaphila. <verse eid="ACT 25:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 25:20"/>Ngisuke ngadideka ukuthi ngizicubungule njani izindaba ezinjalo; yikho ngimbuzile ukuthi angavuma yini ukuya eJerusalema ayethonisiswa khona ngamacala la. <verse eid="ACT 25:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 25:21"/>Kuthe uPhawuli esethe ucela icala lakhe limiswe liyoqunywa nguMbusi oMkhulu, ngathi kagcinwe entolongweni ngize ngimdlulisele kuKhesari.”<verse eid="ACT 25:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 25:22"/>U-Agripha wasesithi kuFestasi, “Ngifuna ukuthi kengiyizwe mina ngokwami indoda leyo.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="ACT 25:22">Waphendula wathi, “Uzayizwa kusasa.”<verse eid="ACT 25:22"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UPhawuli Phambi Kuka-Agripha</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 25:23"/>Kusisa u-Agripha loBhenikhe bafika ngodumo olukhulu bangena emthethwandaba lezikhulu zakhona ezaziwayo kanye labakhokheli bedolobho. UFestasi wathi uPhawuli kalethwe. <verse eid="ACT 25:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 25:24"/>UFestasi wasesithi, “Nkosi Agripha, lani lonke elikhona lathi lapha, liyayibona indoda le! Sonke isizwe samaJuda eJerusalema lakhona lapha eKhesariya senza isikhalazo kimi bememeza ukuthi kayisafanelanga ukuthi ibe ilokhu iphila. <verse eid="ACT 25:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 25:25"/>Ngafumana ukuthi kwakungelalutho alwenzayo olufanele ukufa, kodwa ngenxa yokuthi wacela ukudluliselwa kuMbusi oMkhulu, ngakhetha ukuthi ngimdlulisele eRoma. <verse eid="ACT 25:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="ACT 25:26"/>Kodwa kakulalutho olubambekayo engizalulobela uMhlekazi ngaye. Ngakho sengimlethe lapha phambi kwenu lonke, ikakhulu phambi kwakho wena Nkosi Agripha, ukuze kuthi ngemva kokumhlola hlezi ngithole ulutho engingaluloba. <verse eid="ACT 25:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="ACT 25:27"/>Ngibona kungaba liphutha elikhulu ukuthumela isibotshwa ngingacacanga ngamacala esiwetheswayo.”<verse eid="ACT 25:27"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 25"/>
  <chapter number="26" style="c" sid="ACT 26"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 26:1"/>U-Agripha wasesithi kuPhawuli, “Ulemvumo yokuzikhulumela.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="ACT 26:1">Ngakho uPhawuli wasephakamisa isandla sakhe waqalisa ukuzivikela, wathi, <verse eid="ACT 26:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 26:2"/>“Nkosi Agripha, ngizibona ngilenhlanhla ukuma phambi kwakho lamuhla ngisethula ukuzivikela kwami kuwo wonke amacala engiwetheswa ngamaJuda, <verse eid="ACT 26:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 26:3"/>ikakhulu njengoba wena uwazi amasiko amaJuda kanye lokuphikisana kwawo. Ngakho ngiyakucela ukuthi ungilalele ngokubekezela.<verse eid="ACT 26:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 26:4"/>AmaJuda wonke ayayazi impilo engiyiphilileyo kusukela ebuntwaneni bami, ekuqaleni kokuphila kwami elizweni lakithi njalo laseJerusalema. <verse eid="ACT 26:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 26:5"/>Sebengazi okwesikhathi eside njalo bangafakaza nxa bethanda, ukuthi ngenhlelo zenkolo yethu eqinileyo, ngangiphila ngingumFarisi. <verse eid="ACT 26:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 26:6"/>Manje sekungenxa yethemba lami kulokho uNkulunkulu akuthembisa okhokho bethu okwenza ngithonisiswe lamuhla. <verse eid="ACT 26:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 26:7"/>Lesi yiso isithembiso esilindelwe yizizwana zakithi ezilitshumi lambili ukuthi zizasibona sigcwaliseka zilokhu zimkhonza uNkulunkulu ngokutshiseka emini lebusuku. Mhlekazi, kungenxa yalo lelithemba engimangalelwa lona ngamaJuda. <verse eid="ACT 26:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 26:8"/>Kungenzakala kanjani ukuthi phakathi kwenu kube yinto engakholekiyo ukuthi uNkulunkulu uyabavusa abafileyo na?<verse eid="ACT 26:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 26:9"/>Lami ngokwami ngangizimisele ukuthi ngenze yonke imizamo yokuphikisana lebizo likaJesu waseNazaretha. <verse eid="ACT 26:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 26:10"/>Lakanye yikho lokho engakwenzayo eJerusalema. Ngaphiwa amandla ngabaphristi abakhulu ngaphosela abanengi abangcwele entolongweni, kwathi ekubulaweni kwabo lami ngasekela ukubalahla. <verse eid="ACT 26:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 26:11"/>Izikhathi ezinengi ngangihamba nginquma lamasinagogu ngisithi kabajeziswe, ngazama njalo ukubabamba ngamandla ukuthi bahlambaze uJesu. Ngathi ngihlanyiswa yikubazonda ngaya lakwamanye amadolobho asezizweni ukuyabahlukuluza khona.<verse eid="ACT 26:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 26:12"/>Kolunye uhambo lwami ngalubangisa eDamaseko ngilamandla lomlayo engawuphiwa ngabaphristi abakhulu. <verse eid="ACT 26:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 26:13"/>Kwathi sekungaba yimini enkulu ngisendleleni Mhlekazi Agripha, ngabona ukukhanya kuvela ezulwini, kukhazimula ukwedlula ilanga, kungizingelezele kanye labakhula bami. <verse eid="ACT 26:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 26:14"/>Sonke sawela phansi, ngezwa ilizwi lisithi kimi, ngesiHebheru, <char style="wj">‘Sawuli, Sawuli ungihlukuluzelani na? Kubuhlungu kuwe ukukhahlela izinciji.’</char><verse eid="ACT 26:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 26:15"/>Ngasengibuza ngathi, ‘Ungubani, Nkosi?’</para>
  <para style="p" vid="ACT 26:15">INkosi yaphendula yathi, <char style="wj">‘NginguJesu omhlukuluzayo.</char> <verse eid="ACT 26:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 26:16"/><char style="wj">Phakama khathesi ume ngezinyawo zakho. Ngizibonise kuwe ukuthi ngikukhethe ukuba yinceku njalo ube ngufakazi walokho osukubonile ngami, lalokho engisazakutshengisa khona.</char> <verse eid="ACT 26:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 26:17"/><char style="wj">Ngizakuphephisa ebantwini bakini lakwabeZizwe. Ngikuthuma</char> <verse eid="ACT 26:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 26:18"/><char style="wj">ukuthi uvule amehlo abo, ubaphendule basuke ebumnyameni baye ekukhanyeni, njalo basuke emandleni kaSathane baye kuNkulunkulu ukuze bemukele ukuthethelelwa kwezono lendawo phakathi kwalabo abangcweliswe ngokukholwa kimi.’</char><verse eid="ACT 26:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 26:19"/>Ngakho-ke, Nkosi Agripha, kangiqholozelanga umbono ovela ezulwini. <verse eid="ACT 26:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 26:20"/>Ngaqala ngaba seDamaseko, kwalandela abaseJerusalema laseJudiya lonke, kwalandela labeZizwe labo, ngatshumayela ukuthi kumele baphenduke babuyele kuNkulunkulu njalo babonise ukuphenduka kwabo ngezenzo zabo. <verse eid="ACT 26:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 26:21"/>Kungaleso isizatho okwenza amaJuda angibamba ngisemagumeni ethempeli azama ukungibulala. <verse eid="ACT 26:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 26:22"/>Kodwa uNkulunkulu ungiphephisile kuze kube namuhla, yikho ngimi lapha ngifakaza kwabancinyane labakhulu ngokufananayo. Kakulalutho engilutshoyo ngaphezu kwalokho abaphrofethi loMosi abathi kuzakwenzakala, <verse eid="ACT 26:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 26:23"/>ukuthi uKhristu wayezahlupheka, njalo njengowokuqala ukuvuka kwabafileyo, atshumayele ukukhanya ebantwini bakibo lakwabeZizwe.”<verse eid="ACT 26:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 26:24"/>Khonapho uFestasi wasemphazamisa esazivikela wathi, “Phawuli, usangene ingqondo! Ukufunda kwakho okukhulu sekukuphambanise ingqondo.”<verse eid="ACT 26:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 26:25"/>Waphendula uPhawuli wathi, “Kangihlanyi, Mhlekazi omkhulu Festasi. Engikutshoyo kuliqiniso njalo kulengqondo. <verse eid="ACT 26:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="ACT 26:26"/>Inkosi izijayele lezizinto yikho ngikhuluma kuyo ngikhululekile. Ngiyakholwa ukuthi kakukho lokukodwa kukho okuyeqileyo inkosi, ngoba kakwenziwanga ejikweni ngokucatshelana. <verse eid="ACT 26:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="ACT 26:27"/>Nkosi Agripha, uyabakholwa na abaphrofethi? Ngiyazi ukuthi uyabakholwa.”<verse eid="ACT 26:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="ACT 26:28"/>U-Agripha wasesithi kuPhawuli, “Kambe ucabanga ukuthi ngesikhatshana esifitshane kangaka ungangiphendula ngibe ngumKhristu?”<verse eid="ACT 26:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="ACT 26:29"/>UPhawuli waphendula wathi, “Singaba sisifitshane loba sibeside, ngiyakhuleka kuNkulunkulu ukuthi kakungabi nguwe kuphela kodwa bonke abangizwayo lamuhla bangaba yilokho engiyikho khona, ngaphandle kwala amaketane.”<verse eid="ACT 26:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="ACT 26:30"/>Inkosi yaphakama kanye lombusi loBhenikhe lalabo ababehlezi labo. <verse eid="ACT 26:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="ACT 26:31"/>Baphuma endlini, bathi sebekhuluma bodwa, bathi, “Indoda le kakulalutho elwenzayo olufanele ukufa loba ukuvalelwa entolongweni.”<verse eid="ACT 26:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="ACT 26:32"/>U-Agripha wathi kuFestasi, “Indoda le ibizakhululwa kube ibingedluliselanga icala layo kuKhesari.”<verse eid="ACT 26:32"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 26"/>
  <chapter number="27" style="c" sid="ACT 27"/>
  <para style="s1">UPhawuli Uya ERoma</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 27:1"/>Sekumisiwe ukuthi sizakuya e-Ithali, uPhawuli kanye lezinye izibotshwa banikelwa ezandleni zomphathi wekhulu owayethiwa nguJuliyasi owaye ngoweButho leSikhosini. <verse eid="ACT 27:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 27:2"/>Sagada umkhumbi e-Adramithiya owawusulungele ukuya emathekwini asemakhunjini esifunda sase-Ezhiya, sahle salungena ulwandle. Sasilo-Aristakhasi, owayesuka eThesalonika.<verse eid="ACT 27:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 27:3"/>Kusisa sakhuphukela eSidoni; uJuliyasi watshengisa umusa kuPhawuli, wamvumela ukuthi aye kubangane bakhe bamenzele lokho ayengabe ekuswela. <verse eid="ACT 27:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 27:4"/>Sesisuka lapho saluqonda ulwandle njalo sagudla ethunzini laseSiphrasi ngoba ukuvunguza komoya kwakuphambana lathi. <verse eid="ACT 27:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 27:5"/>Sathi sesiwele sadabula ulwandle olubanzi malungana lasokhunjini lweSilisiya lePhamfiliya, sakhuphukela eMira eseLikhiya. <verse eid="ACT 27:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 27:6"/>Khonapho umphathi wekhulu wafumana umkhumbi wase-Alekizandriya uwelela e-Ithali, wasingenisa kuwo. <verse eid="ACT 27:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 27:7"/>Sahamba sitotoba okwensuku ezinengi, sathwala nzima ukuyafika eKhinidu. Kwathi ngoba umoya usivalela ukuthi sihambe ngendlela yethu, sawela sayagudla ethunzini laseKhrethe, malungana leSalimoni. <verse eid="ACT 27:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 27:8"/>Sahamba siceza okhunjini kanzima, safika endaweni ethiwa kuseMathekumahle, eduze ledolobho laseLaseya.<verse eid="ACT 27:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 27:9"/>Sasesilahlekelwe yisikhathi esinengi kakhulu, lokuhamba olwandle kwasekuyingozi kabi ngoba ngalesisikhathi kwasekungemva kwesikhathi sokuzila. Yikho uPhawuli wabaxwayisa wathi, <verse eid="ACT 27:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 27:10"/>“Madoda, ngibona ukuthi uhambo lolu luzakuba lengozi lomonakalo omkhulu, kubhidlike umkhumbi lempahla, lempilo zethu lathi.” <verse eid="ACT 27:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 27:11"/>Kodwa umphathi wekhulu, esikhundleni sokulalela lokho okwakutshiwo nguPhawuli, walandela iseluleko somtshayeli womkhumbi kanye lomnikazi wawo. <verse eid="ACT 27:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 27:12"/>Njengoba itheku lalingelihle ukuthi simise khona ebusika, abanengi bakhetha ukuthi siqhubeke ngohambo, bethemba ukuthi sizafika eFenikhe simise khona ebusika lobo. Leli kwakulitheku eliseKhrethe, elalikhangele eningizimu yentshonalanga njalo lenyakatho yentshonalanga.<verse eid="ACT 27:12"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Isiphepho</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 27:13"/>Kwathi ngokuphephetha komoya opholileyo waseningizimu, banakana ukuthi basebekutholile ababekudinga; ngakho bawukhulula umkhumbi wawela ugudle iKhrethe. <verse eid="ACT 27:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 27:14"/>Masinyazana nje, umoya olamandla esivunguvungu owawuthiwa “yiNhlampumalanga” wavunguza usuka esihlengeni. <verse eid="ACT 27:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 27:15"/>Umkhumbi watshaywa yilesosiphepho wehluleka ukuqondana lomoya; ngakho wasehlula sasesindenda nje siwulandela. <verse eid="ACT 27:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 27:16"/>Sathi lapho sidlula ekusithekeni kwesihlenge esincane esithiwa yiKhawuda, kwasekusala lokuthi simise kuhle isikepe sokuphephela siqonde. <verse eid="ACT 27:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 27:17"/>Kwathi amadoda esesidonsele phezulu emkhunjini, basebethandela izintambo bebopha umkhumbi ngokwawo ukuze uqine wonke. Bathi ngoba besesaba ukuthi bazatshayeka emhlabathini wetshebetshebe laseSithisi, behlisa iseyili bayekela umkhumbi wazindendela nje. <verse eid="ACT 27:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 27:18"/>Isiphepho sasizunguza kabuhlungu kwaze kwathi ngosuku olulandelayo saqalisa ukujikela umthwalo olwandle. <verse eid="ACT 27:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 27:19"/>Ngosuku lwesithathu baphosela phandle ngezabo izandla izintambo lezinye impahla zokuhambisa umkhumbi. <verse eid="ACT 27:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 27:20"/>Kwathi sekuyizinsuku ezinengi singaliboni ilanga loba izinkanyezi, kodwa isiphepho silokhu sisidla ubhedu, saphelelwa lithemba lokuthi sizaphepha.<verse eid="ACT 27:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 27:21"/>Amadoda ayesehlale isikhathi eside engadlanga, uPhawuli wasesima phambi kwabo, wathi, “Madoda, ngabe lingilalele sangasuki eKhrethe; ngabe kalizifakanga phakathi kwale inhlekenhleke lokulahlekelwa lokhu. <verse eid="ACT 27:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 27:22"/>Kodwa manje ngiyalikhuthaza ukuthi lime isibindi, ngoba kakukho lamunye wenu ozakufa; ngumkhumbi kuphela ozabhidlika. <verse eid="ACT 27:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 27:23"/>Izolo ebusuku ingilosi kaNkulunkulu engingowakhe mina njalo lengimkhonzayo ime phambi kwami <verse eid="ACT 27:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 27:24"/>yathi, ‘Ungesabi, Phawuli. Kumele uyethonisiswa nguKhesari; njalo uNkulunkulu usebe lomusa wokukunika impilo zabo bonke owela labo.’ <verse eid="ACT 27:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 27:25"/>Ngakho manini isibindi, madoda, ngoba ngiyamethemba uNkulunkulu ukuthi kuzakwenzakala njengokungitshela kwakhe. <verse eid="ACT 27:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="ACT 27:26"/>Kodwa phela sisezake sitshayeke phansi sikhaphazelwe esihlengeni esithile.”<verse eid="ACT 27:26"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukubhidlika Komkhumbi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="ACT 27:27"/>Ngobusuku betshumi lane sasilokhu siyaluziswa oLwandle lwe-Adriyathi, lapho okwathi phakathi kobusuku abaqhubi bomkhumbi bezwa kungathi basebesondela emhlabathini. <verse eid="ACT 27:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="ACT 27:28"/>Baphosa izintambo zokulinganisa bafumana ukuthi amanzi ayezike okwezingalo ezilikhulu elilamatshumi amabili. Ngemva kwesikhatshana baphinda baziphosa njalo bafumana izingalo ezingamatshumi ayisificamunwemunye ukuzika. <verse eid="ACT 27:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="ACT 27:29"/>Bathi ngoba besesaba ukuthi sasizasakazeka ematsheni basebesehlisa insika zokumisa umkhumbi ngemuva bekhalela ukuthi kuse. <verse eid="ACT 27:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="ACT 27:30"/>Abaqhubi bomkhumbi bazama ukunyenya babaleke emkhunjini ngokwehlisela isikepe sokusinda olwandle bezenza abafuna ukuyakwehlisa ezinye insika ngaphambili komkhumbi. <verse eid="ACT 27:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="ACT 27:31"/>UPhawuli wasesithi kumphathi wekhulu lasemabuthweni, “Nxa amadoda la engahlali emkhunjini, ngeke lisinde.” <verse eid="ACT 27:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="ACT 27:32"/>Ngakho amabutho asequma izintambo ezazibambe isikepe sokusinda asiyekela sayagxumukela emanzini.<verse eid="ACT 27:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="ACT 27:33"/>Sekubanga emathathakusa, uPhawuli wabakhuthaza bonke ukuthi badle. Wathi, “Okwensuku ezilitshumi lane ezidluleyo belihlezi libambe amaphaphu enu; lisehluleka lokudla; kalizange lidle lutho. <verse eid="ACT 27:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="ACT 27:34"/>Okwamanje ngilicela ukuthi lidle. Kumele lidle ukuze liphile. Kakho loyedwa wenu ozalahlekelwa lalunwele ekhanda lakhe.” <verse eid="ACT 27:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="ACT 27:35"/>Esekutshilo lokhu, wathatha isinkwa wabonga kuNkulunkulu phambi kwabo bonke. Wasesihlephuna wadla. <verse eid="ACT 27:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="ACT 27:36"/>Bonke baqunga isibindi basebesidla labo. <verse eid="ACT 27:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="ACT 27:37"/>Sisonke sasingabantu abangamakhulu amabili lamatshumi ayisikhombisa lesithupha (276) emkhunjini. <verse eid="ACT 27:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="ACT 27:38"/>Bathi sebedlile basutha, baphungula ukusindwa komkhumbi ngokuchithela amabele olwandle.<verse eid="ACT 27:38"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="ACT 27:39"/>Kwathi sokusile kabawunanzelelanga umhlabathi, kodwa babona itheku elaligcwele itshebetshebe, basebezimisela ukuthi umkhumbi bayewumisa khona nxa kuvuma. <verse eid="ACT 27:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="ACT 27:40"/>Baquma insika bazitshiya zicwila olwandle, baphinda banyomula lezintambo ezazibambe okokugwedlisa. Basebephakamisa iseyili yaphambili beyiqondisa emoyeni, basebeqonda ekhunjini. <verse eid="ACT 27:40"/><verse number="41" style="v" sid="ACT 27:41"/>Kodwa umkhumbi watshayelela esidulini setshebetshebe olwandle wahle wabhajwa. Isihloko sawo sathi ngxi phansi asabe sisanyikinyeka, ingemuva yona yahlakazeka itshaywa ngamagagasi.<verse eid="ACT 27:41"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="42" style="v" sid="ACT 27:42"/>Amabutho asesithi kungcono abulale izibotshwa ukuze kungabikhona esizantsheza sibaleke. <verse eid="ACT 27:42"/><verse number="43" style="v" sid="ACT 27:43"/>Kodwa umphathi wekhulu wayefuna ukuvikela impilo kaPhawuli, yikho wabalela ukuthi bakwenze lokho abasebekumisile. Walaya labo ababelamandla okuntsheza ukuba bazithele olwandle bona kuqala baqonde emhlabathini. <verse eid="ACT 27:43"/><verse number="44" style="v" sid="ACT 27:44"/>Inengi lalizandenda ngamapulanka liye khona loba ngasiqa bani somkhumbi. Ngale indlela wonke umuntu wafika emhlabathini ephephile.<verse eid="ACT 27:44"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 27"/>
  <chapter number="28" style="c" sid="ACT 28"/>
  <para style="s1">Emhlabathini EMalitha</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ACT 28:1"/>Sathi sesiphephile safika emhlabathini, sezwa ukuthi isihlenge leso sasithiwa yiMalitha. <verse eid="ACT 28:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="ACT 28:2"/>Abantu bakhona basiphatha ngomusa ongajayelekanga. Basemukela kuhle sonke, basibasela umlilo wekhanka ngoba izulu lalisina njalo kumakhaza. <verse eid="ACT 28:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="ACT 28:3"/>UPhawuli watheza umnyaba wenkuni, wathi ebasela kwaphuma inhlangwana isixotshwa ngumlilo yahle yamthandela esandleni. <verse eid="ACT 28:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="ACT 28:4"/>Abahlali besihlengeni bathi bebona inyoka ilenga esandleni sakhe bakhulumisana besithi, “Indoda le iyisigebenga; ngoba loba isindile olwandle, unkulunkulukazi uKulunga kayivumelanga ukuthi iphile.” <verse eid="ACT 28:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="ACT 28:5"/>Kodwa uPhawuli wayithintitha inyoka wayilabhulela emlilweni yena akaze alimala lakancane. <verse eid="ACT 28:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="ACT 28:6"/>Abantu babelinde okwesikhathi eside bengaboni lutho olubi lusenzakala kuye, baguqula imicabango yabo basebesithi ungunkulunkulu.<verse eid="ACT 28:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="ACT 28:7"/>Eduze kwalapho kwakulepulazi likaPhabhiliyasi, owayeyisikhulu esiphethe isihlenge. Wasemukela ngesihle emzini wakhe, wasihlalisa khona okwensuku ezintathu esiphethe kuhle. <verse eid="ACT 28:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="ACT 28:8"/>Uyise wayegula elele phansi ephethwe luqhuqho lesihudo. UPhawuli wayambona, kwathi esekhulekile, wambeka izandla wamsilisa. <verse eid="ACT 28:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="ACT 28:9"/>Kwathi sekwenzakele lokhu, bonke abagulayo esihlengeni beza basiliswa. <verse eid="ACT 28:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="ACT 28:10"/>Basidumisa ngezipho ezinengi, kwasekusithi sesilungela ukuwela basilungisela umphako owaneleyo.<verse eid="ACT 28:10"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukufika ERoma</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="ACT 28:11"/>Ngemva kwezinyanga ezintathu sangena olwandle sigade umkhumbi owawuchithe ubusika khona lapho. Wawungumkhumbi wase-Alekizandriya owawulophawu lwamakhanda amaphahla abonkulunkulu uKhasto loPholukhi. <verse eid="ACT 28:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="ACT 28:12"/>Sakhuphukela eSirakhusi sahlala khona okwensuku ezintathu. <verse eid="ACT 28:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="ACT 28:13"/>Sesisuka lapho sawela sayafika eRegiyumi. Ngakusasa kwaphephetha umoya weningizimu, kwathi ngelanga elilandelayo sayafika ePhuthewoli. <verse eid="ACT 28:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="ACT 28:14"/>Lapho safumana abazalwane abasicela ukuthi sihlale khona okweviki silabo. Sasesifika eRoma. <verse eid="ACT 28:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="ACT 28:15"/>Abazalwane balapho basebezwile ukuthi siyeza, ngakho bahamba baze bayafika eNkundleni yase-Aphiya laseziNkantini eziNtathu besihlangabeza. Wathi ebabona lababantu uPhawuli wabonga uNkulunkulu njalo waqiniswa. <verse eid="ACT 28:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="ACT 28:16"/>Sithe sesifikile eRoma, uPhawuli wavunyelwa ukuhlala yedwa, elindwe ngelilodwa ibutho.<verse eid="ACT 28:16"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UPhawuli Utshumayela ERoma Elindiwe</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="ACT 28:17"/>Ngemva kwensuku ezintathu uPhawuli wabiza abakhokheli bamaJuda. Bathi sebehlangene wathi kubo, “Bazalwane bami, loba ngingenzanga lutho olubi ebantwini bakithi kumbe olwephula imikhuba yabokhokho bethu, ngabotshwa eJerusalema nganikelwa kwabaseRoma. <verse eid="ACT 28:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="ACT 28:18"/>Wona esengihlolile afisa ukungikhulula ngoba ngangingelacala loba elakuphi ukuganga okwakungafanela ukufa. <verse eid="ACT 28:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="ACT 28:19"/>Kodwa kwathi ngoba amaJuda ekwala lokho ngabona sekufanele ukuthi ngikhalaze kuKhesari; kungayisikho ukuthi ngasengimangalela abantu bakithi. <verse eid="ACT 28:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="ACT 28:20"/>Ngalesisizatho ngicelile ukuthi ngilibone, ngikhulume lani. Kungenxa yethemba lika-Israyeli okwenza ngibotshwe ngale iketane.”<verse eid="ACT 28:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="ACT 28:21"/>Baphendula bathi, “Kasitholanga zincwadi ezivela eJudiya mayelana lawe, njalo kakho umzalwane ovela khonale oke wabika kumbe wakhuluma ulutho olubi ngawe. <verse eid="ACT 28:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="ACT 28:22"/>Kodwa sifuna ukuzwa imibono yakho, ngoba siyakwazi ukuthi ezindaweni zonke abantu bakhuluma kubi ngaloluhlelo lwenkolo.”<verse eid="ACT 28:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="ACT 28:23"/>Balungiselela ukuhlangana loPhawuli ngelanga elithile elalibekiwe, njalo kweza abantu abanengi endaweni ayehlala kuyo. Kusukela ekuseni kwaze kwaba ntambama echaza umbuso kaNkulunkulu njalo efakaza ngokuseMthethweni kaMosi lakubaPhrofethi. Wazama njalo ukubazisa ngoJesu <verse eid="ACT 28:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="ACT 28:24"/>Abanye basuthiseka ngalokhu ayekutsho, kodwa abanye kabazange bakholwe. <verse eid="ACT 28:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="ACT 28:25"/>Baphikisana bona bodwa basebesuka ngemva kokuba uPhawuli esephethe inkulumo yakhe ngokuthi, “Nxa uMoya oNgcwele wakhuluma iqiniso kubokhokho benu aze ukhulume ngomphrofethi u-Isaya ukuthi:<verse eid="ACT 28:25"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="ACT 28:26"/>‘Hamba kulababantu uyekuthi,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ACT 28:26">“Lizahlala lisizwa kokuphela, kodwa lingaqedisisi;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ACT 28:26">lizahlala libona kokuphela kodwa lingabonisisi.”<verse eid="ACT 28:26"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="ACT 28:27"/>Ngoba inhliziyo yalababantu isibuthundu;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ACT 28:27">kabasezwa ngezindlebe zabo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ACT 28:27">njalo sebevale amehlo abo;</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ACT 28:27">ngoba bangaqabuka bebona ngamehlo abo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ACT 28:27">bezwe ngezindlebe zabo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ACT 28:27">baqedisise ngezinhliziyo zabo,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ACT 28:27">baphenduke, lami ngibasilise.’<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">28.27 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">U-Isaya 6.9-10</char></note><verse eid="ACT 28:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="ACT 28:28"/>Ngakho ngithanda ukuthi lazi ukuba insindiso kaNkulunkulu isithunyelwe kwabeZizwe, njalo bona bazalalela!” [ <verse eid="ACT 28:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="ACT 28:29"/>Ngemva kwalokhu, amaJuda asuka, ephikisana wodwa kakhulu.]<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">28.29 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Livesi kayikho kwamanye amaBhayibhili esiLungu.</char></note><verse eid="ACT 28:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="ACT 28:30"/>UPhawuli wahlala khona okweminyaka emibili egcweleyo, ehlala endlini yakhe ayeloje kuyo, njalo esemukela ngesihle bonke ababesiza bezombona. <verse eid="ACT 28:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="ACT 28:31"/>Watshumayela ngombuso kaNkulunkulu, wafundisa ngeNkosi uJesu Khristu ngesibindi njalo engaphazanyiswa muntu.<verse eid="ACT 28:31"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ACT 28"/>
</usx>
